3495 In2iGui.showMessage = function(options) {
3496 	if (typeof(options)=='string') {
3497 		// TODO: Backwards compatibility
3498 		options={text:options};
3499 	}
3500 	if (!In2iGui.message) {
3501 		In2iGui.message = n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_message',html:'<div><div></div></div>'});
3502 		if (!n2i.browser.msie) {
3503 			n2i.setOpacity(In2iGui.message,0);
3504 		}
3505 		document.body.appendChild(In2iGui.message);
3506 	}
3507 	n2i.dom.setText(In2iGui.message.getElementsByTagName('div')[1],options.text);
3508 	In2iGui.message.style.display = 'block';
3509 	In2iGui.message.style.zIndex = In2iGui.nextTopIndex();
3510 	In2iGui.message.style.marginLeft = (In2iGui.message.clientWidth/-2)+'px';
3511 	In2iGui.message.style.marginTop = n2i.getScrollTop()+'px';
3512 	if (!n2i.browser.msie) {
3513 		n2i.ani(In2iGui.message,'opacity',1,300);
3514 	}
3515 	window.clearTimeout(In2iGui.messageTimer);
3516 	if (options.duration) {
3517 		In2iGui.messageTimer = window.setTimeout(In2iGui.hideMessage,options.duration);
3518 	}
3519 };

3534 	if (!t) {
3535 		t = n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_tooltip',style:'display:none;',html:'<div><div></div></div>',parent:document.body});
3536 		In2iGui.toolTips[key] = t;
3537 	}
3538 	t.onclick = function() {In2iGui.hideToolTip(options);};
3539 	var n = n2i.get(options.element);
3540 	var pos = n2i.getPosition(n);
3541 	t.select('div')[1].update(options.text);
3542 	if (t.style.display=='none' && !n2i.browser.msie) {
3543 		n2i.setOpacity(t,0);
3544 	}
3545 	n2i.setStyle(t,{'display':'block',zIndex:In2iGui.nextTopIndex()});
3546 	n2i.setStyle(t,{left:(pos.left-t.clientWidth+4)+'px',top:(pos.top+2-(t.clientHeight/2)+(n.clientHeight/2))+'px'});
3547 	if (!n2i.browser.msie) {
3548 		n2i.ani(t,'opacity',1,300);
3549 	}
3550 };

3566 In2iGui.getElement = function(widgetOrElement) {
3567 	if (n2i.dom.isElement(widgetOrElement)) {
3568 		return widgetOrElement;

3575 In2iGui.isWithin = function(e,element) {
3576 	e = new n2i.Event(e);
3577 	var offset = {left:n2i.getLeft(element),top:n2i.getTop(element)};
3578 	var dims = {width:element.clientWidth,height:element.clientHeight};
3579 	return e.left()>offset.left && e.left()<offset.left+dims.width && e.top()>offset.top && e.top()<offset.top+dims.height;
3580 };

3622 In2iGui.NumberValidator = function(options) {
3623 	n2i.override({allowNull:false,min:0,max:10},options)
3624 	this.min = options.min;
3625 	this.max = options.max;
3626 	this.allowNull = options.allowNull;
3627 	this.middle = Math.max(Math.min(this.max,0),this.min);
3628 }
3629 
3630 In2iGui.NumberValidator.prototype = {
3631 	validate : function(value) {
3632 		if (n2i.isBlank(value) && this.allowNull) {
3633 			return {valid:true,value:null};
3634 		}
3635 		var number = parseFloat(value);
3636 		if (isNaN(number)) {
3637 			return {valid:false,value:this.middle};
3638 		} else if (number<this.min) {
3639 			return {valid:false,value:this.min};
3640 		} else if (number>this.max) {
3641 			return {valid:false,value:this.max};
3642 		}
3643 		return {valid:true,value:number};
3644 	}
3645 }

3660 In2iGui.bounceIn = function(node,time) {
3661 	if (n2i.browser.msie) {
3662 		n2i.setStyle(node,{'display':'block',visibility:'visible'});
3663 	} else {
3664 		n2i.setStyle(node,{'display':'block','opacity':0,visibility:'visible'});
3665 		n2i.animate(node,'transform','scale(0.1)',0);// rotate(10deg)
3666 		window.setTimeout(function() {
3667 			n2i.animate(node,'opacity',1,300);
3668 			n2i.animate(node,'transform','scale(1)',400,{ease:n2i.ease.backOut}); // rotate(0deg)
3669 		});
3670 	}

3673 //////////////////////////// Positioning /////////////////////////////
3674 
3675 In2iGui.positionAtElement = function(element,target,options) {
3676 	options = options || {};
3677 	element = n2i.get(element);
3678 	target = n2i.get(target);
3679 	var origDisplay = n2i.getStyle(element,'display');
3680 	if (origDisplay=='none') {
3681 		n2i.setStyle(element,{'visibility':'hidden','display':'block'});
3682 	}
3683 	var pos = left = n2i.getLeft(target),top = n2i.getTop(target);
3684 	var vert=options.vertical || null;
3685 	if (options.horizontal && options.horizontal=='right') {
3686 		left = left+target.clientWidth-element.clientWidth;
3687 	}
3688 	if (vert=='topOutside') {
3689 		top = top-element.clientHeight;
3690 	} else if (vert=='bottomOutside') {
3691 		top = top+target.clientHeight;
3692 	}
3693 	left+=(options.left || 0);
3694 	top+=(options.top || 0);
3695 	n2i.setStyle(element,{'left':left+'px','top':top+'px'});
3696 	if (origDisplay=='none') {
3697 		n2i.setStyle(element,{'visibility':'visible','display':'none'});
3698 	}
3699 };

3701 In2iGui.getTextAreaHeight = function(input) {
3702 	var t = this.textAreaDummy;
3703 	if (!t) {
3704 		var t = this.textAreaDummy = document.createElement('div');
3705 		t.className='in2igui_textarea_dummy';
3706 		document.body.appendChild(t);
3707 	}
3708 	var html = input.value;
3709 	if (html[html.length-1]==='\n') {
3710 		html+='x';
3711 	}
3712 	html = n2i.escape(html).replace(/\n/g,'<br/>');
3713 	t.innerHTML = html;
3714 	t.style.width=(input.clientWidth)+'px';
3715 	return t.clientHeight;
3716 }

3720 In2iGui.extend = function(obj,options) {
3721 	if (!obj.name) {
3722 		In2iGui.latestObjectIndex++;
3723 		obj.name = 'unnamed'+In2iGui.latestObjectIndex;
3724 	}
3725 	if (options!==undefined) {
3726 		if (obj.options) {
3727 			obj.options = n2i.override(obj.options,options);
3728 		}
3729 		obj.element = n2i.get(options.element);
3730 		obj.name = options.name;
3731 	}
3732 	var ctrl = In2iGui.get();
3733 	ctrl.objects[obj.name] = obj;
3734 	obj.delegates = [];
3735 	obj.listen = function(delegate) {
3736 		n2i.addToArray(this.delegates,delegate);
3737 	}
3738 	obj.removeDelegate = function(delegate) {
3739 		n2i.removeFromArray(this.delegates,delegate);
3740 	}
3741 	obj.clearDelegates = function() {
3742 		this.delegates = [];
3743 	}
3744 	obj.fire = function(method,value,event) {
3745 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,method,value,event);
3746 	}
3747 	obj.fireProperty = function(key,value) {
3748 		In2iGui.firePropertyChange(this,key,value);
3749 	}
3750 	if (!obj.getElement) {
3751 		obj.getElement = function() {
3752 			return this.element;
3753 		}
3754 	}
3755 	if (!obj.valueForProperty) {
3756 		obj.valueForProperty = function(p) {return this[p]};
3757 	}
3758 	if (obj['$$layout']) {
3759 		ctrl.layoutWidgets.push(obj);
3760 	}
3761 };

3763 In2iGui.callDelegatesDrop = function(dragged,dropped) {

3765 	var result = null;
3766 	for (var i=0; i < gui.delegates.length; i++) {
3767 		if (gui.delegates[i]['$drop$'+dragged.kind+'$'+dropped.kind]) {
3768 			gui.delegates[i]['$drop$'+dragged.kind+'$'+dropped.kind](dragged,dropped);
3769 		}
3770 	}
3771 };

3773 In2iGui.callAncestors = function(obj,method,value,event) {
3774 	if (typeof(value)=='undefined') value=obj;
3775 	var d = In2iGui.get().getAncestors(obj);
3776 	for (var i=0; i < d.length; i++) {
3777 		if (d[i][method]) {
3778 			d[i][method](value,event);
3779 		}
3780 	};
3781 };

3783 In2iGui.callDescendants = function(obj,method,value,event) {
3784 	if (typeof(value)=='undefined') {
3785 		value=obj;
3786 	}
3787 	if (!method[0]=='$') {
3788 		method = '$'+method;
3789 	}
3790 	var d = In2iGui.get().getDescendants(obj);
3791 	for (var i=0; i < d.length; i++) {
3792 		if (d[i][method]) {
3793 			thisResult = d[i][method](value,event);
3794 		}
3795 	};
3796 };

3806 In2iGui.callDelegates = function(obj,method,value,event) {
3807 	if (typeof(value)=='undefined') {
3808 		value=obj;
3809 	}
3810 	var result = null;
3811 	if (obj.delegates) {
3812 		for (var i=0; i < obj.delegates.length; i++) {
3813 			var delegate = obj.delegates[i];
3814 			var thisResult = null;
3815 			if (obj.name && delegate['$'+method+'$'+obj.name]) {
3816 				thisResult = delegate['$'+method+'$'+obj.name](value,event);
3817 			} else if (delegate['$'+method]) {
3818 				thisResult = delegate['$'+method](value,event);
3819 			}
3820 			if (result==null && thisResult!=null && typeof(thisResult)!='undefined') {
3821 				result = thisResult;
3822 			}
3823 		};
3824 	}
3825 	var superResult = In2iGui.callSuperDelegates(obj,method,value,event);
3826 	if (result==null && superResult!=null) {
3827 		result = superResult;
3828 	}
3829 	return result;
3830 };
3831 
3832 In2iGui.callSuperDelegates = function(obj,method,value,event) {
3833 	if (typeof(value)=='undefined') value=obj;
3834 	var gui = In2iGui.get();
3835 	var result = null;
3836 	for (var i=0; i < gui.delegates.length; i++) {
3837 		var delegate = gui.delegates[i];
3838 		var thisResult = null;
3839 		if (obj.name && delegate['$'+method+'$'+obj.name]) {
3840 			thisResult = delegate['$'+method+'$'+obj.name](value,event);
3841 		} else if (delegate['$'+method]) {
3842 			thisResult = delegate['$'+method](value,event);
3843 		}
3844 		if (result==null && thisResult!=null && typeof(thisResult)!='undefined') {
3845 			result = thisResult;
3846 		}
3847 	};
3848 	return result;
3849 };
3850 
3851 In2iGui.resolveImageUrl = function(widget,img,width,height) {
3852 	for (var i=0; i < widget.delegates.length; i++) {
3853 		if (widget.delegates[i].$resolveImageUrl) {
3854 			return widget.delegates[i].$resolveImageUrl(img,width,height);
3855 		}
3856 	};
3857 	var gui = In2iGui.get();
3858 	for (var i=0; i < gui.delegates.length; i++) {
3859 		var delegate = gui.delegates[i];
3860 		if (delegate.$resolveImageUrl) {
3861 			return delegate.$resolveImageUrl(img,width,height);
3862 		}
3863 	}
3864 	return null;
3865 };

3867 ////////////////////////////// Bindings ///////////////////////////

3869 In2iGui.firePropertyChange = function(obj,name,value) {
3870 	In2iGui.callDelegates(obj,'propertyChanged',{property:name,value:value});
3871 };
3872 
3873 In2iGui.bind = function(expression,delegate) {
3874 	if (expression.charAt(0)=='@') {
3875 		var pair = expression.substring(1).split('.');
3876 		var obj = In2iGui.get(pair[0]);
3877 		if (!obj) {
3878 			n2i.log('Unable to bind to '+expression);
3879 			return;
3880 		}
3881 		var p = pair.slice(1).join('.');
3882 		obj.listen({
3883 			$propertyChanged : function(prop) {
3884 				if (prop.property==p) {
3885 					delegate(prop.value);
3886 				}
3887 			}
3888 		});
3889 		return obj.valueForProperty(p);
3890 	}
3891 	return expression;
3892 };

3897 /** @private */
3898 In2iGui.jsonResponse = function(t,key) {
3899 	if (!t.responseXML || !t.responseXML.documentElement) {
3900 		var str = t.responseText.replace(/^\s+|\s+$/g, '');
3901 		if (str.length>0) {
3902 			var json = n2i.fromJSON(t.responseText);
3903 		} else {
3904 			json = '';
3905 		}
3906 		In2iGui.callDelegates(json,'success$'+key)
3907 	} else {
3908 		In2iGui.callDelegates(t,'success$'+key)
3909 	}
3910 };

3912 /** @deprecated */
3913 In2iGui.json = function(data,url,delegateOrKey) {
3914 	n2i.log('In2iGui.json is deprecated')
3915 	var options = {url:url,method:'post',parameters:{},onException:function(e) {throw e}};
3916 	if (typeof(delegateOrKey)=='string') {
3917 		options.onSuccess=function(t) {In2iGui.jsonResponse(t,delegateOrKey)};
3918 	} else {
3919 		delegate = delegateOrKey;
3920 	}
3921 	for (key in data) {
3922 		options.parameters[key]=n2i.toJSON(data[key])
3923 	}
3924 	n2i.request(options);
3925 };
3926 
3927 In2iGui.request = function(options) {
3928 	options = n2i.override({method:'post',parameters:{}},options);
3929 	if (options.json) {
3930 		for (key in options.json) {
3931 			options.parameters[key]=n2i.toJSON(options.json[key]);
3932 		}
3933 	}
3934 	var onSuccess = options.onSuccess;
3935 	options.onSuccess=function(t) {
3936 		if (typeof(onSuccess)=='string') {
3937 			In2iGui.jsonResponse(t,onSuccess);
3938 		} else if (t.responseXML && t.responseXML.documentElement && t.responseXML.documentElement.nodeName!='parsererror' && options.onXML) {
3939 			options.onXML(t.responseXML);
3940 		} else if (options.onJSON) {
3941 			var str = t.responseText.replace(/^\s+|\s+$/g, '');
3942 			if (str.length>0) {
3943 				var json = n2i.fromJSON(t.responseText);
3944 			} else {
3945 				var json = null;
3946 			}
3947 			options.onJSON(json);
3948 		} else if (typeof(onSuccess)=='function') {
3949 			onSuccess(t);
3950 		} else if (options.onText) {
3951 			options.onText(t.responseText);
3952 		}
3953 	};
3954 	var onFailure = options.onFailure;
3955 	options.onFailure = function(t) {
3956 		if (typeof(onFailure)=='string') {
3957 			In2iGui.callDelegates(t,'failure$'+onFailure)
3958 		} else if (typeof(onFailure)=='function') {
3959 			onFailure(t);
3960 		}
3961 	}
3962 	options.onException = function(t,e) {n2i.log(e)};
3963 	n2i.request(options);
3964 };

3966 In2iGui.parseItems = function(doc) {
3967 	var root = doc.documentElement;
3968 	var out = [];
3969 	In2iGui.parseSubItems(root,out);
3970 	return out;
3971 };

3973 In2iGui.parseSubItems = function(parent,array) {
3974 	var children = parent.childNodes;
3975 	for (var i=0; i < children.length; i++) {
3976 		var node = children[i];
3977 		if (node.nodeType==1 && node.nodeName=='title') {
3978 			array.push({title:node.getAttribute('title'),type:'title'})
3979 		} else if (node.nodeType==1 && node.nodeName=='item') {
3980 			var sub = [];
3981 			In2iGui.parseSubItems(node,sub);
3982 			array.push({
3983 				title:node.getAttribute('title'),
3984 				value:node.getAttribute('value'),
3985 				icon:node.getAttribute('icon'),
3986 				kind:node.getAttribute('kind'),
3987 				badge:node.getAttribute('badge'),
3988 				children:sub
3989 			});
3990 		}
3991 	};
3992 }

4013 /** A data source
4014  * @constructor
4015  */
4016 In2iGui.Source = function(options) {
4017 	this.options = n2i.override({url:null,dwr:null,parameters:[],lazy:false},options);
4018 	this.name = options.name;
4019 	this.data = null;
4020 	this.parameters = this.options.parameters;
4021 	In2iGui.extend(this);
4022 	if (options.delegate) {
4023 		this.listen(options.delegate);
4024 	}
4025 	this.busy=false;
4026 	In2iGui.onDomReady(this.init.bind(this));
4027 };
4028 
4029 In2iGui.Source.prototype = {
4030 	/** @private */
4031 	init : function() {
4032 		var self = this;
4033 		n2i.each(this.parameters,function(parm) {
4034 			var val = In2iGui.bind(parm.value,function(value) {
4035 				self.changeParameter(parm.key,value);
4036 			});
4037 			parm.value = self.convertValue(val);
4038 		});
4039 		if (!this.options.lazy) {
4040 			this.refresh();
4041 		}
4042 	},
4043 	/** @private */
4044 	convertValue : function(value) {		
4045 		if (value && value.getTime) {
4046 			return value.getTime();
4047 		}
4048 		return value;
4049 	},
4050 	/** Refreshes the data source */
4051 	refresh : function() {
4052 		if (this.delegates.length==0) {
4053 			return;
4054 		}
4055 		for (var i=0; i < this.delegates.length; i++) {
4056 			var d = this.delegates[i];
4057 			if (d['$sourceShouldRefresh'] && d['$sourceShouldRefresh']()==false) {
4058 				return;
4059 			}
4060 		};
4061 		if (this.busy) {
4062 			this.pendingRefresh = true;
4063 			return;
4064 		}
4065 		this.pendingRefresh = false;
4066 		var self = this;
4067 		if (this.options.url) {
4068 			var prms = {};
4069 			for (var i=0; i < this.parameters.length; i++) {
4070 				var p = this.parameters[i];
4071 				prms[p.key] = p.value;
4072 			};
4073 			this.busy=true;
4074 			In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'sourceIsBusy');
4075 			n2i.request({
4076 				method:'post',
4077 				url:this.options.url,
4078 				parameters:prms,
4079 				onSuccess : function(t) {self.parse(t)},
4080 				onException : function(t,e) {n2i.log(e)},
4081 				onFailure : function(t,e) {
4082 					In2iGui.callDelegates(self,'sourceFailed');
4083 				}
4084 			});
4085 		} else if (this.options.dwr) {
4086 			var pair = this.options.dwr.split('.');
4087 			var facade = eval(pair[0]);
4088 			var method = pair[1];
4089 			var args = facade[method].argumentNames();
4090 			for (var i=0; i < args.length; i++) {
4091 				if (this.parameters[i]) {
4092 					args[i]=this.parameters[i].value===undefined ? null : this.parameters[i].value;
4093 				}
4094 			};
4095 			args[args.length-1]=function(r) {self.parseDWR(r)};
4096 			this.busy=true;
4097 			In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'sourceIsBusy');
4098 			facade[method].apply(facade,args);
4099 		}
4100 	},
4101 	/** @private */
4102 	end : function() {
4103 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'sourceIsNotBusy');
4104 		this.busy=false;
4105 		if (this.pendingRefresh) {
4106 			this.refresh();
4107 		}
4108 	},
4109 	/** @private */
4110 	parse : function(t) {
4111 		if (t.responseXML && t.responseXML.documentElement && t.responseXML.documentElement.nodeName!='parsererror') {
4112 			this.parseXML(t.responseXML);
4113 		} else {
4114 			var str = t.responseText.replace(/^\s+|\s+$/g, '');
4115 			if (str.length>0) {
4116 				var json = n2i.fromJSON(t.responseText);
4117 			} else {
4118 				var json = null;
4119 			}
4120 			this.fire('objectsLoaded',json);
4121 		}
4122 		this.end();
4123 	},
4124 	/** @private */
4125 	parseXML : function(doc) {
4126 		if (doc.documentElement.tagName=='items') {
4127 			this.data = In2iGui.parseItems(doc);
4128 			this.fire('itemsLoaded',this.data);
4129 		} else if (doc.documentElement.tagName=='list') {
4130 			this.fire('listLoaded',doc);
4131 		} else if (doc.documentElement.tagName=='articles') {
4132 			this.fire('articlesLoaded',doc);
4133 		}
4134 	},
4135 	/** @private */
4136 	parseDWR : function(data) {
4137 		this.data = data;
4138 		this.fire('objectsLoaded',data);
4139 		this.end();
4140 	},
4141 	addParameter : function(parm) {
4142 		//n2i.log(parm.value);
4143 		this.parameters.push(parm);
4144 	},
4145 	changeParameter : function(key,value) {
4146 		value = this.convertValue(value);
4147 		for (var i=0; i < this.parameters.length; i++) {
4148 			var p = this.parameters[i]
4149 			if (p.key==key) {
4150 				p.value=value;
4151 			}
4152 		};
4153 		window.clearTimeout(this.paramDelay);
4154 		this.paramDelay = window.setTimeout(function() {
4155 			this.refresh();
4156 		}.bind(this),100)
4157 	}

4160 /* EOF */In2iGui.getDragProxy = function() {
4161 	if (!In2iGui.dragProxy) {
4162 		In2iGui.dragProxy = n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_dragproxy',style:'display:none'});
4163 		document.body.appendChild(In2iGui.dragProxy);
4164 	}
4165 	return In2iGui.dragProxy;
4166 };

4168 In2iGui.startDrag = function(e,element,options) {
4169 	e = new n2i.Event(e);
4170 	var info = element.dragDropInfo;
4171 	In2iGui.dropTypes = In2iGui.findDropTypes(info);
4172 	if (!In2iGui.dropTypes) return;
4173 	var proxy = In2iGui.getDragProxy();
4174 	n2i.listen(document.body,'mousemove',In2iGui.dragListener);
4175 	n2i.listen(document.body,'mouseup',In2iGui.dragEndListener);
4176 	In2iGui.dragInfo = info;
4177 	if (info.icon) {
4178 		proxy.style.backgroundImage = 'url('+In2iGui.getIconUrl(info.icon,1)+')';
4179 	}
4180 	In2iGui.startDragPos = {top:e.top(),left:e.left()};
4181 	proxy.innerHTML = info.title ? '<span>'+n2i.escape(info.title)+'</span>' : '###';
4182 	In2iGui.dragging = true;
4183 	document.body.onselectstart = function () { return false; };
4184 };
4185 
4186 In2iGui.findDropTypes = function(drag) {
4187 	var gui = In2iGui.get();
4188 	var drops = null;
4189 	for (var i=0; i < gui.delegates.length; i++) {
4190 		if (gui.delegates[i].dragDrop) {
4191 			for (var j=0; j < gui.delegates[i].dragDrop.length; j++) {
4192 				var rule = gui.delegates[i].dragDrop[j];
4193 				if (rule.drag==drag.kind) {
4194 					if (drops==null) drops={};
4195 					drops[rule.drop] = {};
4196 				}
4197 			};
4198 		}
4199 	}
4200 	return drops;
4201 };
4202 
4203 In2iGui.dragListener = function(e) {
4204 	e = new n2i.Event(e);
4205 	In2iGui.dragProxy.style.left = (e.left()+10)+'px';
4206 	In2iGui.dragProxy.style.top = e.top()+'px';
4207 	In2iGui.dragProxy.style.display='block';
4208 	var target = In2iGui.findDropTarget(e.getElement());
4209 	if (target && In2iGui.dropTypes[target.dragDropInfo['kind']]) {
4210 		if (In2iGui.latestDropTarget) {
4211 			n2i.removeClass(In2iGui.latestDropTarget,'in2igui_drop');
4212 		}
4213 		n2i.addClass(target,'in2igui_drop');
4214 		In2iGui.latestDropTarget = target;
4215 	} else if (In2iGui.latestDropTarget) {
4216 		n2i.removeClass(In2iGui.latestDropTarget,'in2igui_drop');
4217 		In2iGui.latestDropTarget = null;
4218 	}
4219 	return false;
4220 };
4221 
4222 In2iGui.findDropTarget = function(node) {
4223 	while (node) {
4224 		if (node.dragDropInfo) {
4225 			return node;
4226 		}
4227 		node = node.parentNode;
4228 	}
4229 	return null;
4230 };
4231 
4232 In2iGui.dragEndListener = function(event) {
4233 	n2i.unListen(document.body,'mousemove',In2iGui.dragListener);
4234 	n2i.unListen(document.body,'mouseup',In2iGui.dragEndListener);
4235 	In2iGui.dragging = false;
4236 	if (In2iGui.latestDropTarget) {
4237 		n2i.removeClass(In2iGui.latestDropTarget,'in2igui_drop');
4238 		In2iGui.callDelegatesDrop(In2iGui.dragInfo,In2iGui.latestDropTarget.dragDropInfo);
4239 		In2iGui.dragProxy.style.display='none';
4240 	} else {
4241 		n2i.ani(In2iGui.dragProxy,'left',(In2iGui.startDragPos.left+10)+'px',200,{ease:n2i.ease.fastSlow});
4242 		n2i.ani(In2iGui.dragProxy,'top',(In2iGui.startDragPos.top-5)+'px',200,{ease:n2i.ease.fastSlow,hideOnComplete:true});
4243 	}
4244 	In2iGui.latestDropTarget=null;
4245 	document.body.onselectstart=null;
4246 };

4372 ////////////////////////////// Dragging ////////////////////////////////
4373 
4374 	/** @private */
4375 	startDrag : function(e) {
4376 		var event = new n2i.Event(e);
4377 		this.element.style.zIndex=In2iGui.nextPanelIndex();
4378 		var pos = { top : n2i.getTop(this.element), left : n2i.getLeft(this.element) };
4379 		this.dragState = {left:event.left()-pos.left,top:event.top()-pos.top};
4380 		this.latestPosition = {left: this.dragState.left, top:this.dragState.top};
4381 		this.latestTime = new Date().getMilliseconds();
4382 		var self = this;
4383 		this.moveListener = function(e) {self.drag(e)};
4384 		this.upListener = function(e) {self.endDrag(e)};
4385 		n2i.listen(document,'mousemove',this.moveListener);
4386 		n2i.listen(document,'mouseup',this.upListener);
4387 		n2i.listen(document,'mousedown',this.upListener);
4388 		event.stop();
4389 		document.body.onselectstart = function () { return false; };
4390 		return false;
4391 	},
4392 	/** @private */
4393 	calc : function(top,left) {
4394 		// TODO: No need to do this all the time
4395 		this.a = this.latestPosition.left-left;
4396 		this.b = this.latestPosition.top-top;
4397 		this.dist = Math.sqrt(Math.pow((this.a),2),Math.pow((this.b),2));
4398 		this.latestTime = new Date().getMilliseconds();
4399 		this.latestPosition = {'top':top,'left':left};
4400 	},
4401 	/** @private */
4402 	drag : function(e) {
4403 		var event = new n2i.Event(e);
4404 		this.element.style.right = 'auto';
4405 		var top = (event.top()-this.dragState.top);
4406 		var left = (event.left()-this.dragState.left);
4407 		this.element.style.top = Math.max(top,0)+'px';
4408 		this.element.style.left = Math.max(left,0)+'px';
4409 		//this.calc(top,left);
4410 		return false;
4411 	},
4412 	/** @private */
4413 	endDrag : function(e) {
4414 		n2i.unListen(document,'mousemove',this.moveListener);
4415 		n2i.unListen(document,'mouseup',this.upListener);
4416 		n2i.unListen(document,'mousedown',this.upListener);
4417 		document.body.onselectstart = null;
4418 	}
4419 }

4458 			if (d[i].options && d[i].options.key && d[i].getValue) {

4462 			}

4465 	},

4471 				var key = d[i].options.key;
4472 				if (key && values[key]!=undefined) {
4473 					d[i].setValue(values[key]);
4474 				}
4475 			}
4476 		}
4477 	},

4484 				return;
4485 			}
4486 		}
4487 	},

4493 				d[i].reset();
4494 			}

4640 In2iGui.Formula.Text.prototype = {

4663 	/** @private */

4666 			this.fire('submit');

4672 		this.value=this.input.value;
4673 		this.updateClass();
4674 		this.expand(true);
4675 		In2iGui.callAncestors(this,'childValueChanged',this.input.value);
4676 		this.fire('valueChanged',this.input.value);
4677 	},
4678 	updateFromNode : function(node) {
4679 		if (node.firstChild) {
4680 			this.setValue(node.firstChild.nodeValue);
4681 		} else {
4682 			this.setValue(null);
4683 		}
4684 	},
4685 	updateFromObject : function(data) {
4686 		this.setValue(data.value);
4687 	},
4688 	focus : function() {
4689 		try {
4690 			this.input.focus();
4691 		} catch (e) {}
4692 	},
4693 	select : function() {
4694 		try {
4695 			this.input.focus();
4696 			this.input.select();
4697 		} catch (e) {}
4698 	},
4699 	reset : function() {
4700 		this.setValue('');
4701 	},
4702 	setValue : function(value) {
4703 		if (value===undefined || value===null) {
4704 			value='';
4705 		}
4706 		this.value = value;
4707 		this.input.value = value;
4708 		this.expand(true);
4709 	},
4710 	getValue : function() {
4711 		return this.input.value;
4712 	},
4713 	getLabel : function() {
4714 		return this.options.label;
4715 	},
4716 	isEmpty : function() {
4717 		return this.input.value=='';
4718 	},
4719 	isBlank : function() {
4720 		return this.input.value.strip()=='';
4721 	},
4722 	setError : function(error) {
4723 		var isError = error ? true : false;
4724 		n2i.setClass(this.element,'in2igui_field_error',isError);
4725 		if (typeof(error) == 'string') {
4726 			In2iGui.showToolTip({text:error,element:this.element,key:this.name});
4727 		}
4728 		if (!isError) {
4729 			In2iGui.hideToolTip({key:this.name});
4730 		}
4731 	},
4732 	// Expanding
4733 	
4734 	$visibilityChanged : function() {
4735 		window.setTimeout(this.expand.bind(this));
4736 	},
4737 	/** @private */
4738 	expand : function(animate) {
4739 		if (!this.multiline) {return};
4740 		if (!n2i.dom.isVisible(this.element)) {return};
4741 		var textHeight = In2iGui.getTextAreaHeight(this.input);
4742 		textHeight = Math.max(32,textHeight);
4743 		textHeight = Math.min(textHeight,this.options.maxHeight);
4744 		if (animate) {
4745 			this.updateOverflow();
4746 			n2i.animate(this.input,'height',textHeight+'px',300,{ease:n2i.ease.slowFastSlow,onComplete:function() {
4747 				this.updateOverflow();
4748 				}.bind(this)
4749 			});
4750 		} else {
4751 			this.input.style.height=textHeight+'px';
4752 			this.updateOverflow();
4753 		}
4754 	},
4755 	updateOverflow : function() {
4756 		if (!this.multiline) return;
4757 		this.input.style.overflowY=this.input.clientHeight>=this.options.maxHeight ? 'auto' : 'hidden';
4758 	}
4759 }

4766  */
4767 In2iGui.Formula.DateTime = function(o) {
4768 	this.inputFormats = ['d-m-Y','d/m-Y','d/m/Y','d-m-Y H:i:s','d/m-Y H:i:s','d/m/Y H:i:s','d-m-Y H:i','d/m-Y H:i','d/m/Y H:i','d-m-Y H','d/m-Y H','d/m/Y H','d-m','d/m','d','Y','m-d-Y','m-d','m/d'];
4769 	this.outputFormat = 'd-m-Y H:i:s';
4770 	this.name = o.name;
4771 	this.element = n2i.get(o.element);
4772 	this.input = n2i.firstByTag(this.element,'input');
4773 	this.options = n2i.override({returnType:null,label:null,allowNull:true,value:null},o);
4774 	this.value = this.options.value;
4775 	In2iGui.extend(this);
4776 	this.addBehavior();
4777 	this.updateUI();
4778 }

4780 In2iGui.Formula.DateTime.create = function(options) {

4787 In2iGui.Formula.DateTime.prototype = {
4788 	addBehavior : function() {
4789 		In2iGui.addFocusClass({element:this.input,classElement:this.element,'class':'in2igui_field_focused'});
4790 		n2i.listen(this.input,'blur',this.check.bind(this));
4791 	},
4792 	updateFromNode : function(node) {
4793 		if (node.firstChild) {
4794 			this.setValue(node.firstChild.nodeValue);
4795 		} else {
4796 			this.setValue(null);
4797 		}
4798 	},
4799 	updateFromObject : function(data) {
4800 		this.setValue(data.value);
4801 	},
4802 	focus : function() {
4803 		try {this.input.focus();} catch (ignore) {}
4804 	},
4805 	reset : function() {
4806 		this.setValue('');
4807 	},
4808 	setValue : function(value) {
4809 		if (!value) {
4810 			this.value = null;
4811 		} else if (value.constructor==Date) {
4812 			this.value = value;
4813 		} else {
4814 			this.value = new Date();
4815 			this.value.setTime(parseInt(value)*1000);
4816 		}
4817 		this.updateUI();
4818 	},
4819 	check : function() {
4820 		var str = this.input.value;
4821 		var parsed = null;
4822 		for (var i=0; i < this.inputFormats.length && parsed==null; i++) {
4823 			parsed = Date.parseDate(str,this.inputFormats[i]);
4824 		};
4825 		if (this.options.allowNull || parsed!=null) {
4826 			this.value = parsed;
4827 		}
4828 		this.updateUI();
4829 	},
4830 	getValue : function() {
4831 		if (this.value!=null && this.options.returnType=='seconds') {
4832 			return Math.round(this.value.getTime()/1000);
4833 		}
4834 		return this.value;
4835 	},
4836 	getElement : function() {
4837 		return this.element;
4838 	},
4839 	getLabel : function() {
4840 		return this.options.label;
4841 	},
4842 	updateUI : function() {
4843 		if (this.value) {
4844 			this.input.value = this.value.dateFormat(this.outputFormat);
4845 		} else {
4846 			this.input.value = ''
4847 		}
4848 	}
4849 }

4869 In2iGui.Formula.Number.create = function(o) {

4872 		html:'<span><span><input type="text" value="'+(o.value!==undefined ? o.value : '0')+'"/><a class="in2igui_number_up"></a><a class="in2igui_number_down"></a></span></span>'
4873 	});

4876 
4877 In2iGui.Formula.Number.prototype = {
4878 	addBehavior : function() {
4879 		var e = this.element;
4880 		n2i.listen(this.input,'focus',function() {n2i.addClass(e,'in2igui_number_focused')});
4881 		n2i.listen(this.input,'blur',this.blurEvent.bind(this));
4882 		n2i.listen(this.input,'keyup',this.keyEvent.bind(this));
4883 		n2i.listen(this.up,'mousedown',this.upEvent.bind(this));
4884 		n2i.listen(this.down,'mousedown',this.downEvent.bind(this));
4885 	},
4886 	blurEvent : function() {
4887 		n2i.removeClass(this.element,'in2igui_number_focused');
4888 		this.updateField();
4889 	},
4890 	keyEvent : function(e) {
4891 		e = e || window.event;
4892 		if (e.keyCode==n2i.KEY_UP) {
4893 			n2i.stop(e);
4894 			this.upEvent();
4895 		} else if (e.keyCode==n2i.KEY_DOWN) {
4896 			this.downEvent();
4897 		} else {
4898 			var parsed = parseInt(this.input.value,10);
4899 			if (!isNaN(parsed)) {
4900 				this.setLocalValue(parsed,true);
4901 			} else {
4902 				this.setLocalValue(null,true);
4903 			}
4904 		}
4905 	},
4906 	downEvent : function() {
4907 		if (this.value===null) {
4908 			this.setLocalValue(this.options.min,true);
4909 		} else {
4910 			this.setLocalValue(this.value-1,true);
4911 		}
4912 		this.updateField();
4913 	},
4914 	upEvent : function() {
4915 		this.setLocalValue(this.value+1,true);
4916 		this.updateField();
4917 	},
4918 	getValue : function() {
4919 		return this.value;
4920 	},
4921 	getLabel : function() {
4922 		return this.options.label;
4923 	},
4924 	setValue : function(value) {
4925 		value = parseInt(value,10);
4926 		if (!isNaN(value)) {
4927 			this.setLocalValue(value,false);
4928 		}
4929 		this.updateField();
4930 	},
4931 	updateField : function() {
4932 		this.input.value = this.value===null || this.value===undefined ? '' : this.value;
4933 	},
4934 	setLocalValue : function(value,fire) {
4935 		var orig = this.value;
4936 		if (value===null || value===undefined && this.options.allowNull) {
4937 			this.value = null;
4938 		} else {
4939 			this.value = Math.min(Math.max(value,this.options.min),this.options.max);
4940 		}
4941 		if (fire && orig!==this.value) {
4942 			In2iGui.callAncestors(this,'childValueChanged',this.value);
4943 			this.fire('valueChanged',this.value);
4944 		}
4945 	},
4946 	reset : function() {
4947 		if (this.options.allowNull) {
4948 			this.value = null;
4949 		} else {
4950 			this.value = Math.min(Math.max(0,this.options.min),this.options.max);
4951 		}
4952 		this.updateField();
4953 	}
4954 }

4990 
4991 In2iGui.Formula.DropDown.prototype = {
4992 	/** @private */
4993 	addBehavior : function() {
4994 		In2iGui.addFocusClass({element:this.element,'class':'in2igui_dropdown_focused'});
4995 		n2i.listen(this.element,'click',this.clicked.bind(this));
4996 		n2i.listen(this.element,'blur',this.hideSelector.bind(this));
4997 		n2i.listen(this.element,'keydown',this._keyDown.bind(this));
4998 	},
4999 	/** @private */
5000 	updateIndex : function() {
5001 		this.index=-1;
5002 		for (var i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
5003 			if (this.items[i].value==this.value) {
5004 				this.index=i;
5005 			}
5006 		};
5007 	},
5008 	/** @private */
5009 	updateUI : function() {
5010 		var selected = this.items[this.index];
5011 		if (selected) {
5012 			var text = selected.label || selected.title || '';
5013 			this.inner.innerHTML='';
5014 			n2i.dom.addText(this.inner,n2i.wrap(text));
5015 		} else if (this.options.placeholder) {
5016 			this.inner.innerHTML='';
5017 			this.inner.appendChild(n2i.build('em',{text:n2i.escape(this.options.placeholder)}));
5018 		} else {
5019 			this.inner.innerHTML='';
5020 		}
5021 		if (!this.selector) {
5022 			return;
5023 		}
5024 		var as = this.selector.getElementsByTagName('a');
5025 		n2i.each(as,function(a,i) {
5026 			if (this.index==i) {
5027 				n2i.addClass(a,'in2igui_selected');
5028 			}
5029 			else {a.className=''};
5030 		}.bind(this));
5031 	},
5032 	/** @private */
5033 	clicked : function(e) {
5034 		n2i.stop(e);
5035 		this.buildSelector();
5036 		var el = this.element, s=this.selector;
5037 		el.focus();
5038 		if (!this.items) return;
5039 		var docHeight = n2i.getDocumentHeight();
5040 		if (docHeight<200) {
5041 			var left = n2i.getLeft(this.element);
5042 			n2i.setStyle(this.selector,{'left':left+'px',top:'5px'});
5043 		} else {
5044 			n2i.place({
5045 				target:{element:this.element,vertical:1,horizontal:0},
5046 				source:{element:this.selector,vertical:0,horizontal:0}
5047 			});
5048 		}
5049 		n2i.setStyle(s,{visibility:'hidden',display:'block',width:''});
5050 		var height = Math.min(docHeight-n2i.getTop(s)-5,200);
5051 		var width = Math.max(el.clientWidth-5,100,s.clientWidth+20);
5052 		var space = n2i.getDocumentWidth()-n2i.getLeft(el)-20;
5053 		width = Math.min(width,space);
5054 		n2i.setStyle(s,{visibility:'visible',width:width+'px',zIndex:In2iGui.nextTopIndex(),maxHeight:height+'px'});
5055 	},
5056 	getValue : function() {
5057 		return this.value;
5058 	},
5059 	/** @private */
5060 	_keyDown : function(e) {
5061 		if (this.items.length==0) {
5062 			return;
5063 		}
5064 		if (e.keyCode==40) {
5065 			n2i.stop(e);
5066 			if (this.index>=this.items.length-1) {
5067 				this.value=this.items[0].value;
5068 			} else {
5069 				this.value=this.items[this.index+1].value;
5070 			}
5071 			this.updateIndex();
5072 			this.updateUI();
5073 			this.fireChange();
5074 		} else if (e.keyCode==38) {
5075 			n2i.stop(e);
5076 			if (this.index>0) {
5077 				this.index--;
5078 			} else {
5079 				this.index = this.items.length-1;
5080 			}
5081 			this.value = this.items[this.index].value;
5082 			this.updateUI();
5083 			this.fireChange();
5084 		}
5085 	},
5086 	setValue : function(value) {
5087 		this.value = value;
5088 		this.updateIndex();
5089 		this.updateUI();
5090 	},
5091 	reset : function() {
5092 		this.setValue(null);
5093 	},
5094 	getLabel : function() {
5095 		return this.options.label;
5096 	},
5097 	refresh : function() {
5098 		if (this.options.source) {
5099 			this.options.source.refresh();
5100 		}
5101 	},
5102 	getItem : function(value) {
5103 		if (this.index>=0) {
5104 			return this.items[this.index];
5105 		}
5106 		return 0;
5107 	},
5108 	addItem : function(item) {
5109 		this.items.push(item);
5110 		this.dirty = true;
5111 		this.updateIndex();
5112 		this.updateUI();
5113 	},
5114 	setItems : function(items) {
5115 		this.items = items;
5116 		this.dirty = true;
5117 		this.index = -1;
5118 		this.updateIndex();
5119 		this.updateUI();
5120 	},
5121 	/** @private */
5122 	$itemsLoaded : function(items) {
5123 		this.setItems(items);
5124 	},
5125 	/** @private */
5126 	hideSelector : function() {
5127 		if (!this.selector) return;
5128 		this.selector.style.display='none';
5129 	},
5130 	/** @private */
5131 	buildSelector : function() {
5132 		if (!this.dirty || !this.items) return;
5133 		if (!this.selector) {
5134 			this.selector = n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_dropdown_selector'});
5135 			document.body.appendChild(this.selector);
5136 			n2i.listen(this.selector,'mousedown',function(e) {e.stop()});
5137 		} else {
5138 			this.selector.innerHTML='';
5139 		}
5140 		var self = this;
5141 		n2i.each(this.items,function(item,i) {
5142 			var e = n2i.build('a',{href:'#',text:item.label || item.title});
5143 			n2i.listen(e,'mousedown',function(e) {
5144 				n2i.stop(e);
5145 				self.itemClicked(item,i);
5146 			})
5147 			if (i==self.index) {
5148 				n2i.addClass(e,'in2igui_selected')
5149 			};
5150 			self.selector.appendChild(e);
5151 		});
5152 		this.dirty = false;
5153 	},
5154 	/** @private */
5155 	itemClicked : function(item,index) {
5156 		this.index = index;
5157 		var changed = this.value!=this.items[index].value;
5158 		this.value = this.items[index].value;
5159 		this.updateUI();
5160 		this.hideSelector();
5161 		if (changed) {
5162 			this.fireChange();
5163 		}
5164 	},
5165 	fireChange : function() {
5166 		In2iGui.callAncestors(this,'childValueChanged',this.value);
5167 		this.fire('valueChanged',this.value);
5168 	}
5169 }

5252 		n2i.listen(this.element,'click',this.click.bind(this));
5253 	},
5254 	/** @private */
5255 	click : function(e) {
5256 		n2i.stop(e);
5257 		this.element.focus();
5258 		this.value = !this.value;
5259 		this.updateUI();
5260 		In2iGui.callAncestors(this,'childValueChanged',this.value);
5261 		this.fire('valueChanged',this.value);
5262 	},
5263 	/** @private */
5264 	updateUI : function() {
5265 		n2i.setClass(this.element,'in2igui_checkbox_selected',this.value);
5266 	},
5267 	/** Sets the value
5268 	 * @param {Boolean} value Whether the checkbox is checked
5269 	 */
5270 	setValue : function(value) {
5271 		this.value = value===true || value==='true';
5272 		this.updateUI();
5273 	},
5274 	/** Gets the value
5275 	 * @return {Boolean} Whether the checkbox is checked
5276 	 */
5277 	getValue : function() {
5278 		return this.value;
5279 	},
5280 	/** Resets the checkbox */
5281 	reset : function() {
5282 		this.setValue(false);
5283 	},
5284 	/** Gets the label
5285 	 * @return {String} The checkbox label
5286 	 */
5287 	getLabel : function() {
5288 		return this.options.label;
5289 	}
5290 }

5326 In2iGui.Formula.Checkboxes.prototype = {
5327 	/** @private */
5328 	addBehavior : function() {
5329 		var checks = n2i.byClass(this.element,'in2igui_checkbox');
5330 		n2i.each(checks,function(check,i) {
5331 			n2i.listen(check,'click',function(e) {
5332 				n2i.stop(e);
5333 				this.flipValue(this.items[i].value);
5334 			}.bind(this))
5335 		}.bind(this))
5336 	},
5337 	getValue : function() {
5338 		return this.values;
5339 	},
5340 	/** @deprecated */
5341 	getValues : function() {
5342 		return this.values;
5343 	},
5344 	checkValues : function() {
5345 		var newValues = [];
5346 		for (var i=0; i < this.values.length; i++) {
5347 			var value = this.values[i];
5348 			var found = false;
5349 			for (var j=0; j < this.items.length; j++) {
5350 				found = found || this.items[j].value===value;
5351 			}
5352 			for (var j=0; j < this.subItems.length; j++) {
5353 				found = found || this.subItems[j].hasValue(value);
5354 			};
5355 			if (found) {
5356 				newValues.push(value);
5357 			}
5358 		};
5359 		this.values=newValues;
5360 	},
5361 	setValue : function(values) {
5362 		this.values=values;
5363 		this.checkValues();
5364 		this.updateUI();
5365 	},
5366 	/** @deprecated */
5367 	setValues : function(values) {
5368 		this.setValue(values);
5369 	},
5370 	flipValue : function(value) {
5371 		n2i.flipInArray(this.values,value);
5372 		this.checkValues();
5373 		this.updateUI();
5374 		this.fire('valueChanged',this.values);
5375 		In2iGui.callAncestors(this,'childValueChanged',this.values);
5376 	},
5377 	updateUI : function() {
5378 		for (var i=0; i < this.subItems.length; i++) {
5379 			this.subItems[i].updateUI();
5380 		};
5381 		var nodes = n2i.byClass(this.element,'in2igui_checkbox');
5382 		n2i.each(this.items,function(item,i) {
5383 			n2i.setClass(nodes[i],'in2igui_checkbox_selected',this.values.indexOf(item.value)!==-1);
5384 		}.bind(this));
5385 	},
5386 	refresh : function() {
5387 		for (var i=0; i < this.subItems.length; i++) {
5388 			this.subItems[i].refresh();
5389 		};
5390 	},
5391 	reset : function() {
5392 		this.setValues([]);
5393 	},
5394 	registerSource : function(source) {
5395 		source.parent = this;
5396 		this.sources.push(source);
5397 	},
5398 	registerItem : function(item) {
5399 		// If it is a number, treat it as such
5400 		if (parseInt(item.value)==item.value) {
5401 			item.value = parseInt(item.value);
5402 		}
5403 		this.items.push(item);
5404 	},
5405 	registerItems : function(items) {
5406 		items.parent = this;
5407 		this.subItems.push(items);
5408 	},
5409 	getLabel : function() {
5410 		return this.options.label;
5411 	},
5412 	$itemsLoaded : function(items) {
5413 		n2i.each(items,function(item) {
5414 			var node = n2i.build('a',{'class':'in2igui_checkbox',href:'javascript:void(0);',html:'<span><span></span></span>'+n2i.escape(item.title)});
5415 			n2i.listen(node,'click',function(e) {
5416 				n2i.stop(e);
5417 				this.flipValue(item.value);
5418 			}.bind(this))
5419 			In2iGui.addFocusClass({element:node,'class':'in2igui_checkbox_focused'});
5420 			this.element.appendChild(node);
5421 			this.items.push(item);
5422 		}.bind(this));
5423 		this.checkValues();
5424 		this.updateUI();
5425 	}
5426 }

5431  * Check box items
5432  * @constructor
5433  */
5434 In2iGui.Formula.Checkboxes.Items = function(options) {
5435 	this.element = n2i.get(options.element);
5436 	this.name = options.name;
5437 	this.parent = null;
5438 	this.options = options;
5439 	this.checkboxes = [];
5440 	In2iGui.extend(this);
5441 	if (this.options.source) {
5442 		this.options.source.listen(this);
5443 	}

5445 
5446 In2iGui.Formula.Checkboxes.Items.prototype = {
5447 	refresh : function() {
5448 		if (this.options.source) {
5449 			this.options.source.refresh();
5450 		}
5451 	},
5452 	$itemsLoaded : function(items) {
5453 		this.checkboxes = [];
5454 		this.element.innerHTML='';
5455 		var self = this;
5456 		n2i.each(items,function(item) {
5457 			var node = n2i.build('a',{'class':'in2igui_checkbox',href:'#',html:'<span><span></span></span>'+item.title});
5458 			n2i.listen(node,'click',function(e) {
5459 				n2i.stop(e);
5460 				node.focus();
5461 				self.itemWasClicked(item)
5462 			});
5463 			In2iGui.addFocusClass({element:node,'class':'in2igui_checkbox_focused'});
5464 			self.element.appendChild(node);
5465 			self.checkboxes.push({title:item.title,element:node,value:item.value});
5466 		});
5467 		this.parent.checkValues();
5468 		this.updateUI();
5469 	},
5470 	itemWasClicked : function(item) {
5471 		this.parent.flipValue(item.value);
5472 	},
5473 	updateUI : function() {
5474 		try {
5475 		for (var i=0; i < this.checkboxes.length; i++) {
5476 			var item = this.checkboxes[i];
5477 			var index = n2i.indexInArray(this.parent.values,item.value);
5478 			n2i.setClass(item.element,'in2igui_checkbox_selected',index!=-1);
5479 		};
5480 		} catch (e) {
5481 			alert(typeof(this.parent.values));
5482 			alert(e);
5483 		}
5484 	},
5485 	hasValue : function(value) {
5486 		for (var i=0; i < this.checkboxes.length; i++) {
5487 			if (this.checkboxes[i].value==value) {
5488 				return true;
5489 			}
5490 		};
5491 		return false;
5492 	}
5493 }

5516 In2iGui.Formula.Tokens.prototype = {
5517 	setValue : function(objects) {
5518 		this.value = objects;
5519 		this.value.push('');
5520 		this.updateUI();
5521 	},
5522 	reset : function() {
5523 		this.value = [''];
5524 		this.updateUI();
5525 	},
5526 	getValue : function() {
5527 		var out = [];
5528 		n2i.each(this.value,function(value) {
5529 			value = value.strip();
5530 			if (value.length>0) {
5531 				out.push(value);
5532 			}
5533 		})
5534 		return out;
5535 	},
5536 	getLabel : function() {
5537 		return this.options.label;
5538 	},
5539 	updateUI : function() {
5540 		this.element.innerHTML='';
5541 		n2i.each(this.value,function(value,i) {
5542 			var input = n2i.build('input',{'class':'in2igui_tokens_token',parent:this.element});
5543 			if (this.options.width) {
5544 				input.style.width=this.options.width+'px';
5545 			}
5546 			input.value = value;
5547 			input.in2iguiIndex = i;
5548 			n2i.listen(input,'keyup',function() {
5549 				this.inputChanged(input,i)
5550 			}.bind(this));
5551 		}.bind(this));
5552 	},
5553 	/** @private */
5554 	inputChanged : function(input,index) {
5555 		if (index==this.value.length-1 && input.value!=this.value[index]) {
5556 			this.addField();
5557 		}
5558 		this.value[index] = input.value;
5559 	},
5560 	/** @private */
5561 	addField : function() {
5562 		var input = n2i.build('input',{'class':'in2igui_tokens_token'});
5563 		if (this.options.width) {
5564 			input.style.width = this.options.width+'px';
5565 		}
5566 		var i = this.value.length;
5567 		this.value.push('');
5568 		this.element.appendChild(input);
5569 		var self = this;
5570 		n2i.listen(input,'keyup',function() {self.inputChanged(input,i)});
5571 	}
5572 }

5576 /**
5577  * A date and time field
5578  * @constructor
5579  */
5580 In2iGui.Formula.StyleLength = function(o) {
5581 	this.options = n2i.override({value:null,min:0,max:1000,units:['px','pt','em','%'],defaultUnit:'px',allowNull:false},o);	
5582 	this.name = o.name;
5583 	var e = this.element = n2i.get(o.element);
5584 	this.input = n2i.firstByTag(e,'input');
5585 	var as = e.getElementsByTagName('a');
5586 	this.up = as[0];
5587 	this.down = as[1];
5588 	this.value = this.parseValue(this.options.value);
5589 	In2iGui.extend(this);
5590 	this.addBehavior();
5591 }
5592 
5593 In2iGui.Formula.StyleLength.prototype = {
5594 	/** @private */
5595 	addBehavior : function() {
5596 		var e = this.element;
5597 		n2i.listen(this.input,'focus',function() {n2i.addClass(e,'in2igui_number_focused')});
5598 		n2i.listen(this.input,'blur',this.blurEvent.bind(this));
5599 		n2i.listen(this.input,'keyup',this.keyEvent.bind(this));
5600 		n2i.listen(this.up,'mousedown',this.upEvent.bind(this));
5601 		n2i.listen(this.down,'mousedown',this.downEvent.bind(this));
5602 	},
5603 	/** @private */
5604 	parseValue : function(value) {
5605 		var num = parseFloat(value,10);
5606 		if (isNaN(num)) {
5607 			return null;
5608 		}
5609 		var parsed = {number: num, unit:this.options.defaultUnit};
5610 		for (var i=0; i < this.options.units.length; i++) {
5611 			var unit = this.options.units[i];
5612 			if (value.indexOf(unit)!=-1) {
5613 				parsed.unit = unit;
5614 				break;
5615 			}
5616 		};
5617 		parsed.number = Math.max(this.options.min,Math.min(this.options.max,parsed.number));
5618 		return parsed;
5619 	},
5620 	/** @private */
5621 	blurEvent : function() {
5622 		n2i.removeClass(this.element,'in2igui_number_focused');
5623 		this.updateInput();
5624 	},
5625 	/** @private */
5626 	keyEvent : function(e) {
5627 		e = e || window.event;
5628 		if (e.keyCode==n2i.KEY_UP) {
5629 			n2i.stop(e);
5630 			this.upEvent();
5631 		} else if (e.keyCode==n2i.KEY_DOWN) {
5632 			this.downEvent();
5633 		} else {
5634 			this.checkAndSetValue(this.parseValue(this.input.value));
5635 		}
5636 	},
5637 	/** @private */
5638 	updateInput : function() {
5639 		this.input.value = this.getValue();
5640 	},
5641 	/** @private */
5642 	checkAndSetValue : function(value) {
5643 		var old = this.value;
5644 		var changed = false;
5645 		if (old===null && value===null) {
5646 			// nothing
5647 		} else if (old!=null && value!=null && old.number===value.number && old.unit===value.unit) {
5648 			// nothing
5649 		} else {
5650 			changed = true;
5651 		}
5652 		this.value = value;
5653 		if (changed) {
5654 			this.fire('valueChanged',this.getValue());
5655 		}
5656 	},
5657 	/** @private */
5658 	downEvent : function() {
5659 		if (this.value) {
5660 			this.checkAndSetValue({number:Math.max(this.options.min,this.value.number-1),unit:this.value.unit});
5661 		} else {
5662 			this.checkAndSetValue({number:this.options.min,unit:this.options.defaultUnit});
5663 		}
5664 		this.updateInput();
5665 	},
5666 	/** @private */
5667 	upEvent : function() {
5668 		if (this.value) {
5669 			this.checkAndSetValue({number:Math.min(this.options.max,this.value.number+1),unit:this.value.unit});
5670 		} else {
5671 			this.checkAndSetValue({number:this.options.min+1,unit:this.options.defaultUnit});
5672 		}
5673 		this.updateInput();
5674 	},
5675 	
5676 	// Public
5677 	
5678 	getValue : function() {
5679 		return this.value ? this.value.number+this.value.unit : '';
5680 	},
5681 	setValue : function(value) {
5682 		this.value = this.parseValue(value);
5683 		this.updateInput();
5684 	}
5685 }

5717 In2iGui.Formula.Location.prototype = {

5721 		In2iGui.addFocusClass({element:this.latField.element,classElement:this.element,'class':'in2igui_field_focused'});
5722 		In2iGui.addFocusClass({element:this.lngField.element,classElement:this.element,'class':'in2igui_field_focused'});
5723 	},

5725 		return this.options.label;
5726 	},

5728 		this.setValue();
5729 	},
5730 	getValue : function() {
5731 		return this.value;
5732 	},
5733 	setValue : function(loc) {
5734 		if (loc) {
5735 			this.latField.setValue(loc.latitude);
5736 			this.lngField.setValue(loc.longitude);
5737 			this.value = loc;
5738 		} else {
5739 			this.latField.setValue();
5740 			this.lngField.setValue();
5741 			this.value = null;
5742 		}
5743 		this.updatePicker();

5753 			this.picker = new In2iGui.LocationPicker();
5754 			this.picker.listen(this);
5755 		}
5756 		this.picker.show({node:this.chooser,location:this.value});
5757 	},
5758 	$locationChanged : function(loc) {
5759 		this.setValue(loc);
5760 	},
5761 	$valueChanged : function() {
5762 		var lat = this.latField.getValue();
5763 		var lng = this.lngField.getValue();
5764 		if (lat===null || lng===null) {
5765 			this.value = null;
5766 		} else {
5767 			this.value = {latitude:lat,longitude:lng};
5768 		}
5769 		this.updatePicker();
5770 	}

5772 
5773 /* EOF *//**
5774  * <p><strong>Events:</strong></p>
5775  * <ul>
5776  * <li>listRowWasOpened - When a row is double clicked (rename to open)</li>
5777  * <li>selectionChanged - When a row is selected (rename to select)</li>
5778  * <li>selectionReset - When a selection is removed</li>
5779  * </ul>
5780  * <p><strong>Bindings:</strong></p>
5781  * <ul>
5782  * <li><del>window</del></li>
5783  * <li>window.page</li>
5784  * <li>sort.direction</li>
5785  * <li>sort.key</li>
5786  * </ul>
5787  * <p><strong>XML:</strong></p>
5788  * <code>
5789  * <list name="list" source="sourcesListSource" state="list"/>
5790  * <br/>
5791  * <list name="list" url="my_list_data.xml" state="list"/>
5792  * </code>
5793  *
5794  * @constructor
5795  * @param {Object} options The options : {url:null,source:null}
5796  */
5797 In2iGui.List = function(options) {
5798 	this.options = n2i.override({url:null,source:null},options);
5799 	this.element = n2i.get(options.element);
5800 	this.name = options.name;
5801 	if (this.options.source) {
5802 		this.options.source.listen(this);
5803 	}
5804 	this.url = options.url;
5805 	this.table = n2i.firstByTag(this.element,'table');
5806 	this.head = n2i.firstByTag(this.element,'thead');
5807 	this.body = n2i.firstByTag(this.element,'tbody');
5808 	this.columns = [];
5809 	this.rows = [];
5810 	this.selected = [];
5811 	this.navigation = n2i.firstByClass(this.element,'in2igui_list_navigation');
5812 	this.count = n2i.firstByClass(this.navigation,'in2igui_list_count');
5813 	this.windowPage = n2i.firstByClass(this.navigation,'window_page');
5814 	this.windowPageBody = n2i.firstByClass(this.navigation,'window_page_body');
5815 	this.parameters = {};
5816 	this.sortKey = null;
5817 	this.sortDirection = null;
5818 	
5819 	this.window = {size:null,page:0,total:0};
5820 	if (options.windowSize!='') {
5821 		this.window.size = parseInt(options.windowSize);
5822 	}
5823 	In2iGui.extend(this);
5824 	if (this.url)  {
5825 		this.refresh();
5826 	}
5827 }

5829 /**
5830  * Creates a new list widget
5831  * @param {Object} options The options
5832  */
5833 In2iGui.List.create = function(options) {
5834 	options = n2i.override({},options);
5835 	var e = options.element = n2i.build('div',{
5836 		'class':'in2igui_list',
5837 		html: '<div class="in2igui_list_navigation"><div class="in2igui_list_selection window_page"><div><div class="window_page_body"></div></div></div><span class="in2igui_list_count"></span></div><div class="in2igui_list_body"'+(options.maxHeight>0 ? ' style="max-height: '+options.maxHeight+'px; overflow: auto;"' : '')+'><table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><thead><tr></tr></thead><tbody></tbody></table></div>'});
5838 	return new In2iGui.List(options);
5839 }

5841 In2iGui.List.prototype = {
5842 	/** Hides the list */
5843 	hide : function() {
5844 		this.element.style.display='none';
5845 	},
5846 	/** Shows the list */
5847 	show : function() {
5848 		this.element.style.display='block';
5849 		this.refresh();
5850 	},
5851 	/** @private */
5852 	registerColumn : function(column) {
5853 		this.columns.push(column);
5854 	},
5855 	/** Gets an array of selections
5856 	 * @returns {Array} The selected rows
5857 	 */
5858 	getSelection : function() {
5859 		var items = [];
5860 		for (var i=0; i < this.selected.length; i++) {
5861 			items.push(this.rows[this.selected[i]]);
5862 		};
5863 		return items;
5864 	},
5865 	/** Gets the first selection or null
5866 	 * @returns {Object} The first selected row
5867 	 */
5868 	getFirstSelection : function() {
5869 		var items = this.getSelection();
5870 		if (items.length>0) return items[0];
5871 		else return null;
5872 	},
5873 	/** Add a parameter 
5874 	 * @param {String} key The key
5875 	 * @param {String} value The value
5876 	 */
5877 	setParameter : function(key,value) {
5878 		this.parameters[key]=value;
5879 	},
5880 	/** @private */
5881 	loadData : function(url) {
5882 		this.setUrl(url);
5883 	},
5884 	/**
5885 	 * Sets the lists data source and refreshes it if it is new
5886 	 * @param {In2iGui.Source} source The source
5887 	 */
5888 	setSource : function(source) {
5889 		if (this.options.source!=source) {
5890 			if (this.options.source) {
5891 				this.options.source.removeDelegate(this);
5892 			}
5893 			source.listen(this);
5894 			this.options.source = source;
5895 			source.refresh();
5896 		}
5897 	},
5898 	/**
5899 	 * Set an url to load data from, and load the data
5900 	 * @param {String} url The url
5901 	 */
5902 	setUrl : function(url) {
5903 		if (this.options.source) {
5904 			this.options.source.removeDelegate(this);
5905 			this.options.source=null;
5906 		}
5907 		this.url = url;
5908 		this.selected = [];
5909 		this.sortKey = null;
5910 		this.sortDirection = null;
5911 		this.resetState();
5912 		this.refresh();
5913 	},
5914 	/** Clears the data of the list */
5915 	clear : function() {
5916 		this.selected = [];
5917 		this.columns = [];
5918 		this.rows = [];
5919 		this.navigation.style.display='none';
5920 		n2i.dom.clear(this.body);
5921 		n2i.dom.clear(this.head);
5922 		if (this.options.source) {
5923 			this.options.source.removeDelegate(this);
5924 		}
5925 		this.options.source = null;
5926 		this.url = null;
5927 	},
5928 	/** Resets the window state of the navigator */
5929 	resetState : function() {
5930 		this.window = {size:null,page:0,total:0};
5931 		In2iGui.firePropertyChange(this,'window',this.window);
5932 		In2iGui.firePropertyChange(this,'window.page',this.window.page);
5933 	},
5934 	/** @private */
5935 	valueForProperty : function(p) {
5936 		if (p=='window.page') return this.window.page;
5937 		if (p=='window.page') return this.window.page;
5938 		else if (p=='sort.key') return this.sortKey;
5939 		else if (p=='sort.direction') return (this.sortDirection || 'ascending');
5940 		else return this[p];
5941 	},
5942 	/** @private */
5943 	$sourceShouldRefresh : function() {
5944 		return this.element.style.display!='none';
5945 	},
5946 	/** @private */
5947 	refresh : function() {
5948 		if (this.options.source) {
5949 			this.options.source.refresh();
5950 			return;
5951 		}
5952 		if (!this.url) return;
5953 		var url = this.url;
5954 		if (typeof(this.window.page)=='number') {
5955 			url+=url.indexOf('?')==-1 ? '?' : '&';
5956 			url+='windowPage='+this.window.page;
5957 		}
5958 		if (this.window.size) {
5959 			url+=url.indexOf('?')==-1 ? '?' : '&';
5960 			url+='windowSize='+this.window.size;
5961 		}
5962 		if (this.sortKey) {
5963 			url+=url.indexOf('?')==-1 ? '?' : '&';
5964 			url+='sort='+this.sortKey;
5965 		}
5966 		if (this.sortDirection) {
5967 			url+=url.indexOf('?')==-1 ? '?' : '&';
5968 			url+='direction='+this.sortDirection;
5969 		}
5970 		for (key in this.parameters) {
5971 			url+=url.indexOf('?')==-1 ? '?' : '&';
5972 			url+=key+'='+this.parameters[key];
5973 		}
5974 		In2iGui.request({
5975 			url:url,
5976 			onJSON : this.$objectsLoaded.bind(this),
5977 			onXML : this.$listLoaded.bind(this)
5978 		});
5979 	},
5980 	/** @private */
5981 	sort : function(index) {
5982 		var key = this.columns[index].key;
5983 		if (key==this.sortKey) {
5984 			this.sortDirection = this.sortDirection=='ascending' ? 'descending' : 'ascending';
5985 			In2iGui.firePropertyChange(this,'sort.direction',this.sortDirection);
5986 		} else {
5987 			In2iGui.firePropertyChange(this,'sort.key',key);
5988 		}
5989 		this.sortKey = key;
5990 	},
5991 
5992 	/** @private */
5993 	$listLoaded : function(doc) {
5994 		this.selected = [];
5995 		this.parseWindow(doc);
5996 		this.buildNavigation();
5997 		n2i.dom.clear(this.head);
5998 		n2i.dom.clear(this.body);
5999 		this.rows = [];
6000 		this.columns = [];
6001 		var headTr = document.createElement('tr');
6002 		var sort = doc.getElementsByTagName('sort');
6003 		this.sortKey=null;
6004 		this.sortDirection=null;
6005 		if (sort.length>0) {
6006 			this.sortKey=sort[0].getAttribute('key');
6007 			this.sortDirection=sort[0].getAttribute('direction');
6008 		}
6009 		var headers = doc.getElementsByTagName('header');
6010 		for (var i=0; i < headers.length; i++) {
6011 			var className = '';
6012 			var th = document.createElement('th');
6013 			var width = headers[i].getAttribute('width');
6014 			var key = headers[i].getAttribute('key');
6015 			var sortable = headers[i].getAttribute('sortable')=='true';
6016 			if (width && width!='') {
6017 				th.style.width=width+'%';
6018 			}
6019 			if (sortable) {
6020 				var self = this;
6021 				th.in2iguiIndex = i;
6022 				th.onclick=function() {self.sort(this.in2iguiIndex)};
6023 				className+='sortable';
6024 			}
6025 			if (key==this.sortKey) {
6026 				className+=' sort_'+this.sortDirection;
6027 			}
6028 			th.className=className;
6029 			var span = document.createElement('span');
6030 			th.appendChild(span);
6031 			span.appendChild(document.createTextNode(headers[i].getAttribute('title') || ''));
6032 			headTr.appendChild(th);
6033 			this.columns.push({'key':key,'sortable':sortable,'width':width});
6034 		};
6035 		this.head.appendChild(headTr);
6036 		var frag = document.createDocumentFragment();
6037 		var rows = doc.getElementsByTagName('row');
6038 		for (var i=0; i < rows.length; i++) {
6039 			var cells = rows[i].getElementsByTagName('cell');
6040 			var row = document.createElement('tr');
6041 			var icon = rows[i].getAttribute('icon');
6042 			var title = rows[i].getAttribute('title');
6043 			for (var j=0; j < cells.length; j++) {
6044 				var td = document.createElement('td');
6045 				this.parseCell(cells[j],td);
6046 				row.appendChild(td);
6047 				if (!title) {
6048 					title = n2i.dom.getText(cells[j]);
6049 				}
6050 				if (!icon) {
6051 					icon = cells[j].getAttribute('icon');
6052 				}
6053 			};
6054 			var info = {id:rows[i].getAttribute('id'),kind:rows[i].getAttribute('kind'),icon:icon,title:title,index:i};
6055 			row.dragDropInfo = info;
6056 			this.addRowBehavior(row,i);
6057 			frag.appendChild(row);
6058 			//this.body.insert(row);
6059 			this.rows.push(info);
6060 		};
6061 		this.body.appendChild(frag);
6062 		this.fire('selectionReset');
6063 	},
6064 	
6065 	/** @private */
6066 	$objectsLoaded : function(data) {
6067 		if (data==null) {
6068 			// NOOP
6069 		} else if (data.constructor == Array) {
6070 			this.setObjects(data);
6071 		} else {
6072 			this.setData(data);
6073 		}
6074 		this.fire('selectionReset');
6075 	},
6076 	/** @private */
6077 	$sourceIsBusy : function() {
6078 		this.busy = true;
6079 		n2i.addClass(this.element,'in2igui_list_busy');
6080 	},
6081 	/** @private */
6082 	$sourceIsNotBusy : function() {

6087 	/** @private */
6088 	filter : function(str) {
6089 		var len = 20;
6090 		var regex = new RegExp("[\\w]{"+len+",}","g");
6091 		var match = regex.exec(str);
6092 		if (match) {
6093 			for (var i=0; i < match.length; i++) {
6094 				var rep = '';
6095 				for (var j=0; j < match[i].length; j++) {
6096 					rep+=match[i][j];
6097 					if ((j+1)%len==0) rep+='\u200B';
6098 				};
6099 				str = str.replace(match[i],rep);
6100 			};
6101 		}
6102 		return str;
6103 	},
6104 	
6105 	/** @private */
6106 	parseCell : function(node,cell) {
6107 		var icon = node.getAttribute('icon');
6108 		if (icon!=null && icon!='') {
6109 			cell.appendChild(In2iGui.createIcon(icon,1));
6110 		}
6111 		for (var i=0; i < node.childNodes.length; i++) {
6112 			var child = node.childNodes[i];
6113 			if (n2i.dom.isDefinedText(child)) {
6114 				n2i.dom.addText(cell,child.nodeValue);
6115 			} else if (n2i.dom.isElement(child,'break')) {
6116 				cell.appendChild(document.createElement('br'));
6117 			} else if (n2i.dom.isElement(child,'icon')) {
6118 				cell.appendChild(In2iGui.createIcon(child.getAttribute('icon'),1));
6119 			} else if (n2i.dom.isElement(child,'line')) {
6120 				var line = n2i.build('p',{'class':'in2igui_list_line'});
6121 				if (child.getAttribute('dimmed')=='true') {
6122 					n2i.addClass(line,'in2igui_list_dimmed')
6123 				}
6124 				cell.appendChild(line);
6125 				this.parseCell(child,line);
6126 			} else if (n2i.dom.isElement(child,'object')) {
6127 				var obj = n2i.build('div',{'class':'object'});
6128 				if (child.getAttribute('icon')) {
6129 					obj.appendChild(In2iGui.createIcon(child.getAttribute('icon'),1));
6130 				}
6131 				if (child.firstChild && child.firstChild.nodeType==n2i.TEXT_NODE && child.firstChild.nodeValue.length>0) {
6132 					n2i.dom.addText(obj,child.firstChild.nodeValue);
6133 				}
6134 				cell.appendChild(obj);
6135 			} else if (n2i.dom.isElement(child,'icons')) {
6136 				var icons = n2i.build('span',{'class':'in2igui_list_icons'});
6137 				this.parseCell(child,icons);
6138 				cell.appendChild(icons);
6139 			}
6140 		};
6141 	},
6142 	/** @private */
6143 	parseWindow : function(doc) {
6144 		var wins = doc.getElementsByTagName('window');
6145 		if (wins.length>0) {
6146 			var win = wins[0];
6147 			this.window.total = parseInt(win.getAttribute('total'));
6148 			this.window.size = parseInt(win.getAttribute('size'));
6149 			this.window.page = parseInt(win.getAttribute('page'));
6150 		} else {
6151 			this.window.total = 0;
6152 			this.window.size = 0;
6153 			this.window.page = 0;
6154 		}
6155 	},
6156 	/** @private */
6157 	buildNavigation : function() {
6158 		var self = this;
6159 		var pages = this.window.size>0 ? Math.ceil(this.window.total/this.window.size) : 0;
6160 		if (pages<2) {
6161 			this.navigation.style.display='none';
6162 			return;
6163 		}
6164 		this.navigation.style.display='block';
6165 		var from = ((this.window.page)*this.window.size+1);
6166 		n2i.dom.setText(this.count,(from+'-'+Math.min((this.window.page+1)*this.window.size,this.window.total)+' / '+this.window.total));
6167 		var pageBody = this.windowPageBody;
6168 		pageBody.innerHTML='';
6169 		if (pages<2) {
6170 			this.windowPage.style.display='none';	
6171 		} else {
6172 			var indices = this.buildPages(pages,this.window.page);
6173 			for (var i=0; i < indices.length; i++) {
6174 				var index = indices[i];
6175 				if (index==='') {
6176 					pageBody.appendChild(n2i.build('span',{text:''}));
6177 				} else {
6178 					var a = document.createElement('a');
6179 					a.appendChild(document.createTextNode(index+1));
6180 					a.setAttribute('data-index',index);
6181 					a.onmousedown = function() {
6182 						self.windowPageWasClicked(this);
6183 						return false;
6184 					}
6185 					if (index==self.window.page) {
6186 						a.className='selected';
6187 					}
6188 					n2i.log(a);
6189 					pageBody.appendChild(a);
6190 				}
6191 			}
6192 			this.windowPage.style.display='block';
6193 		}
6194 	},
6195 	/** @private */
6196 	buildPages : function(count,selected) {
6197 		var pages = [];
6198 		var x = false;
6199 		for (var i=0;i<count;i++) {
6200 			if (i<1 || i>count-2 || Math.abs(selected-i)<5) {
6201 				pages.push(i);
6202 				x=false;
6203 			} else {
6204 				if (!x) {
6205 					pages.push('')
6206 				};
6207 				x=true;
6208 			}
6209 		}
6210 		return pages;
6211 	},
6212 	/** @private */
6213 	setData : function(data) {
6214 		this.selected = [];
6215 		var win = data.window || {};
6216 		this.window.total = win.total || 0;
6217 		this.window.size = win.size || 0;
6218 		this.window.page = win.page || 0;
6219 		this.buildNavigation();
6220 		this.buildHeaders(data.headers);
6221 		this.buildRows(data.rows);
6222 	},
6223 	/** @private */
6224 	buildHeaders : function(headers) {
6225 		n2i.dom.clear(this.head);
6226 		this.columns = [];
6227 		var tr = n2i.build('tr',{parent:this.head});
6228 		n2i.each(headers,function(h,i) {
6229 			var th = n2i.build('th');
6230 			if (h.width) {
6231 				th.style.width = h.width+'%';
6232 			}
6233 			if (h.sortable) {
6234 				n2i.listen(th,'click',function() {this.sort(i)}.bind(this));
6235 				n2i.addClass(th,'sortable');
6236 			}
6237 			th.appendChild(n2i.build('span',{text:h.title}));
6238 			tr.appendChild(th);
6239 			this.columns.push(h);
6240 		}.bind(this));
6241 	},
6242 	/** @private */
6243 	buildRows : function(rows) {
6244 		var self = this;
6245 		n2i.dom.clear(this.body);
6246 		this.rows = [];
6247 		if (!rows) return;
6248 		n2i.each(rows,function(r,i) {
6249 			var tr = new Element('tr');
6250 			var icon = r.icon;
6251 			var title = r.title;
6252 			r.cells.each(function(c) {
6253 				var td = new Element('td');
6254 				if (c.icon) {
6255 					td.insert(In2iGui.createIcon(c.icon,1));
6256 					icon = icon || c.icon;
6257 				}
6258 				if (c.text) {
6259 					td.appendChild(document.createTextNode(c.text))
6260 					title = title || c.text;
6261 				}
6262 				tr.insert(td);
6263 			})
6264 			self.body.insert(tr);
6265 			// TODO: Memory leak!
6266 			var info = {id:r.id,kind:r.kind,icon:icon,title:title,index:i};
6267 			tr.dragDropInfo = info;
6268 			self.rows.push({id:r.id,kind:r.kind,icon:icon,title:title,index:i,data:r.data});
6269 			this.addRowBehavior(tr,i);
6270 		}.bind(this));
6271 	},
6272 	/** @private */
6273 	setObjects : function(objects) {
6274 		this.selected = [];
6275 		this.body.update();
6276 		this.rows = [];
6277 		for (var i=0; i < objects.length; i++) {
6278 			var row = new Element('tr');
6279 			var obj = objects[i];
6280 			var title = null;
6281 			for (var j=0; j < this.columns.length; j++) {
6282 				var cell = new Element('td');
6283 				if (this.builder) {
6284 					cell.update(this.builder.buildColumn(this.columns[j],obj));
6285 				} else {
6286 					var value = obj[this.columns[j].key] || '';
6287 					if (value.constructor == Array) {
6288 						for (var k=0; k < value.length; k++) {
6289 							if (value[k].constructor == Object) {
6290 								cell.insert(this.createObject(value[k]));
6291 							} else {
6292 								cell.insert(new Element('div').update(value));
6293 							}
6294 						};
6295 					} else if (value.constructor == Object) {
6296 						cell.insert(this.createObject(value[j]));
6297 					} else {
6298 						cell.insert(value);
6299 						title = title==null ? value : title;
6300 					}
6301 				}
6302 				row.insert(cell);
6303 			};
6304 			var info = {id:obj.id,kind:obj.kind,title:title};
6305 			row.dragDropInfo = info;
6306 			this.body.insert(row);
6307 			this.addRowBehavior(row,i);
6308 			this.rows.push(obj);
6309 		};
6310 	},
6311 	/** @private */
6312 	createObject : function(object) {
6313 		var node = new Element('div',{'class':'object'});
6314 		if (object.icon) {
6315 			node.insert(In2iGui.createIcon(object.icon,1));
6316 			//node.insert(new Element('span',{'class':'in2igui_icon in2igui_icon_1'}).setStyle({'backgroundImage':'url("'+In2iGui.getIconUrl(object.icon,1)+'")'}));
6317 		}
6318 		return node.insert(object.text || object.name || '');
6319 	},
6320 	/** @private */
6321 	addRowBehavior : function(row,index) {
6322 		var self = this;
6323 		row.onmousedown = function(e) {
6324 			if (self.busy) {return};
6325 			self.rowDown(index);
6326 			In2iGui.startDrag(e,row);
6327 			return false;
6328 		}
6329 		row.ondblclick = function() {
6330 			if (self.busy) {return};
6331 			self.rowDoubleClick(index);
6332 			return false;
6333 		}
6334 	},
6335 	/** @private */
6336 	changeSelection : function(indexes) {
6337 		var rows = this.body.getElementsByTagName('tr');
6338 		for (var i=0;i<this.selected.length;i++) {
6339 			n2i.removeClass(rows[this.selected[i]],'selected');
6340 		}
6341 		for (var i=0;i<indexes.length;i++) {
6342 			n2i.addClass(rows[indexes[i]],'selected');
6343 		}
6344 		this.selected = indexes;
6345 		this.fire('selectionChanged',this.rows[indexes[0]]);
6346 	},
6347 	/** @private */
6348 	rowDown : function(index) {
6349 		this.changeSelection([index]);
6350 	},
6351 	/** @private */
6352 	rowDoubleClick : function(index) {
6353 		this.fire('listRowWasOpened',this.getFirstSelection());
6354 	},
6355 	/** @private */
6356 	windowPageWasClicked : function(tag) {
6357 		var index = parseInt(tag.getAttribute('data-index'));
6358 		this.window.page = index;
6359 		In2iGui.firePropertyChange(this,'window',this.window);
6360 		In2iGui.firePropertyChange(this,'window.page',this.window.page);
6361 	}
6362 };

6367 In2iGui.Tabs = function(o) {

6370 	this.element = n2i.get(o.element);
6371 	this.activeTab = -1;

6373 	this.bar = n2i.firstByTag(x,'ul');

6399 In2iGui.Tabs.prototype = {
6400 	/** @private */
6401 	addBehavior : function() {
6402 		for (var i=0; i < this.tabs.length; i++) {
6403 			this.addTabBehavior(this.tabs[i],i);
6404 		};
6405 	},
6406 	/** @private */
6407 	addTabBehavior : function(tab,index) {	
6408 		n2i.listen(tab,'click',function() {
6409 			this.tabWasClicked(index);
6410 		}.bind(this))
6411 	},
6412 	/** @private */
6413 	registerTab : function(obj) {
6414 		obj.parent = this;
6415 		this.tabs.push(obj);
6416 	},
6417 	/** @private */
6418 	tabWasClicked : function(index) {
6419 		this.activeTab = index;
6420 		this.updateGUI();
6421 	},
6422 	/** @private */
6423 	updateGUI : function() {
6424 		for (var i=0; i < this.tabs.length; i++) {
6425 			n2i.setClass(this.tabs[i],'in2igui_tabs_selected',i==this.activeTab);
6426 			this.contents[i].style.display = i==this.activeTab ? 'block' : 'none';
6427 		};
6428 	},
6429 	createTab : function(options) {
6430 		options = options || {};
6431 		var tab = n2i.build('li',{html:'<a><span><span>'+n2i.escape(options.title)+'</span></span></a>',parent:this.bar});
6432 		this.addTabBehavior(tab,this.tabs.length);
6433 		this.tabs.push(tab);
6434 		var e = options.element = n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_tabs_tab'});
6435 		if (options.padding>0) {
6436 			e.style.padding = options.padding+'px';
6437 		}
6438 		this.contents.push(e);
6439 		this.element.appendChild(e);
6440 		if (this.activeTab==-1) {
6441 			this.activeTab=0;
6442 			n2i.addClass(tab,'in2igui_tabs_selected');
6443 		} else {
6444 			e.style.display='none';
6445 		}
6446 		return new In2iGui.Tab(options);
6447 	}
6448 };

6477 In2iGui.ObjectList.create = function(o) {
6478 	o=o || {};
6479 	var e = o.element = n2i.build('table',{'class':'in2igui_objectlist',cellpadding:'0',cellspacing:'0'});
6480 	if (o.template) {
6481 		var head = '<thead><tr>';
6482 		for (var i=0; i < o.template.length; i++) {
6483 			head+='<th>'+(o.template[i].label || '')+'</th>';
6484 		};
6485 		head+='</tr></thead>';
6486 		e.innerHTML=head;
6487 	}
6488 	n2i.build('tbody',{parent:e});
6489 	var list = new In2iGui.ObjectList(o);
6490 	if (o.template) {
6491 		n2i.each(o.template,function(item) {
6492 			list.registerTemplateItem(new In2iGui.ObjectList.Text(item.key));
6493 		});
6494 	}

6498 In2iGui.ObjectList.prototype = {
6499 	ignite : function() {
6500 		this.addObject({});
6501 	},
6502 	addObject : function(data,addToEnd) {
6503 		if (this.objects.length==0 || addToEnd) {
6504 			var obj = new In2iGui.ObjectList.Object(this.objects.length,data,this);
6505 			this.objects.push(obj);
6506 			this.body.appendChild(obj.getElement());
6507 		} else {
6508 			var last = this.objects[this.objects.length-1];
6509 			var obj = new In2iGui.ObjectList.Object(last.index,data,this);
6510 			last.index++;
6511 			this.objects.push(obj);
6512 			this.objects.push(last);
6513 			this.body.insertBefore(obj.getElement(),last.getElement())
6514 		}
6515 	},
6516 	reset : function() {
6517 		for (var i=0; i < this.objects.length; i++) {
6518 			var element = this.objects[i].getElement();
6519 			if (!element.parentNode) {
6520 				n2i.log('no parent for...');
6521 				n2i.log(element);
6522 			} else {
6523 				element.parentNode.removeChild(element);
6524 			}
6525 		};
6526 		this.objects = [];
6527 		this.addObject({});
6528 	},
6529 	addObjects : function(data) {
6530 		for (var i=0; i < data.length; i++) {
6531 			this.addObject(data[i]);
6532 		};
6533 	},
6534 	setObjects : function(data) {
6535 		this.reset();
6536 		this.addObjects(data);
6537 	},
6538 	getObjects : function(data) {
6539 		var list = [];
6540 		for (var i=0; i < this.objects.length-1; i++) {
6541 			list.push(this.objects[i].getData());
6542 		};
6543 		return list;
6544 	},
6545 	getValue : function() {
6546 		return this.getObjects();
6547 	},
6548 	setValue : function(data) {
6549 		this.setObjects(data);
6550 	},
6551 	registerTemplateItem : function(item) {
6552 		this.template.push(item);
6553 	},
6554 	objectDidChange : function(obj) {
6555 		if (obj.index>=this.objects.length-1) {
6556 			this.addObject({},true);
6557 		}
6558 	},
6559 	getLabel : function() {
6560 		return this.options.label;
6561 	}
6562 }

6574 In2iGui.ObjectList.Object.prototype = {
6575 	getElement : function() {
6576 		if (!this.element) {
6577 			var self = this;
6578 			this.element = document.createElement('tr');
6579 			for (var i=0; i < this.list.template.length; i++) {
6580 				var template = this.list.template[i];
6581 				var field = template.clone();
6582 				field.object = this;
6583 				this.fields.push(field);
6584 				var cell = document.createElement('td');
6585 				if (i==0) cell.className='first';
6586 				cell.appendChild(field.getElement());
6587 				field.setValue(this.data[template.key]);
6588 				this.element.appendChild(cell);
6589 			};
6590 		}
6591 		return this.element;
6592 	},
6593 	valueDidChange : function() {
6594 		this.list.objectDidChange(this);
6595 	},
6596 	getData : function() {
6597 		var data = this.data;
6598 		for (var i=0; i < this.fields.length; i++) {
6599 			data[this.fields[i].key] = this.fields[i].getValue();
6600 		};
6601 		return data;
6602 	}
6603 }

6687 /**
6688  * Creates a new instance of an alert
6689  * <br/><strong>options:</strong> { name: String, title: String, text: String, emotion: 'smile' | 'gasp', modal: Boolean}
6690  * @static
6691  */
6692 In2iGui.Alert.create = function(options) {
6693 	options = n2i.override({title:'',text:'',emotion:null,title:null},options);
6694 	
6695 	var element = options.element = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_alert'});
6696 	var body = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_alert_body'});
6697 	element.insert(body);
6698 	var content = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_alert_content'});
6699 	body.insert(content);
6700 	document.body.appendChild(element);
6701 	var obj = new In2iGui.Alert(options);
6702 	if (options.emotion) {
6703 		obj.setEmotion(options.emotion);
6704 	}
6705 	if (options.title) {
6706 		obj.setTitle(options.title);
6707 	}
6708 	if (options.text) {
6709 		obj.setText(options.text);
6710 	}
6711 	
6712 	return obj;
6713 }

6715 In2iGui.Alert.prototype = {

6792 /**
6793  * Creates a new button
6794  */
6795 In2iGui.Button.create = function(o) {
6796 	var o = n2i.override({text:'',highlighted:false,enabled:true},o);
6797 	var className = 'in2igui_button'+(o.highlighted ? ' in2igui_button_highlighted' : '');
6798 	if (o.small && o.rounded) {
6799 		className+=' in2igui_button_small_rounded';
6800 	}
6801 	if (!o.enabled) {
6802 		className+=' in2igui_button_disabled';
6803 	}
6804 	var element = o.element = n2i.build('a',{'class':className,href:'#'});
6805 	var element2 = document.createElement('span');
6806 	element.appendChild(element2);
6807 	var element3 = document.createElement('span');
6808 	element2.appendChild(element3);
6809 	if (o.icon) {
6810 		var icon = n2i.build('em',{'class':'in2igui_button_icon',style:'background-image:url('+In2iGui.getIconUrl(o.icon,1)+')'});
6811 		if (!o.text || o.text.length==0) {
6812 			n2i.addClass(icon,'in2igui_button_icon_notext');
6813 		}
6814 		element3.appendChild(icon);
6815 	}
6816 	if (o.text && o.text.length>0) {
6817 		n2i.dom.addText(element3,o.text);
6818 	}
6819 	if (o.title && o.title.length>0) {
6820 		n2i.dom.addText(element3,o.title);
6821 	}
6822 	return new In2iGui.Button(o);
6823 }
