6825 In2iGui.Button.prototype = {
6826 	/** @private */
6827 	addBehavior : function() {
6828 		var self = this;
6829 		n2i.listen(this.element,'click',function(e) {
6830 			n2i.stop(e);
6831 			self.clicked();
6832 		});
6833 	},
6834 	/** @private */
6835 	clicked : function() {
6836 		if (this.enabled) {
6837 			if (this.options.confirm) {
6838 				In2iGui.confirmOverlay({
6839 					widget:this,
6840 					text:this.options.confirm.text,
6841 					okText:this.options.confirm.okText,
6842 					cancelText:this.options.confirm.cancelText,
6843 					onOk:this.fireClick.bind(this)
6844 				});
6845 			} else {
6846 				this.fireClick();
6847 			}
6848 		} else {
6849 			this.element.blur();
6850 		}
6851 	},
6852 	/** @private */
6853 	fireClick : function() {
6854 		this.fire('click');
6855 		if (this.options.submit) {
6856 			var form = In2iGui.get().getAncestor(this,'in2igui_formula');
6857 			if (form) {form.submit();}
6858 		}
6859 	},
6860 	/** Registers a function as a click listener or issues a click */
6861 	click : function(func) {
6862 		if (func) {
6863 			this.listen({$click:func});
6864 			return this;
6865 		} else {
6866 			this.clicked();
6867 		}
6868 	},
6869 	/** Registers a function as a click handler */
6870 	onClick : function(func) {
6871 		this.listen({$click:func});
6872 	},
6873 	/** Enables or disables the button */
6874 	setEnabled : function(enabled) {
6875 		this.enabled = enabled;
6876 		this.updateUI();
6877 	},
6878 	/** Enables the button */
6879 	enable : function() {
6880 		this.setEnabled(true);
6881 	},
6882 	/** Disables the button */
6883 	disable : function() {
6884 		this.setEnabled(false);
6885 	},
6886 	/** Sets whether the button is highlighted */
6887 	setHighlighted : function(highlighted) {
6888 		this.element.setClassName('in2igui_button_highlighted',highlighted);
6889 	},
6890 	/** @private */
6891 	updateUI : function() {
6892 		n2i.setClass(this.element,'in2igui_button_disabled',!this.enabled);
6893 	},
6894 	/** Sets the button text */
6895 	setText : function(text) {
6896 		this.element.getElementsByTagName('span')[1].innerHTML = text;
6897 	}
6898 }

6962 	/** Get the selected item
6963 	 * @returns {Object} The selected item, null if no selection */
6964 	getValue : function() {
6965 		return this.selection;
6966 	},
6967 	valueForProperty : function(p) {
6968 		if (p==='value') {
6969 			return this.selection ? this.selection.value : null;
6970 		} else if (p==='kind') {
6971 			return this.selection ? this.selection.kind : null;
6972 		}
6973 		return undefined;
6974 	},
6975 	/** Set the selected item
6976 	 * @param {Object} value The selected item */
6977 	setValue : function(value) {
6978 		var item = this.getSelectionWithValue(value);
6979 		if (item===null) {
6980 			this.selection = null;
6981 		} else {
6982 			this.selection = item;
6983 			this.kind=item.kind;
6984 		}
6985 		this.updateUI();
6986 		this.fireChange();
6987 	},
6988 	/** @private */
6989 	getSelectionWithValue : function(value) {
6990 		for (var i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
6991 			if (this.items[i].value==value) {
6992 				return this.items[i];
6993 			}
6994 		};
6995 		for (var i=0; i < this.subItems.length; i++) {
6996 			var items = this.subItems[i].items;
6997 			for (var j=0; j < items.length; j++) {
6998 				if (items[j].value==value) {
6999 					return items[j];
7000 				}
7001 			};
7002 		};
7003 		return null;
7004 	},
7005 	/** Set the value to null */
7006 	reset : function() {
7007 		this.setValue(null);
7008 	},
7009 	/** @private */
7010 	updateUI : function() {
7011 		for (var i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
7012 			n2i.setClass(this.items[i].element,'in2igui_selected',this.isSelection(this.items[i]));
7013 		};
7014 		for (var i=0; i < this.subItems.length; i++) {
7015 			this.subItems[i].updateUI();
7016 		};
7017 	},
7018 	/** @private */
7019 	changeSelection : function(item) {
7020 		for (var i=0; i < this.subItems.length; i++) {
7021 			this.subItems[i].selectionChanged(this.selection,item);
7022 		};
7023 		this.selection = item;
7024 		this.updateUI();
7025 		this.fireChange();
7026 	},
7027 	/** @private */
7028 	fireChange : function() {
7029 		this.fire('selectionChanged',this.selection);
7030 		this.fireProperty('value',this.selection ? this.selection.value : null);
7031 		this.fireProperty('kind',this.selection ? this.selection.kind : null);
7032 		for (var i=0; i < this.subItems.length; i++) {
7033 			this.subItems[i].parentValueChanged();
7034 		};
7035 	},
7036 	/** @private */
7037 	registerItems : function(items) {
7038 		items.parent = this;
7039 		this.subItems.push(items);
7040 	},
7041 	/** @private */
7042 	registerItem : function(id,title,icon,badge,value,kind) {
7043 		var element = n2i.get(id);
7044 		var item = {id:id,title:title,icon:icon,badge:badge,element:element,value:value,kind:kind};
7045 		this.items.push(item);
7046 		this.addItemBehavior(element,item);
7047 		this.selection = this.getSelectionWithValue(this.options.value);
7048 	},
7049 	/** @private */
7050 	addItemBehavior : function(node,item) {
7051 		n2i.listen(node,'click',function() {
7052 			this.itemWasClicked(item);
7053 		}.bind(this));
7054 		n2i.listen(node,'dblclick',function() {
7055 			this.itemWasDoubleClicked(item);
7056 		}.bind(this));
7057 		node.dragDropInfo = item;
7058 	},
7059 	/** Untested!! */
7060 	setObjects : function(items) {
7061 		this.items = [];
7062 		items.each(function(item) {
7063 			this.items.push(item);
7064 			var node = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_selection_item'});
7065 			item.element = node;
7066 			this.element.insert(node);
7067 			var inner = new Element('span',{'class':'in2igui_selection_label'}).update(item.title);
7068 			if (item.icon) {
7069 				node.insert(In2iGui.createIcon(item.icon,1));
7070 			}
7071 			node.insert(inner);
7072 			node.observe('click',function() {
7073 				this.itemWasClicked(item);
7074 			}.bind(this));
7075 			node.observe('dblclick',function(e) {
7076 				this.itemWasDoubleClicked(item);
7077 				e.stop();
7078 			}.bind(this));
7079 		}.bind(this));
7080 	},
7081 	/** @private */
7082 	isSelection : function(item) {
7083 		if (this.selection===null) {
7084 			return false;
7085 		}
7086 		var selected = item.value==this.selection.value;
7087 		if (this.selection.kind) {
7088 			selected = selected && item.kind==this.selection.kind;
7089 		}
7090 		return selected;
7091 	},
7092 	
7093 	/** @private */
7094 	itemWasClicked : function(item) {
7095 		this.changeSelection(item);
7096 	},
7097 	/** @private */
7098 	itemWasDoubleClicked : function(item) {
7099 		this.fire('selectionWasOpened',item);
7100 	}
7101 }
7102 
7103 /////////////////////////// Items ///////////////////////////
7104 
7105 /**
7106  * @constructor
7107  * A group of items loaded from a source
7108  * @param {Object} options The options : {element,name,source}
7109  */
7110 In2iGui.Selection.Items = function(options) {
7111 	this.options = n2i.override({source:null},options);
7112 	this.element = n2i.get(options.element);
7113 	this.title = n2i.get(this.element.id+'_title');
7114 	this.name = options.name;
7115 	this.parent = null;
7116 	this.items = [];
7117 	In2iGui.extend(this);
7118 	if (this.options.source) {
7119 		this.options.source.listen(this);
7120 	}
7121 }
7122 
7123 In2iGui.Selection.Items.prototype = {
7124 	/**
7125 	 * Refresh the underlying source
7126 	 */
7127 	refresh : function() {
7128 		if (this.options.source) {
7129 			this.options.source.refresh();
7130 		}
7131 	},
7132 	/** @private */
7133 	$objectsLoaded : function(objects) {
7134 		this.$itemsLoaded(objects);
7135 	},
7136 	/** @private */
7137 	$itemsLoaded : function(items) {
7138 		this.items = [];
7139 		this.element.innerHTML='';
7140 		this.buildLevel(this.element,items,0);
7141 		if (this.title) {
7142 			this.title.style.display=this.items.length>0 ? 'block' : 'none';
7143 		}
7144 		this.parent.updateUI();
7145 	},
7146 	/** @private */
7147 	buildLevel : function(parent,items,inc) {
7148 		if (!items) return;
7149 		var hierarchical = this.isHierarchy(items);
7150 		var open = inc==0;
7151 		var level = n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_selection_level',style:(open ? 'display:block' : 'display:none'),parent:parent});
7152 		n2i.each(items,function(item) {
7153 			if (item.type=='title') {
7154 				var div = n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_selection_title',html:'<span>'+item.title+'</span>',parent:level});
7155 				return;
7156 			}
7157 			var hasChildren = item.children && item.children.length>0;
7158 			var left = inc*16+6;
7159 			if (!hierarchical && inc>0 || hierarchical && !hasChildren) left+=13;
7160 			var node = n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_selection_item'});
7161 			node.style.paddingLeft = left+'px';
7162 			if (item.badge) {
7163 				node.appendChild(n2i.build('strong',{'class':'in2igui_selection_badge',text:item.badge}));
7164 			}
7165 			if (hierarchical && hasChildren) {
7166 				var self = this;
7167 				var x = n2i.build('span',{'class':'in2igui_disclosure',parent:node});
7168 				n2i.listen(x,'click',function(e) {
7169 					n2i.stop(e);
7170 					self.toggle(x);
7171 				});
7172 			}
7173 			var inner = n2i.build('span',{'class':'in2igui_selection_label',text:item.title});
7174 			if (item.icon) {
7175 				node.appendChild(n2i.build('span',{'class':'in2igui_icon_1',style:'background-image: url('+In2iGui.getIconUrl(item.icon,1)+')'}));
7176 			}
7177 			node.appendChild(inner);
7178 			n2i.listen(node,'click',function(e) {
7179 				this.parent.itemWasClicked(item);
7180 			}.bind(this));
7181 			n2i.listen(node,'dblclick',function(e) {
7182 				this.parent.itemWasDoubleClicked(item);
7183 			}.bind(this));
7184 			level.appendChild(node);
7185 			var info = {title:item.title,icon:item.icon,badge:item.badge,kind:item.kind,element:node,value:item.value};
7186 			node.dragDropInfo = info;
7187 			this.items.push(info);
7188 			this.buildLevel(level,item.children,inc+1);
7189 		}.bind(this));
7190 	},
7191 	/** @private */
7192 	toggle : function(node) {
7193 		if (n2i.hasClass(node,'in2igui_disclosure_open')) {
7194 			n2i.getNext(node.parentNode).style.display='none';
7195 			n2i.removeClass(node,'in2igui_disclosure_open');
7196 		} else {
7197 			n2i.getNext(node.parentNode).style.display='block';
7198 			n2i.addClass(node,'in2igui_disclosure_open');
7199 		}
7200 	},
7201 	/** @private */
7202 	isHierarchy : function(items) {
7203 		if (!items) {return false};
7204 		for (var i=0; i < items.length; i++) {
7205 			if (items[i]!==null && items[i].children && items[i].children.length>0) {
7206 				return true;
7207 			}
7208 		};
7209 		return false;
7210 	},
7211 	/** Get the selection of this items group
7212 	 * @returns {Object} The selected item or null */
7213 	getValue : function() {
7214 		if (this.parent.selection==null) {
7215 			return null;
7216 		}
7217 		for (var i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
7218 			if (this.items[i].value == this.parent.selection.value) {
7219 				return this.items[i];
7220 			}
7221 		};
7222 		return null;
7223 	},
7224 	/** @private */
7225 	updateUI : function() {
7226 		for (var i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
7227 			n2i.setClass(this.items[i].element,'in2igui_selected',this.parent.isSelection(this.items[i]));
7228 		};
7229 	},
7230 	/** @private */
7231 	selectionChanged : function(oldSelection,newSelection) {
7232 		for (var i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
7233 			var value = this.items[i].value;
7234 			if (value == newSelection.value) {
7235 				this.fireProperty('value',newSelection.value);
7236 				return;
7237 			}
7238 		};
7239 		this.fireProperty('value',null);
7240 	},
7241 	/**
7242 	 * Called when the parent changes value, must fire its new value
7243 	 * @private
7244 	 */
7245 	parentValueChanged : function() {
7246 		for (var i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
7247 			if (this.parent.isSelection(this.items[i])) {
7248 				this.fireProperty('value',this.items[i].value);
7249 				return;
7250 			}
7251 		};
7252 		this.fireProperty('value',null);
7253 	}
7254 }

7261 }

7359 			self.wasClicked();
7360 		}
7361 	},
7362 	/** Sets wether the icon should be enabled */

7364 		this.enabled = enabled;
7365 		this.element.tabIndex=enabled ? 0 : -1;

7367 	},

7375 	},

7386 					text:this.options.confirm.text,
7387 					okText:this.options.confirm.okText,
7388 					cancelText:this.options.confirm.cancelText,
7389 					onOk:this.fireClick.bind(this)
7390 				});
7391 			} else {
7392 				this.fireClick();
7393 			}
7394 		}
7395 	},
7396 	/** @private */
7397 	fireClick : function() {
7398 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'toolbarIconWasClicked');
7399 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'click');
7400 	}
7401 }

7479 In2iGui.ImagePicker = function(o) {

7481 	this.options = o || {};
7482 	this.element = n2i.get(o.element);
7483 	this.images = [];

7485 	this.thumbnailsLoaded = false;
7486 	In2iGui.extend(this);
7487 	this.addBehavior();
7488 }
7489 
7490 In2iGui.ImagePicker.prototype = {
7491 	/** @private */
7492 	addBehavior : function() {
7493 		this.element.onclick = this.showPicker.bind(this);
7494 	},
7495 	setObject : function(obj) {
7496 		this.object = obj;
7497 		this.updateUI();
7498 	},
7499 	getObject : function() {
7500 		return this.object;
7501 	},
7502 	reset : function() {
7503 		this.object = null;
7504 		this.updateUI();
7505 	},
7506 	/** @private */
7507 	updateUI : function() {
7508 		if (this.object==null) {
7509 			this.element.style.backgroundImage='';
7510 		} else {
7511 			var url = In2iGui.resolveImageUrl(this,this.object,48,48);
7512 			this.element.style.backgroundImage='url('+url+')';
7513 		}
7514 	},
7515 	/** @private */
7516 	showPicker : function() {
7517 		if (!this.picker) {
7518 			var self = this;
7519 			this.picker = In2iGui.BoundPanel.create();
7520 			this.content = n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_imagepicker_thumbs'});
7521 			var buttons = In2iGui.Buttons.create({align:'right'});
7522 			var close = In2iGui.Button.create({text:'Luk',highlighted:true});
7523 			close.listen({
7524 				$click:function() {self.hidePicker()}
7525 			});
7526 			var remove = In2iGui.Button.create({text:'Fjern'});
7527 			remove.listen({
7528 				$click:function() {self.setObject(null);self.hidePicker()}
7529 			});
7530 			buttons.add(remove).add(close);
7531 			this.picker.add(this.content);
7532 			this.picker.add(buttons);
7533 		}
7534 		this.picker.position(this.element);
7535 		this.picker.show();
7536 		if (!this.thumbnailsLoaded) {
7537 			this.updateImages();
7538 			this.thumbnailsLoaded = true;
7539 		}
7540 	},
7541 	/** @private */
7542 	hidePicker : function() {
7543 		this.picker.hide();
7544 	},
7545 	/** @private */
7546 	updateImages : function() {
7547 		var self = this;
7548 		n2i.request({
7549 			onSuccess:function(t) {
7550 				self.parse(t.responseXML);
7551 			},
7552 			url:this.options.source
7553 		});
7554 	},
7555 	/** @private */
7556 	parse : function(doc) {
7557 		this.content.innerHTML='';
7558 		var images = doc.getElementsByTagName('image');
7559 		var self = this;
7560 		for (var i=0; i < images.length; i++) {
7561 			var id = images[i].getAttribute('id');
7562 			var img = {id:images[i].getAttribute('id')};
7563 			var url = In2iGui.resolveImageUrl(this,img,48,48);
7564 			var thumb = n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_imagepicker_thumbnail',style:'background-image:url('+url+')'});
7565 			thumb.in2iguiObject = {'id':id};
7566 			thumb.onclick = function() {
7567 				self.setObject(this.in2iguiObject);
7568 				self.hidePicker();
7569 			}
7570 			this.content.appendChild(thumb);
7571 		};
7572 	}
7573 }

7580 In2iGui.BoundPanel = function(options) {

7589 /**
7590  * Creates a new bound panel
7591  * <br/><strong>options:</strong> { name: String, top: pixels, left: pixels, padding: pixels, width: pixels }
7592  * @param {Object} options The options
7593  */
7594 In2iGui.BoundPanel.create = function(options) {
7595 	var options = n2i.override({name:null, top:0, left:0, width:null, padding: null}, options);
7596 
7597 	
7598 	var html = 
7599 		'<div class="in2igui_boundpanel_arrow"></div>'+
7600 		'<div class="in2igui_boundpanel_top"><div><div></div></div></div>'+
7601 		'<div class="in2igui_boundpanel_body"><div class="in2igui_boundpanel_body"><div class="in2igui_boundpanel_body"><div class="in2igui_boundpanel_content" style="';
7602 	if (options.width) {
7603 		html+='width:'+options.width+'px;';
7604 	}
7605 	if (options.padding) {
7606 		html+='padding:'+options.padding+'px;';
7607 	}
7608 	html+='"></div></div></div></div>'+
7609 		'<div class="in2igui_boundpanel_bottom"><div><div></div></div></div>';
7610 
7611 	options.element = n2i.build(
7612 		'div',{
7613 			'class':'in2igui_boundpanel',
7614 			style:'display:none;zIndex:'+In2iGui.nextPanelIndex()+';top:'+options.top+'px;left:'+options.left+'px',
7615 			html:html,
7616 			parent:document.body
7617 		}
7618 	);
7619 	return new In2iGui.BoundPanel(options);
7620 }

7623 
7624 In2iGui.BoundPanel.prototype = {
7625 	/** Shows the panel */
7626 	show : function() {
7627 		if (!this.visible) {
7628 			if (!n2i.browser.msie) {
7629 				n2i.setOpacity(this.element,0);
7630 			}
7631 			if (this.relativePosition=='left') {
7632 				this.element.style.marginLeft='30px';
7633 			} else {
7634 				this.element.style.marginLeft='-30px';
7635 			}
7636 			n2i.setStyle(this.element,{
7637 				visibility : 'hidden', display : 'block'
7638 			})
7639 			var width = this.element.clientWidth;
7640 			n2i.setStyle(this.element,{
7641 				width : width+'px' , visibility : 'visible'
7642 			});
7643 			this.element.style.marginTop='0px';
7644 			this.element.style.display='block';
7645 			if (!n2i.browser.msie) {
7646 				n2i.animate(this.element,'opacity',1,400,{ease:n2i.ease.fastSlow});
7647 			}
7648 			n2i.animate(this.element,'margin-left','0px',800,{ease:n2i.ease.bounce});
7649 		}
7650 		this.element.style.zIndex = In2iGui.nextPanelIndex();
7651 		this.visible=true;
7652 	},
7653 	/** Hides the panel */
7654 	hide : function() {
7655 		if (n2i.browser.msie) {
7656 			this.element.style.display='none';
7657 		} else {
7658 			n2i.animate(this.element,'opacity',0,300,{ease:n2i.ease.slowFast,hideOnComplete:true});
7659 		}
7660 		this.visible=false;
7661 	},
7662 	/**
7663 	 * Adds a widget or element to the panel
7664 	 * @param {Node | Widget} child The object to add
7665 	 */
7666 	add : function(child) {
7667 		if (child.getElement) {
7668 			this.content.appendChild(child.getElement());
7669 		} else {
7670 			this.content.appendChild(child);
7671 		}
7672 	},
7673 	/**
7674 	 * Adds som vertical space to the panel
7675 	 * @param {pixels} height The height of the space in pixels
7676 	 */
7677 	addSpace : function(height) {
7678 		this.add(n2i.build('div',{style:'font-size:0px;height:'+height+'px'}));
7679 	},
7680 	/** @private */
7681 	getDimensions : function() {
7682 		if (this.element.style.display=='none') {
7683 			this.element.style.visibility='hidden';
7684 			this.element.style.display='block';
7685 			var width = this.element.clientWidth;
7686 			var height = this.element.clientHeight;
7687 			this.element.style.display='none';
7688 			this.element.style.visibility='';
7689 		} else {
7690 			var width = this.element.clientWidth;
7691 			var height = this.element.clientHeight;
7692 		}
7693 		return {width:width,height:height};
7694 	},
7695 	/** Position the panel at a node
7696 	 * @param {Node} node The node the panel should be positioned at 
7697 	 */
7698 	position : function(node) {
7699 		node = n2i.get(node);
7700 		var offset = {left:n2i.getLeft(node),top:n2i.getTop(node)};
7701 		var scrollOffset = {left:n2i.getScrollLeft(),top:n2i.getScrollTop()};
7702 		var dims = this.getDimensions();
7703 		var winWidth = n2i.getInnerWidth();
7704 		var nodeLeft = offset.left-scrollOffset.left+n2i.getScrollLeft();
7705 		var nodeWidth = node.clientWidth;
7706 		var nodeHeight = node.clientHeight;
7707 		var nodeTop = offset.top-scrollOffset.top+n2i.getScrollTop();
7708 		if ((nodeLeft+nodeWidth/2)/winWidth<.5) {
7709 			this.relativePosition='left';
7710 			var left = nodeLeft+nodeWidth+10;
7711 			this.arrow.className='in2igui_boundpanel_arrow in2igui_boundpanel_arrow_left';
7712 			var arrowLeft=-14;
7713 		} else {
7714 			this.relativePosition='right';
7715 			var left = nodeLeft-dims.width-10;
7716 			this.arrow.className='in2igui_boundpanel_arrow in2igui_boundpanel_arrow_right';
7717 			var arrowLeft=dims.width-4;
7718 		}
7719 		var top = Math.max(0,nodeTop+(nodeHeight-dims.height)/2);
7720 		this.arrow.style.marginTop = (dims.height-32)/2+Math.min(0,nodeTop+(nodeHeight-dims.height)/2)+'px';
7721 		this.arrow.style.marginLeft = arrowLeft+'px';
7722 		if (this.visible) {
7723 			n2i.animate(this.element,'top',top+'px',500,{ease:n2i.ease.fastSlow});
7724 			n2i.animate(this.element,'left',left+'px',500,{ease:n2i.ease.fastSlow});
7725 		} else {
7726 			this.element.style.top=top+'px';
7727 			this.element.style.left=left+'px';
7728 		}
7729 	}
7730 }

7778 In2iGui.RichText.replaceInput = function(options) {
7779 	options = options || {};
7780 	var input = $(options.input);
7781 	input.style.display='none';
7782 	options.value = input.value;
7783 	var obj = In2iGui.RichText.create(options);
7784 	input.parentNode.insertBefore(obj.element,input);
7785 	obj.ignite();
7786 }

7796 In2iGui.RichText.prototype = {
7797 	isCompatible : function() {
7798 	    var agt=navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase();
7799 		return true;
7800 		return (agt.indexOf('msie 6')>-1 || agt.indexOf('msie 7')>-1 || (agt.indexOf('gecko')>-1 && agt.indexOf('safari')<0));
7801 	},
7802 	ignite : function() {
7803 		var self = this;
7804 		this.editor.observe("wysihat:loaded", function(event) {
7805 			if (this.ignited) {
7806 				return;
7807 			}
7808 			this.editor.setStyle(this.options.style);
7809 			this.editor.setRawContent(this.value);
7810 			this.document = this.editor.getDocument();
7811 			if (this.document.body) {
7812 				this.document.body.style.minHeight='100%';
7813 				this.document.body.style.margin='0';
7814 				this.document.documentElement.style.cursor='text';
7815 				this.document.documentElement.style.minHeight='100%';
7816 				Element.setStyle(this.document.body,this.options.style);
7817 			}
7818 			this.window = this.editor.getWindow();
7819 			Event.observe(this.window,'focus',function() {self.documentFocused()});
7820 			Event.observe(this.window,'blur',function() {self.documentBlurred()});
7821 			this.document.body.focus();
7822 			this.ignited = true;
7823      	}.bind(this));
7824 		this.editor.observe("wysihat:change", function(event) {
7825         	this.documentChanged();
7826      	}.bind(this));
7827 	},
7828 	setHeight : function(height) {
7829 		this.editor.style.height=height+'px';
7830 	},
7831 	focus : function() {
7832 		try { // TODO : May only work in gecko
7833 			var r = this.document.createRange();
7834 			r.selectNodeContents(this.document.body);
7835 			this.window.getSelection().addRange(r);
7836 		} catch (ignore) {}
7837 		if (this.window)this.window.focus();
7838 	},
7839 	setValue : function(value) {
7840 		this.value = value;
7841 		this.editor.setRawContent(this.value);
7842 	},
7843 	getValue : function() {
7844 		return this.value;
7845 	},
7846 	deactivate : function() {
7847 		if (this.colorPicker) this.colorPicker.hide();
7848 		if (this.toolbar) this.toolbar.style.display='none';
7849 	},
7850 	
7851 	buildToolbar : function() {
7852 		this.toolbar.onmousedown = function() {this.toolbarMouseDown=true}.bind(this);
7853 		this.toolbar.onmouseup = function() {this.toolbarMouseDown=false}.bind(this);
7854 		var self = this;
7855 		var actions = In2iGui.RichText.actions;
7856 		for (var i=0; i < actions.length; i++) {
7857 			if (actions[i]==null) {
7858 				this.toolbarContent.insert(new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_richtext_divider'}));
7859 			} else {
7860 				var div = new Element('div').addClassName('action action_'+actions[i].key);
7861 				div.title=actions[i].key;
7862 				div.in2iguiRichTextAction = actions[i]
7863 				div.onclick = div.ondblclick = function(e) {return self.actionWasClicked(this.in2iguiRichTextAction,e);}
7864 				var img = new Element('img');
7865 				img.src=In2iGui.context+'/In2iGui/gfx/trans.png';
7866 				if (actions[i].icon) {
7867 					div.setStyle({'backgroundImage':'url('+In2iGui.getIconUrl(actions[i].icon,1)+')'});
7868 				}
7869 				div.insert(img);
7870 				this.toolbarContent.appendChild(div);
7871 				div.onmousedown = In2iGui.RichText.stopEvent;
7872 			}
7873 		};
7874 	},
7875 	documentFocused : function() {
7876 		if (n2i.browser.msie) {
7877 			this.toolbar.style.display='block';
7878 			return;
7879 		}
7880 		if (this.toolbar.style.display!='block') {
7881 			this.toolbar.style.marginTop='-40px';
7882 			n2i.setOpacity(this.toolbar,0);
7883 			this.toolbar.style.display='block';
7884 			n2i.ani(this.toolbar,'opacity',1,300);
7885 			n2i.ani(this.toolbar,'margin-top','-32px',300);
7886 		}
7887 	},
7888 	
7889 	documentBlurred : function() {
7890 		if (this.toolbarMouseDown) return;
7891 		if (this.options.autoHideToolbar) {
7892 			if (n2i.browser.msie) {
7893 				var self = this;
7894 				window.setTimeout(function() {
7895 					self.toolbar.style.display='none';
7896 				},100);
7897 				return;
7898 			}
7899 			n2i.ani(this.toolbar,'opacity',0,300,{hideOnComplete:true});
7900 			n2i.ani(this.toolbar,'margin-top','-40px',300);
7901 		}
7902 		this.documentChanged();
7903 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'richTextDidChange');
7904 	},
7905 	
7906 	documentChanged : function() {
7907 		this.value = this.editor.content();
7908 		if (this.options.input) {
7909 			$(this.options.input).value=this.value;
7910 		}
7911 	},
7912 	
7913 	disabler : function(e) {
7914 		var evt = e ? e : window.event; 
7915 		if (evt.returnValue) {
7916 			evt.returnValue = false;
7917 		} else if (evt.preventDefault) {
7918 			evt.preventDefault( );
7919 		}
7920 		return false;
7921 	},
7922 	actionWasClicked : function(action,e) {
7923 		In2iGui.RichText.stopEvent(e);
7924 		if (action.key=='color') {
7925 			this.showColorPicker();
7926 		} else {
7927 			this.execCommand(action);
7928 		}
7929 		this.document.body.focus();
7930 		return false;
7931 	},
7932 	execCommand : function(action) {
7933 		this.editor.execCommand(action.cmd,false,action.value);
7934 		this.documentChanged();
7935 	},
7936 	showColorPicker : function() {
7937 		if (!this.colorPicker) {
7938 			var panel = In2iGui.Window.create({variant:'dark'});
7939 			var picker = In2iGui.ColorPicker.create();
7940 			picker.listen(this);
7941 			panel.add(picker);
7942 			panel.show();
7943 			this.colorPicker = panel;
7944 		}
7945 		this.colorPicker.show();
7946 	},
7947 	$colorWasHovered : function(color) {
7948 		//this.document.execCommand('forecolor',false,color);
7949 	},
7950 	$colorWasSelected : function(color) {
7951 		this.document.execCommand('forecolor',false,color);
7952 		this.documentChanged();
7953 	}
7954 }

7961     evt.returnValue = false;
7962   } else if (evt.preventDefault) {

8036 			self.playOrPause();
8037 		}
8038 		this.closeControl.onclick = this.hide.bind(this);
8039 		n2i.listen(this.viewer,'click',this.zoom.bind(this));
8040 		this.timer = function() {
8041 			self.next(false);
8042 		}
8043 		this.keyListener = function(e) {
8044 			e = n2i.event(e);
8045 			if (e.rightKey) {
8046 				self.next(true);
8047 			} else if (e.leftKey) {
8048 				self.previous(true);
8049 			} else if (e.escapeKey) {
8050 				self.hide();
8051 			} else if (e.returnKey) {
8052 				self.playOrPause();
8053 			}
8054 		},
8055 		n2i.listen(this.viewer,'mousemove',this.mouseMoveEvent.bind(this));
8056 		n2i.listen(this.controller,'mouseenter',function() {
8057 			self.overController = true;
8058 		});
8059 		n2i.listen(this.controller,'mouseleave',function() {
8060 			self.overController = false;
8061 		});
8062 		n2i.listen(this.viewer,'mouseout',function(e) {
8063 			if (!In2iGui.isWithin(e,this.viewer)) {
8064 				self.hideController();
8065 			}
8066 		}.bind(this));
8067 	},
8068 	/** @private */
8069 	mouseMoveEvent : function() {
8070 		window.clearTimeout(this.ctrlHider);
8071 		if (this.shouldShowController()) {
8072 			this.ctrlHider = window.setTimeout(this.hideController.bind(this),2000);
8073 			if (n2i.browser.msie) {
8074 				this.controller.show();
8075 			} else {
8076 				In2iGui.fadeIn(this.controller,200);
8077 			}
8078 		}
8079 	},
8080 	/** @private */
8081 	hideController : function() {
8082 		if (!this.overController) {
8083 			if (n2i.browser.msie) {
8084 				this.controller.hide();
8085 			} else {
8086 				In2iGui.fadeOut(this.controller,500);
8087 			}
8088 		}
8089 	},
8090 	/** @private */
8091 	zoom : function(e) {
8092 		var img = this.images[this.index];
8093 		if (img.width<=this.width && img.height<=this.height) {
8094 			return; // Don't zoom if small
8095 		}
8096 		if (!this.zoomer) {
8097 			this.zoomer = n2i.build('div',{
8098 				'class' : 'in2igui_imageviewer_zoomer',
8099 				style : 'width:'+this.viewer.clientWidth+'px;height:'+this.viewer.clientHeight+'px'
8100 			});
8101 			this.element.insertBefore(this.zoomer,n2i.firstByTag(this.element,'*'));
8102 			n2i.listen(this.zoomer,'mousemove',this.zoomMove.bind(this));
8103 			n2i.listen(this.zoomer,'click',function() {
8104 				this.style.display='none';
8105 			});
8106 		}
8107 		this.pause();
8108 		var size = this.getLargestSize({width:2000,height:2000},img);
8109 		var url = In2iGui.resolveImageUrl(this,img,size.width,size.height);
8110 		this.zoomer.innerHTML = '<div style="width:'+size.width+'px;height:'+size.height+'px;"><img src="'+url+'"/></div>';
8111 		this.zoomer.style.display = 'block';
8112 		this.zoomInfo = {width:size.width,height:size.height};
8113 		this.zoomMove(e);
8114 	},
8115 	zoomMove : function(e) {
8116 		e = new n2i.Event(e);
8117 		if (!this.zoomInfo) {
8118 			return;
8119 		}
8120 		var offset = {left:n2i.getLeft(this.zoomer),top:n2i.getTop(this.zoomer)};
8121 		var x = (e.left()-offset.left)/this.zoomer.clientWidth*(this.zoomInfo.width-this.zoomer.clientWidth);
8122 		var y = (e.top()-offset.top)/this.zoomer.clientHeight*(this.zoomInfo.height-this.zoomer.clientHeight);
8123 		this.zoomer.scrollLeft = x;
8124 		this.zoomer.scrollTop = y;
8125 	},
8126 	/** @private */
8127 	getLargestSize : function(canvas,image) {
8128 		if (image.width<=canvas.width && image.height<=canvas.height) {
8129 			return {width:image.width,height:image.height};
8130 		} else if (canvas.width/canvas.height>image.width/image.height) {
8131 			return {width:Math.round(canvas.height/image.height*image.width),height:canvas.height};
8132 		} else if (canvas.width/canvas.height<image.width/image.height) {
8133 			return {width:canvas.width,height:Math.round(canvas.width/image.width*image.height)};
8134 		} else {
8135 			return {width:canvas.width,height:canvas.height};
8136 		}
8137 	},
8138 	/** @private */
8139 	calculateSize : function() {
8140 		var snap = this.options.sizeSnap;
8141 		var newWidth = n2i.getInnerWidth()-this.options.perimeter;
8142 		newWidth = Math.floor(newWidth/snap)*snap;
8143 		newWidth = Math.min(newWidth,this.options.maxWidth);
8144 		var newHeight = n2i.getInnerHeight()-this.options.perimeter;
8145 		newHeight = Math.floor(newHeight/snap)*snap;
8146 		newHeight = Math.min(newHeight,this.options.maxHeight);
8147 		var maxWidth = 0;
8148 		var maxHeight = 0;
8149 		for (var i=0; i < this.images.length; i++) {
8150 			var dims = this.getLargestSize({width:newWidth,height:newHeight},this.images[i]);
8151 			maxWidth = Math.max(maxWidth,dims.width);
8152 			maxHeight = Math.max(maxHeight,dims.height);
8153 		};
8154 		newHeight = Math.floor(Math.min(newHeight,maxHeight));
8155 		newWidth = Math.floor(Math.min(newWidth,maxWidth));
8156 		
8157 		if (newWidth!=this.width || newHeight!=this.height) {
8158 			this.width = newWidth;
8159 			this.height = newHeight;
8160 			this.dirty = true;
8161 		}
8162 	},
8163 	adjustSize : function() {
8164 		
8165 	},
8166 	showById: function(id) {
8167 		for (var i=0; i < this.images.length; i++) {
8168 			if (this.images[i].id==id) {
8169 				this.show(i);
8170 				break;
8171 			}
8172 		};
8173 	},
8174 	show: function(index) {
8175 		this.index = index || 0;
8176 		this.calculateSize();
8177 		this.updateUI();
8178 		var margin = this.options.margin;
8179 		n2i.setStyle(this.element, {width:(this.width+margin)+'px',height:(this.height+margin*2-1)+'px'});
8180 		n2i.setStyle(this.viewer, {width:(this.width+margin)+'px',height:(this.height-1)+'px'});
8181 		n2i.setStyle(this.innerViewer, {width:((this.width+margin)*this.images.length)+'px',height:(this.height-1)+'px'});
8182 		n2i.setStyle(this.controller, {marginLeft:((this.width-180)/2+margin*0.5)+'px',display:'none'});
8183 		this.box.show();
8184 		this.goToImage(false,0,false);
8185 		n2i.listen(document,'keydown',this.keyListener);
8186 	},
8187 	hide: function(index) {
8188 		this.pause();
8189 		this.box.hide();
8190 		n2i.unListen(document,'keydown',this.keyListener);
8191 	},
8192 	/** @private */
8193 	$boxCurtainWasClicked : function() {
8194 		this.hide();
8195 	},
8196 	/** @private */
8197 	$boxWasClosed : function() {
8198 		this.hide();
8199 	},
8200 	/** @private */
8201 	updateUI : function() {
8202 		if (this.dirty) {
8203 			this.innerViewer.innerHTML='';
8204 			for (var i=0; i < this.images.length; i++) {
8205 				var element = n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_imageviewer_image'});
8206 				n2i.setStyle(element,{'width':(this.width+this.options.margin)+'px','height':(this.height-1)+'px'});
8207 				this.innerViewer.appendChild(element);
8208 			};
8209 			if (this.shouldShowController()) {
8210 				this.controller.style.display='block';
8211 			} else {
8212 				this.controller.style.display='none';
8213 			}
8214 			this.dirty = false;
8215 			this.preload();
8216 		}
8217 	},
8218 	/** @private */
8219 	shouldShowController : function() {
8220 		return this.images.length>1;
8221 	},
8222 	/** @private */
8223 	goToImage : function(animate,num,user) {	
8224 		if (animate) {
8225 			if (num>1) {
8226 				n2i.ani(this.viewer,'scrollLeft',this.index*(this.width+this.options.margin),Math.min(num*this.options.transitionReturn,2000),{ease:this.options.easeReturn});				
8227 			} else {
8228 				var end = this.index==0 || this.index==this.images.length-1;
8229 				var ease = (end ? this.options.easeEnd : this.options.ease);
8230 				if (!user) {
8231 					ease = this.options.easeAuto;
8232 				}
8233 				n2i.ani(this.viewer,'scrollLeft',this.index*(this.width+this.options.margin),(end ? this.options.transitionEnd : this.options.transition),{ease:ease});
8234 			}
8235 		} else {
8236 			this.viewer.scrollLeft=this.index*(this.width+this.options.margin);
8237 		}
8238 		var text = this.images[this.index].text;
8239 		if (text) {
8240 			this.text.innerHTML=text;
8241 			this.text.style.display='block';
8242 		} else {
8243 			this.text.innerHTML='';
8244 			this.text.style.display='none';
8245 		}
8246 	},
8247 	clearImages : function() {
8248 		this.images = [];
8249 		this.dirty = true;
8250 	},
8251 	addImages : function(images) {
8252 		for (var i=0; i < images.length; i++) {
8253 			this.addImage(images[i]);
8254 		};
8255 	},
8256 	addImage : function(img) {
8257 		this.images.push(img);
8258 		this.dirty = true;
8259 	},
8260 	play : function() {
8261 		if (!this.interval) {
8262 			this.interval = window.setInterval(this.timer,6000);
8263 		}
8264 		this.next(false);
8265 		this.playing=true;
8266 		this.playControl.className='in2igui_imageviewer_pause';
8267 	},
8268 	pause : function() {
8269 		window.clearInterval(this.interval);
8270 		this.interval = null;
8271 		this.playControl.className='in2igui_imageviewer_play';
8272 		this.playing = false;
8273 	},
8274 	playOrPause : function() {
8275 		if (this.playing) {
8276 			this.pause();
8277 		} else {
8278 			this.play();
8279 		}
8280 	},
8281 	resetPlay : function() {
8282 		if (this.playing) {
8283 			window.clearInterval(this.interval);
8284 			this.interval = window.setInterval(this.timer,6000);
8285 		}
8286 	},
8287 	previous : function(user) {
8288 		var num = 1;
8289 		this.index--;
8290 		if (this.index<0) {
8291 			this.index=this.images.length-1;
8292 			num = this.images.length-1;
8293 		}
8294 		this.goToImage(true,num,user);
8295 		this.resetPlay();
8296 	},
8297 	next : function(user) {
8298 		var num = 1;
8299 		this.index++;
8300 		if (this.index==this.images.length) {
8301 			this.index=0;
8302 			num = this.images.length-1;
8303 		}
8304 		this.goToImage(true,num,user);
8305 		this.resetPlay();
8306 	},
8307 	/** @private */
8308 	preload : function() {
8309 		var guiLoader = new n2i.Preloader();
8310 		guiLoader.addImages(In2iGui.context+'In2iGui/gfx/imageviewer_controls.png');
8311 		var self = this;
8312 		guiLoader.setDelegate({allImagesDidLoad:function() {self.preloadImages()}});
8313 		guiLoader.load();
8314 	},
8315 	/** @private */
8316 	preloadImages : function() {
8317 		var loader = new n2i.Preloader();
8318 		loader.setDelegate(this);
8319 		for (var i=0; i < this.images.length; i++) {
8320 			var url = In2iGui.resolveImageUrl(this,this.images[i],this.width,this.height);
8321 			if (url!==null) {
8322 				loader.addImages(url);
8323 			}
8324 		};
8325 		this.status.innerHTML = '0%';
8326 		this.status.style.display='';
8327 		loader.load(this.index);
8328 	},
8329 	/** @private */
8330 	allImagesDidLoad : function() {
8331 		this.status.style.display='none';
8332 	},
8333 	/** @private */
8334 	imageDidLoad : function(loaded,total,index) {
8335 		this.status.innerHTML = Math.round(loaded/total*100)+'%';
8336 		var url = In2iGui.resolveImageUrl(this,this.images[index],this.width,this.height);
8337 		url = url.replace(/&/g,'&');
8338 		this.innerViewer.childNodes[index].style.backgroundImage="url('"+url+"')";
8339 		n2i.setClass(this.innerViewer.childNodes[index],'in2igui_imageviewer_image_abort',false);
8340 		n2i.setClass(this.innerViewer.childNodes[index],'in2igui_imageviewer_image_error',false);
8341 	},
8342 	/** @private */
8343 	imageDidGiveError : function(loaded,total,index) {
8344 		n2i.setClass(this.innerViewer.childNodes[index],'in2igui_imageviewer_image_error',true);
8345 	},
8346 	/** @private */
8347 	imageDidAbort : function(loaded,total,index) {
8348 		n2i.setClass(this.innerViewer.childNodes[index],'in2igui_imageviewer_image_abort',true);
8349 	}

8382 In2iGui.Picker.prototype = {
8383 	addBehavior : function() {
8384 		var self = this;
8385 		n2i.listen(this.content,'mousedown',function(e) {
8386 			self.startDrag(e);
8387 			return false;
8388 		});
8389 	},
8390 	setObjects : function(objects) {
8391 		this.selected = null;
8392 		this.objects = objects || [];
8393 		this.updateUI();
8394 	},
8395 	setValue : function(value) {
8396 		this.value = value;
8397 		this.updateSelection();
8398 	},
8399 	getValue : function() {
8400 		return this.value;
8401 	},
8402 	reset : function() {
8403 		this.value = null;
8404 		this.updateSelection();
8405 	},
8406 	updateUI : function() {
8407 		var self = this;
8408 		this.content.innerHTML='';
8409 		this.container.scrollLeft=0;
8410 		if (this.options.itemsVisible) {
8411 			var width = this.options.itemsVisible*(this.options.itemWidth+14);
8412 		} else {
8413 			var width = this.container.clientWidth;
8414 		}
8415 		n2i.setStyle(this.container,{width:width+'px',height:(this.options.itemHeight+10)+'px'});
8416 		this.content.style.width=(this.objects.length*(this.options.itemWidth+14))+'px';
8417 		this.content.style.height=(this.options.itemHeight+10)+'px';
8418 		n2i.each(this.objects,function(object,i) {
8419 			var item = n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_picker_item',title:object.title});
8420 			if (self.value!=null && object[self.options.valueProperty]==self.value) {
8421 				 n2i.addClass(item,'in2igui_picker_item_selected');
8422 			}
8423 			item.innerHTML = '<div class="in2igui_picker_item_middle"><div class="in2igui_picker_item_middle">'+
8424 				'<div style="width:'+self.options.itemWidth+'px;height:'+self.options.itemHeight+'px; overflow: hidden; background-image:url(\''+object.image+'\')"><strong>'+n2i.escape(object.title)+'</strong></div>'+
8425 				'</div></div>'+
8426 				'<div class="in2igui_picker_item_bottom"><div><div></div></div></div>';
8427 			n2i.listen(item,'mouseup',function() {
8428 				self.selectionChanged(object[self.options.valueProperty])
8429 			});
8430 			self.content.appendChild(item);
8431 		});
8432 	},

8436 			n2i.setClass(children[i],'in2igui_picker_item_selected',this.value!=null && this.objects[i][this.options.valueProperty]==this.value);
8437 		};
8438 	},
8439 	selectionChanged : function(value) {
8440 		if (this.dragging) return;
8441 		if (this.value==value) return;
8442 		this.value = value;
8443 		this.updateSelection();
8444 		this.fire('selectionChanged',value);
8445 	},
8446 	
8447 	// Dragging
8448 	startDrag : function(e) {
8449 		e = new n2i.Event(e);
8450 		e.stop();
8451 		var self = this;
8452 		this.dragX = e.left();
8453 		this.dragScroll = this.container.scrollLeft;
8454 		In2iGui.Picker.mousemove = function(e) {self.drag(e);return false;}
8455 		In2iGui.Picker.mouseup = In2iGui.Picker.mousedown = function(e) {self.endDrag(e);return false;}
8456 		n2i.listen(window.document,'mousemove',In2iGui.Picker.mousemove);
8457 		n2i.listen(window.document,'mouseup',In2iGui.Picker.mouseup);
8458 		n2i.listen(window.document,'mousedown',In2iGui.Picker.mouseup);

8462 		this.dragging = true;
8463 		e.stop();
8464 		this.container.scrollLeft=this.dragX-e.left()+this.dragScroll;
8465 	},
8466 	endDrag : function(e) {
8467 		this.dragging = false;
8468 		n2i.stop(e);
8469 		n2i.unListen(window.document,'mousemove',In2iGui.Picker.mousemove);
8470 		n2i.unListen(window.document,'mouseup',In2iGui.Picker.mouseup);
8471 		n2i.unListen(window.document,'mousedown',In2iGui.Picker.mouseup);
8472 		var size = this.options.itemWidth+14;
8473 		n2i.ani(this.container,'scrollLeft',Math.round(this.container.scrollLeft/size)*size,500,{ease:n2i.ease.bounceOut});
8474 	},
8475 	$visibilityChanged : function() {
8476 		this.container.style.display='none';
8477 		if (this.options.itemsVisible) {
8478 			var width = this.options.itemsVisible*(this.options.itemWidth+14);
8479 		} else {
8480 			var width = this.container.parentNode.clientWidth-12;
8481 		}
8482 		width = Math.max(width,0);
8483 		n2i.setStyle(this.container,{width:width+'px',display:'block'});

8509 In2iGui.Editor.prototype = {
8510 	ignite : function() {
8511 		this.reload();
8512 	},
8513 	addPartController : function(key,title,controller) {
8514 		this.partControllers.push({key:key,'title':title,'controller':controller});
8515 	},
8516 	setOptions : function(options) {

8518 	},
8519 	getPartController : function(key) {
8520 		var ctrl = null;
8521 		n2i.each(this.partControllers,function(item) {
8522 			if (item.key==key) {ctrl=item};
8523 		});
8524 		return ctrl;
8525 	},
8526 	reload : function() {
8527 		if (this.partControls) {
8528 			this.partControls.hide();
8529 		}
8530 		var self = this;
8531 		this.parts = [];
8532 		var rows = n2i.byClass(document.body,this.options.partClass);
8533 		n2i.each(rows,function(row,i) {
8534 			var columns = n2i.byClass(row,self.options.columnClass);

8536 			n2i.each(columns,function(column,j) {

8538 				self.reloadParts(parts,i,j);
8539 			});
8540 		});
8541 		var parts = n2i.byClass(document.body,this.options.partClass);
8542 		n2i.each(this.parts,function(part) {
8543 			var i = parts.indexOf(part.element);
8544 			if (i!=-1) {
8545 				delete(parts[i]);
8546 			}
8547 		});
8548 		this.reloadParts(parts,-1,-1);
8549 	},
8550 	partExists : function(element) {
8551 		
8552 	},
8553 	reloadColumns : function(columns,rowIndex) {
8554 		var self = this;
8555 		n2i.each(columns,function(column,columnIndex) {
8556 			n2i.lsiten(column,'mouseover',function() {
8557 				self.hoverColumn(column);
8558 			});
8559 			n2i.listen(column,'mouseout',function() {
8560 				self.blurColumn();
8561 			});
8562 			n2i.listen(column,'contextmenu',function(e) {
8563 				self.contextColumn(column,rowIndex,columnIndex,e);
8564 			});
8565 		});
8566 	},
8567 	reloadParts : function(parts,row,column) {
8568 		var self = this;
8569 		var reg = new RegExp(this.options.partClass+"_([\\w]+)","i");
8570 		n2i.each(parts,function(element,partIndex) {
8571 			if (!element) return;
8572 			var match = element.className.match(reg);
8573 			if (match && match[1]) {
8574 				var handler = self.getPartController(match[1]);
8575 				if (handler) {
8576 					var part = new handler.controller(element,row,column,partIndex);
8577 					part.type=match[1];
8578 					n2i.listen(element,'click',function() {
8579 						self.editPart(part);
8580 					});
8581 					n2i.listen(element,'mouseover',function(e) {
8582 						self.hoverPart(part);
8583 					});
8584 					n2i.listen(element,'mouseout',function(e) {
8585 						self.blurPart(e);
8586 					});
8587 					n2i.listen(element,'mousedown',function(e) {
8588 						self.startPartDrag(e);
8589 					});
8590 					self.parts.push(part);
8591 				}
8592 			}
8593 		});
8594 	},

8596 		this.active = true;
8597 	},
8598 	deactivate : function() {
8599 		this.active = false;
8600 		if (this.activePart) {
8601 			this.activePart.deactivate();
8602 		}
8603 		if (this.partControls) this.partControls.hide();
8604 	},

8906 In2iGui.Editor.startDrag = function(e,element) {
8907 	In2iGui.Editor.dragElement = element;
8908 	n2i.listen(document.body,'mousemove',In2iGui.Editor.dragListener);
8909 	n2i.listen(document.body,'mouseup',In2iGui.Editor.dragEndListener);
8910 	In2iGui.Editor.startDragPos = {top:e.pointerY(),left:e.pointerX()};
8911 	e.stop();
8912 	return false;
8913 }
8914 
8915 In2iGui.Editor.dragListener = function(e) {
8916 	var element = In2iGui.Editor.dragElement;
8917 	element.style.left = e.pointerX()+'px';
8918 	element.style.top = e.pointerY()+'px';
8919 	element.style.display='block';
8920 	return false;
8921 }
8922 
8923 In2iGui.Editor.dragEndListener = function(event) {
8924 	n2i.unListen(document.body,'mousemove',In2iGui.Editor.dragListener);
8925 	n2i.unListen(document.body,'mouseup',In2iGui.Editor.dragEndListener);
8926 	In2iGui.Editor.dragElement.style.display='none';
8927 	In2iGui.Editor.dragElement=null;
8928 }
8929 
8930 In2iGui.Editor.getPartId = function(element) {
8931 	var m = element.id.match(/part\-([\d]+)/i);
8932 	if (m && m.length>0) return m[1];
8933 }

8937 /**
8938  * @constructor
8939  */
8940 In2iGui.Editor.Header = function(element,row,column,position) {
8941 	this.element = $(element);
8942 	this.row = row;
8943 	this.column = column;
8944 	this.position = position;
8945 	this.id = In2iGui.Editor.getPartId(this.element);
8946 	this.header = this.element.firstDescendant();
8947 	this.field = null;
8948 }
8949 
8950 In2iGui.Editor.Header.prototype = {
8951 	activate : function() {
8952 		this.value = this.header.innerHTML;
8953 		this.field = n2i.build('textarea',{className:'in2igui_editor_header'});
8954 		this.field.value = this.value;
8955 		this.header.style.visibility='hidden';
8956 		this.updateFieldStyle();
8957 		this.element.insertBefore(this.field,this.header);
8958 		this.field.focus();
8959 		this.field.select();
8960 		n2i.listen(this.field,'keydown',function(e) {
8961 			if (e.keyCode==Event.KEY_RETURN) {
8962 				this.save();
8963 			}
8964 		}.bind(this));
8965 	},
8966 	save : function() {
8967 		var value = this.field.value;
8968 		this.header.innerHTML = value;
8969 		this.deactivate();
8970 		if (value!=this.value) {
8971 			this.value = value;
8972 			In2iGui.Editor.get().partChanged(this);
8973 		}
8974 	},
8975 	cancel : function() {
8976 		this.deactivate();
8977 	},
8978 	deactivate : function() {
8979 		this.header.style.visibility='';
8980 		this.element.removeChild(this.field);
8981 		In2iGui.Editor.get().partDidDeacivate(this);
8982 	},
8983 	updateFieldStyle : function() {
8984 		n2i.setStyle(this.field,{width:this.header.getWidth()+'px',height:this.header.getHeight()+'px'});
8985 		n2i.copyStyle(this.header,this.field,['fontSize','lineHeight','marginTop','fontWeight','fontFamily','textAlign','color','fontStyle']);
8986 	},
8987 	getValue : function() {
8988 		return this.value;
8989 	}
8990 }

8997 In2iGui.Editor.Html = function(element,row,column,position) {

8999 	this.row = row;
9000 	this.column = column;

9006 In2iGui.Editor.Html.prototype = {
9007 	activate : function() {
9008 		this.value = this.element.innerHTML;
9009 		//if (Prototype.Browser.IE) return;
9010 		var height = this.element.clientHeight;
9011 		this.element.innerHTML='';
9012 		var style = this.buildStyle();
9013 		this.editor = In2iGui.RichText.create({autoHideToolbar:false,style:style});
9014 		this.editor.setHeight(height);
9015 		this.element.appendChild(this.editor.getElement());
9016 		this.editor.listen(this);
9017 		this.editor.ignite();
9018 		this.editor.setValue(this.value);
9019 		this.editor.focus();
9020 	},
9021 	buildStyle : function() {
9022 		return {
9023 			'textAlign':n2i.getStyle(this.element,'text-align')
9024 			,'fontFamily':n2i.getStyle(this.element,'font-family')
9025 			,'fontSize':n2i.getStyle(this.element,'font-size')
9026 			,'fontWeight':n2i.getStyle(this.element,'font-weight')
9027 			,'color':n2i.getStyle(this.element,'color')
9028 		}
9029 	},
9030 	cancel : function() {
9031 		this.deactivate();
9032 		this.element.innerHTML = this.value;
9033 	},
9034 	save : function() {
9035 		this.deactivate();
9036 		var value = this.editor.value;
9037 		if (value!=this.value) {
9038 			this.value = value;
9039 			In2iGui.Editor.get().partChanged(this);
9040 		}
9041 		this.element.innerHTML = this.value;
9042 	},
9043 	deactivate : function() {
9044 		if (this.editor) {
9045 			this.editor.deactivate();
9046 			this.element.innerHTML = this.value;
9047 		}
9048 		In2iGui.Editor.get().partDidDeacivate(this);
9049 	},
9050 	richTextDidChange : function() {
9051 		//this.deactivate();
9052 	},
9053 	getValue : function() {
9054 		return this.value;
9055 	}
9056 }

9060  */
9061 In2iGui.Menu = function(options) {
9062 	this.options = n2i.override({autoHide:false,parentElement:null},options);
9063 	this.element = n2i.get(options.element);
9064 	this.name = options.name;
9065 	this.value = null;
9066 	this.subMenus = [];
9067 	this.visible = false;
9068 	In2iGui.extend(this);
9069 	this.addBehavior();
9070 }
9071 
9072 In2iGui.Menu.create = function(options) {
9073 	options = options || {};
9074 	options.element = n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_menu'});
9075 	var obj = new In2iGui.Menu(options);
9076 	document.body.appendChild(options.element);
9077 	return obj;
9078 }
9079 
9080 In2iGui.Menu.prototype = {
9081 	/** @private */
9082 	addBehavior : function() {
9083 		var self = this;
9084 		this.hider = function() {
9085 			self.hide();
9086 		}
9087 		if (this.options.autoHide) {
9088 			var x = function(e) {
9089 				if (!In2iGui.isWithin(e,self.element) && (!self.options.parentElement || !In2iGui.isWithin(e,self.options.parentElement))) {
9090 					if (!self.isSubMenuVisible()) {
9091 						self.hide();
9092 					}
9093 				}
9094 			};
9095 			n2i.listen(this.element,'mouseout',x);
9096 			if (this.options.parentElement) {
9097 				n2i.listen(this.options.parentElement,'mouseout',x);
9098 			}
9099 		}
9100 	},
9101 	addDivider : function() {
9102 		n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_menu_divider',parent:this.element});
9103 	},
9104 	addItem : function(item) {
9105 		var self = this;
9106 		var element = n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_menu_item',text:item.title});
9107 		n2i.listen(element,'click',function(e) {
9108 			n2i.stop(e);
9109 			self.itemWasClicked(item.value);
9110 		});
9111 		if (item.children) {
9112 			var sub = In2iGui.Menu.create({autoHide:true,parentElement:element});
9113 			sub.addItems(item.children);
9114 			n2i.listen(element,'mouseover',function(e) {
9115 				sub.showAtElement(element,e,'horizontal');
9116 			});
9117 			self.subMenus.push(sub);
9118 			n2i.addClass(element,'in2igui_menu_item_children');
9119 		}
9120 		this.element.appendChild(element);
9121 	},
9122 	addItems : function(items) {
9123 		for (var i=0; i < items.length; i++) {
9124 			if (items[i]==null) {
9125 				this.addDivider();
9126 			} else {
9127 				this.addItem(items[i]);
9128 			}
9129 		};
9130 	},
9131 	getValue : function() {
9132 		return this.value;
9133 	},
9134 	itemWasClicked : function(value) {
9135 		this.value = value;
9136 		this.fire('itemWasClicked',value);
9137 		this.fire('select',value);
9138 		this.hide();
9139 	},
9140 	showAtPointer : function(e) {
9141 		e = n2i.event(e);
9142 		e.stop();
9143 		this.showAtPoint({'top' : e.getTop(),'left' : e.getLeft()});
9144 	},
9145 	showAtElement : function(element,event,position) {
9146 		event = n2i.event(event);
9147 		event.stop();
9148 		element = n2i.get(element);
9149 		var point = n2i.getPosition(element);
9150 		if (position=='horizontal') {
9151 			point.left += element.clientWidth;
9152 		} else if (position=='vertical') {
9153 			point.top += element.clientHeight;
9154 		}
9155 		this.showAtPoint(point);
9156 	},
9157 	showAtPoint : function(pos) {
9158 		var innerWidth = n2i.getInnerWidth();
9159 		var innerHeight = n2i.getInnerHeight();
9160 		var scrollTop = n2i.getScrollTop();
9161 		var scrollLeft = n2i.getScrollLeft();
9162 		if (!this.visible) {
9163 			n2i.setStyle(this.element,{'display':'block','visibility':'hidden',opacity:0});
9164 		}
9165 		var width = this.element.clientWidth;
9166 		var height = this.element.clientHeight;
9167 		var left = Math.min(pos.left,innerWidth-width-20+scrollLeft);
9168 		var top = Math.max(0,Math.min(pos.top,innerHeight-height-20+scrollTop));
9169 		n2i.setStyle(this.element,{'top':top+'px','left':left+'px','visibility':'visible',zIndex:In2iGui.nextTopIndex(),'width':(width-2)+'px'});
9170 		if (!this.visible) {
9171 			n2i.setStyle(this.element,{opacity:1});
9172 			this.addHider();
9173 			this.visible = true;
9174 		}
9175 	},
9176 	hide : function() {
9177 		if (!this.visible) return;
9178 		var self = this;
9179 		n2i.animate(this.element,'opacity',0,200,{onComplete:function() {
9180 			self.element.style.display='none';
9181 		}});
9182 		this.removeHider();
9183 		for (var i=0; i < this.subMenus.length; i++) {
9184 			this.subMenus[i].hide();
9185 		};
9186 		this.visible = false;
9187 	},
9188 	isSubMenuVisible : function() {
9189 		for (var i=0; i < this.subMenus.length; i++) {
9190 			if (this.subMenus[i].visible) return true;
9191 		};
9192 		return false;
9193 	},
9194 	addHider : function() {
9195 		n2i.listen(document.body,'click',this.hider);
9196 	},
9197 	removeHider : function() {
9198 		n2i.unListen(document.body,'click',this.hider);
9199 	}
9200 }

9232 		this.hider = function(e) {
9233 			if (self.boundElement) {

9235 				// TODO: should be unreg'ed but it fails
9236 				//self.boundElement.stopObserving(self.hider);

9238 				self.boundElement = null;

9240 			}
9241 		}
9242 		n2i.listen(this.element,'mouseout',this.hider);
9243 	},

9246 		var element = n2i.build('div',{className:'in2igui_overlay_icon'});

9249 			self.iconWasClicked(key,e);
9250 		});
9251 		this.icons[key]=element;
9252 		this.content.appendChild(element);
9253 	},
9254 	addText : function(text) {
9255 		this.content.appendChild(n2i.build('span',{'class':'in2igui_overlay_text',text:text}));
9256 	},

9259 	},
9260 	hideIcons : function(keys) {
9261 		for (var i=0; i < keys.length; i++) {
9262 			this.icons[keys[i]].style.display='none';
9263 		};
9264 	},
9265 	showIcons : function(keys) {
9266 		for (var i=0; i < keys.length; i++) {
9267 			this.icons[keys[i]].style.display='';
9268 		};
9269 	},
9270 	iconWasClicked : function(key,e) {
9271 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'iconWasClicked',key,e);
9272 	},
9273 	showAtElement : function(element,options) {
9274 		options = options || {};
9275 		In2iGui.positionAtElement(this.element,element,options);
9276 		if (this.visible) return;
9277 		if (n2i.browser.msie) {
9278 			this.element.style.display='block';
9279 		} else {
9280 			n2i.setStyle(this.element,{'display':'block','opacity':0});
9281 			n2i.ani(this.element,'opacity',1,150);
9282 		}
9283 		this.visible = true;
9284 		if (options.autoHide) {
9285 			this.boundElement = element;
9286 			n2i.listen(element,'mouseout',this.hider);
9287 			n2i.addClass(element,'in2igui_overlay_bound');
9288 		}
9289 		if (this.options.modal) {
9290 			var zIndex = In2iGui.nextAlertIndex();
9291 			this.element.style.zIndex=zIndex+1;
9292 			In2iGui.showCurtain({widget:this,zIndex:zIndex});
9293 		}
9294 		return;
9295 	},
9296 	show : function(options) {
9297 		options = options || {};
9298 		if (!this.visible) {
9299 			n2i.setStyle(this.element,{'display':'block',visibility:'hidden'});
9300 		}
9301 		if (options.element) {
9302 			n2i.place({
9303 				source:{element:this.element,vertical:0,horizontal:.5},
9304 				target:{element:options.element,vertical:.5,horizontal:.5}
9305 			});
9306 		}
9307 		if (this.visible) return;
9308 		In2iGui.bounceIn(this.element);
9309 		this.visible = true;
9310 		if (options.autoHide && options.element) {
9311 			this.boundElement = options.element;
9312 			n2i.listen(options.element,'mouseout',this.hider);
9313 			n2i.addClass(options.element,'in2igui_overlay_bound');
9314 		}
9315 		if (this.options.modal) {
9316 			var zIndex = In2iGui.nextAlertIndex();
9317 			this.element.style.zIndex=zIndex+1;
9318 			var color = n2i.getStyle(document.body,'background-color');
9319 			In2iGui.showCurtain({widget:this,zIndex:zIndex,color:color});
9320 		}
9321 	},
9322 	/** private */
9323 	$curtainWasClicked : function() {
9324 		this.hide();
9325 	},
9326 	hide : function() {
9327 		In2iGui.hideCurtain(this);
9328 		this.element.style.display='none';
9329 		this.visible = false;
9330 	},
9331 	clear : function() {
9332 		In2iGui.destroyDescendants(this.content);
9333 		this.content.innerHTML='';
9334 	}

9338 /**
9339  * @class
9340  * @constructor
9341  *
9342  * Options
9343  * {url:'',parameters:{}}
9344  *
9345  * Events:
9346  * uploadDidCompleteQueue - when all files are done
9347  * uploadDidStartQueue - when the upload starts
9348  * uploadDidComplete(file) - when a single file is successfull
9349  * uploadDidFail(file) - when a single file fails
9350  */
9351 In2iGui.Upload = function(options) {
9352 	this.options = n2i.override({url:'',parameters:{},maxItems:50,maxSize:"20480",types:"*.*",useFlash:true,fieldName:'file',chooseButton:'Choose files...'},options);
9353 	this.element = n2i.get(options.element);
9354 	this.itemContainer = n2i.firstByClass(this.element,'in2igui_upload_items');
9355 	this.status = n2i.firstByClass(this.element,'in2igui_upload_status');
9356 	this.placeholder = n2i.firstByClass(this.element,'in2igui_upload_placeholder');
9357 	this.name = options.name;
9358 	this.items = [];
9359 	this.busy = false;
9360 	this.loaded = false;
9361 	this.useFlash = this.options.useFlash;
9362 	if (this.options.useFlash) {
9363 		this.useFlash = In2iGui.Flash.getMajorVersion()>=10;
9364 	}
9365 	In2iGui.extend(this);
9366 	this.addBehavior();
9367 }

9379 			(options.placeholder.title ? '<h2>'+n2i.escape(options.placeholder.title)+'</h2>' : '')+
9380 			(options.placeholder.text ? '<p>'+n2i.escape(options.placeholder.text)+'</p>' : '')+

9386 In2iGui.Upload.prototype = {
9387 	/** @private */
9388 	addBehavior : function() {
9389 		if (!this.useFlash) {
9390 			this.createIframeVersion();
9391 			return;
9392 		}
9393 		In2iGui.onDomReady(this.createFlashVersion.bind(this));
9394 	},
9395 	/**
9396 	 * Change a parameter
9397 	 */
9398 	setParameter : function(name,value) {
9399 		if (this.useFlash) {
9400 			alert('Not implemented for flash');
9401 		} else {
9402 			var existing = this.form.getElementsByTagName('input');
9403 			for (var i=0; i < existing.length; i++) {
9404 				if (existing[i].name==name) {
9405 					existing[i].value = value;
9406 					return;
9407 				}
9408 			};
9409 			this.form.insert(new Element('input',{'type':'hidden','name':name,'value':value}));
9410 		}
9411 	},
9412 	
9413 	/////////////////////////// Iframe //////////////////////////
9414 	
9415 	/** @private */
9416 	createIframeVersion : function() {
9417 		In2iGui.Upload.nameIndex++;
9418 		var frameName = 'in2igui_upload_'+In2iGui.Upload.nameIndex;
9419 		
9420 		var form = this.form = n2i.build('form');
9421 		form.setAttribute('action',this.options.url || '');
9422 		form.setAttribute('method','post');
9423 		form.setAttribute('enctype','multipart/form-data');
9424 		form.setAttribute('encoding','multipart/form-data');
9425 		form.setAttribute('target',frameName);
9426 		if (this.options.parameters) {
9427 			for (key in this.options.parameters) {
9428 				var hidden = n2i.build('input',{'type':'hidden','name':key});
9429 				hidden.value = this.options.parameters[key];
9430 				form.appendChild(hidden);
9431 			}
9432 		}
9433 		var iframe = this.iframe = n2i.build('iframe',{name:frameName,id:frameName,src:In2iGui.context+'/In2iGui/html/blank.html',style:'display:none'});
9434 		this.element.appendChild(iframe);
9435 		this.fileInput = n2i.build('input',{'type':'file','class':'file','name':this.options.fieldName});
9436 		n2i.listen(this.fileInput,'change',this.iframeSubmit.bind(this));
9437 		form.appendChild(this.fileInput);
9438 		var buttonContainer = n2i.build('span',{'class':'in2igui_upload_button'});
9439 		var span = n2i.build('span',{'class':'in2igui_upload_button_input'});
9440 		span.appendChild(form);
9441 		buttonContainer.appendChild(span);
9442 		if (this.options.widget) {
9443 			In2iGui.onDomReady(function() {
9444 				var w = In2iGui.get(this.options.widget);
9445 				w.element.parentNode.insertBefore(buttonContainer,w.element);
9446 				w.element.parentNode.removeChild(w.element);
9447 				buttonContainer.appendChild(w.element);
9448 			}.bind(this));
9449 		} else {
9450 			buttonContainer.innerHTML='<a href="javascript:void(0);" class="in2igui_button"><span><span>'+this.options.chooseButton+'</span></span></a>';
9451 			this.element.appendChild(buttonContainer);
9452 		}
9453 		n2i.listen(iframe,'load',function() {this.iframeUploadComplete()}.bind(this));
9454 	},
9455 	/** @private */
9456 	iframeUploadComplete : function() {
9457 		if (!this.uploading) return;
9458 		n2i.log('iframeUploadComplete uploading: '+this.uploading+' ('+this.name+')');
9459 		this.uploading = false;
9460 		this.form.reset();
9461 		var doc = n2i.getFrameDocument(this.iframe);
9462 		var last = this.items[this.items.length-1];
9463 		if (doc.body.innerHTML.indexOf('SUCCESS')!=-1) {
9464 			if (last) {
9465 				last.update({progress:1,filestatus:'Frdig'});
9466 			}
9467 			this.fire('uploadDidComplete',{}); // TODO: Send the correct file
9468 			n2i.log('Iframe upload succeeded');
9469 		} else if (last) {
9470 			last.setError('Upload af filen fejlede!');
9471 			n2i.log('Iframe upload failed!');
9472 			this.fire('uploadDidFail',{}); // TODO: Send the correct file
9473 		}
9474 		this.fire('uploadDidCompleteQueue');
9475 		this.iframe.src=In2iGui.context+'/In2iGui/html/blank.html';
9476 		this.endIframeProgress();
9477 	},
9478 	/** @private */
9479 	iframeSubmit : function() {
9480 		this.startIframeProgress();
9481 		this.uploading = true;
9482 		// IE: set value of parms again since they disappear
9483 		if (n2i.browser.msie) {
9484 			var p = this.options.parameters;
9485 			n2i.each(this.options.parameters,function(key,value) {
9486 				this.form[key].value = value;
9487 			}.bind(this));
9488 		}
9489 		this.form.submit();
9490 		this.fire('uploadDidStartQueue');
9491 		var fileName = this.fileInput.value.split('\\').pop();
9492 		this.addItem({name:fileName,filestatus:'I gang'}).setWaiting();
9493 		n2i.log('Iframe upload started!');
9494 	},
9495 	/** @private */
9496 	startIframeProgress : function() {
9497 		this.form.style.display='none';
9498 	},
9499 	/** @private */
9500 	endIframeProgress : function() {
9501 		this.form.style.display='block';
9502 		this.form.reset();
9503 	},
9504 	/** @public */
9505 	clear : function() {
9506 		for (var i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
9507 			if (this.items[i]) {
9508 				this.items[i].destroy();
9509 			}
9510 		};
9511 		this.items = [];
9512 		this.itemContainer.hide();
9513 		this.status.hide();
9514 		if (this.placeholder) {
9515 			this.placeholder.show();
9516 		}
9517 	},

9521 	/** @private */
9522 	getAbsoluteUrl : function(relative) {
9523 		var loc = new String(document.location);
9524 		var url = loc.slice(0,loc.lastIndexOf('/'));
9525 		while (relative.indexOf('../')===0) {
9526 			relative=relative.substring(3);
9527 			url = url.slice(0,url.lastIndexOf('/'));
9528 		}
9529 		url += '/'+relative;
9530 		return url;
9531 	},
9532 	
9533 	/** @private */
9534 	createFlashVersion : function() {
9535 		n2i.log('Creating flash verison');
9536 		var url = this.getAbsoluteUrl(this.options.url);
9537 		var javaSession = n2i.cookie.get('JSESSIONID');
9538 		if (javaSession) {
9539 			url+=';jsessionid='+javaSession;
9540 		}
9541 		var phpSession = n2i.cookie.get('PHPSESSID');
9542 		if (phpSession) {
9543 			url+='?PHPSESSID='+phpSession;
9544 		}
9545 		var buttonContainer = n2i.build('span',{'class':'in2igui_upload_button'});
9546 		var placeholder = n2i.build('span',{'class':'in2igui_upload_button_object',parent:buttonContainer});
9547 		if (this.options.widget) {
9548 			var w = In2iGui.get(this.options.widget);
9549 			w.element.parentNode.insertBefore(buttonContainer,w.element);
9550 			w.element.parentNode.removeChild(w.element);
9551 			buttonContainer.appendChild(w.element);
9552 		} else {
9553 			buttonContainer.innerHTL='<a href="javascript:void(0);" class="in2igui_button"><span><span>'+this.options.chooseButton+'</span></span></a>';
9554 			this.element.appendChild(buttonContainer);
9555 		}
9556 		
9557 		var self = this;
9558 		this.loader = new SWFUpload({
9559 			upload_url : url,
9560 			flash_url : In2iGui.context+"/In2iGui/lib/swfupload/swfupload.swf",
9561 			file_size_limit : this.options.maxSize,
9562 			file_queue_limit : this.options.maxItems,
9563 			file_post_name : this.options.fieldName,
9564 			file_upload_limit : this.options.maxItems,
9565 			file_types : this.options.types,
9566 			debug : true,
9567 			post_params : this.options.parameters,
9568 			button_placeholder_id : 'x',
9569 			button_placeholder : placeholder,
9570 			button_width : '100%',
9571 			button_height : 30,
9572 
9573 			swfupload_loaded_handler : this.flashLoaded.bind(this),
9574 			file_queued_handler : self.fileQueued.bind(self),
9575 			file_queue_error_handler : this.fileQueueError.bind(this),
9576 			file_dialog_complete_handler : this.fileDialogComplete.bind(this),
9577 			upload_start_handler : this.uploadStart.bind(this),
9578 			upload_progress_handler : this.uploadProgress.bind(this),
9579 			upload_error_handler : this.uploadError.bind(this),
9580 			upload_success_handler : this.uploadSuccess.bind(this),
9581 			upload_complete_handler : this.uploadComplete.bind(this)
9582 		});
9583 	},

9617 	},
9618 	/** @private */
9619 	uploadStart : function() {
9620 		this.status.style.display='block';
9621 		n2i.log('uploadStart');
9622 		if (!this.busy) {
9623 			this.fire('uploadDidStartQueue');
9624 		}
9625 		this.busy = true;
9626 	},
9627 	/** @private */
9628 	uploadProgress : function(file,complete,total) {
9629 		this.updateStatus();
9630 		this.items[file.index].updateProgress(complete,total);
9631 	},
9632 	/** @private */
9633 	uploadError : function(file, error, message) {
9634 		n2i.log('uploadError file:'+file+', error:'+error+', message:'+message);
9635 		if (file) {
9636 			this.items[file.index].update(file);
9637 		}
9638 	},
9639 	/** @private */
9640 	uploadSuccess : function(file,data) {
9641 		n2i.log('uploadSuccess file:'+file+', data:'+data);
9642 		this.items[file.index].updateProgress(file.size,file.size);
9643 	},
9644 	/** @private */
9645 	uploadComplete : function(file) {
9646 		this.items[file.index].update(file);
9647 		this.startNextUpload();
9648 		var self = this;
9649 		this.fire('uploadDidComplete',file);
9650 		if (this.loader.getStats().files_queued==0) {
9651 			this.fire('uploadDidCompleteQueue');
9652 		}
9653 		this.updateStatus();
9654 		this.busy = false;
9655 	},
9656 	
9657 	//////////// Items ////////////
9658 	
9659 	/** @private */
9660 	addItem : function(file) {
9661 		var index = file.index;
9662 		if (index===undefined) {
9663 			index = this.items.length;
9664 			file.index = index;
9665 		}
9666 		var item = new In2iGui.Upload.Item(file);
9667 		this.items[index] = item;
9668 		this.itemContainer.appendChild(item.element);
9669 		this.itemContainer.style.display='block';
9670 		if (this.placeholder) {
9671 			this.placeholder.style.display='none';
9672 		}
9673 		return item;
9674 	},
9675 	
9676 	/** @private */
9677 	updateStatus : function() {
9678 		var s = this.loader.getStats();
9679 		if (this.items.length==0) {
9680 			this.status.style.display='none';
9681 		} else {
9682 			n2i.dom.setText(this.status,'Status: '+Math.round(s.successful_uploads/this.items.length*100)+'%');
9683 			this.status.style.display='block';
9684 		}
9685 		n2i.log(s);
9686 	}
9687 }

9774 In2iGui.ProgressBar = function(o) {

9779 	/** @private */
9780 	this.COMPLETE = o.small ? 'in2igui_progressbar_small_complete' : 'in2igui_progressbar_complete';
9781 	/** @private */
9782 	this.options = o || {};
9783 	/** @private */
9784 	this.indicator = n2i.firstByTag(this.element,'div');

9791 In2iGui.ProgressBar.create = function(o) {

9798 In2iGui.ProgressBar.prototype = {
9799 	/** Set the progress value
9800 	@param value {Number} A number between 0 and 1
9801 	*/
9802 	setValue : function(value) {
9803 		var el = this.element;
9804 		if (this.waiting) {
9805 			n2i.removeClass(el,this.WAITING);
9806 		}
9807 		n2i.setClass(el,this.COMPLETE,value==1);
9808 		n2i.ani(this.indicator,'width',(value*100)+'%',200);
9809 	},
9810 	/** Mark progress as waiting */
9811 	setWaiting : function() {
9812 		this.waiting = true;
9813 		this.indicator.style.width=0;
9814 		n2i.addClass(this.element,this.WAITING);
9815 	},
9816 	/** Reset the progress bar */
9817 	reset : function() {
9818 		var el = this.element;
9819 		if (this.waiting) {
9820 			n2i.removeClass(el,this.WAITING);
9821 		}
9822 		n2i.removeClass(el,this.COMPLETE);
9823 		this.indicator.style.width='0%';
9824 	},
9825 	/** Hide the progress bar */
9826 	hide : function() {
9827 		this.element.style.display = 'none';
9828 	},
9829 	/** Show the progress bar */
9830 	show : function() {
9831 		this.element.style.display = 'block';

9862 In2iGui.Gallery.prototype = {
9863 	setObjects : function(objects) {
9864 		this.objects = objects;
9865 		this.render();
9866 		this.fire('selectionReset');
9867 	},
9868 	getObjects : function() {
9869 		return this.objects;
9870 	},
9871 	/** @private */
9872 	$objectsLoaded : function(objects) {
9873 		this.setObjects(objects);
9874 	},
9875 	/** @private */
9876 	$itemsLoaded : function(objects) {
9877 		this.setObjects(objects);
9878 	},
9879 	/** @private */
9880 	render : function() {
9881 		this.nodes = [];
9882 		this.maxRevealed=0;
9883 		this.element.innerHTML='';
9884 		var self = this;
9885 		n2i.each(this.objects,function(object,i) {
9886 			var url = self.resolveImageUrl(object);
9887 			if (url!==null) {
9888 				url = url.replace(/&/,'&');
9889 			}
9890 			if (object.height<object.width) {
9891 				var top = (self.height-(self.height*object.height/object.width))/2;
9892 			} else {
9893 				var top = 0;
9894 			}
9895 			var img = n2i.build('img',{style:'margin:'+top+'px auto 0px'});
9896 			img.setAttribute(self.revealing ? 'data-src' : 'src', url );
9897 			var item = n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_gallery_item',style:'width:'+self.width+'px; height:'+self.height+'px'});
9898 			item.appendChild(img);
9899 			n2i.listen(item,'click',function() {
9900 				self.itemClicked(i);
9901 			});
9902 			item.dragDropInfo = {kind:'image',icon:'common/image',id:object.id,title:object.name || object.title};
9903 			item.onmousedown=function(e) {
9904 				In2iGui.startDrag(e,item);
9905 				return false;
9906 			};
9907 			n2i.listen(item,'dblclick',function() {
9908 				self.itemDoubleClicked(i);
9909 			});
9910 			self.element.appendChild(item);
9911 			self.nodes.push(item);
9912 		});
9913 		this._reveal();
9914 	},
9915 	$$layout : function() {
9916 		if (this.nodes.length>0) {
9917 			this._reveal();
9918 		}
9919 	},
9920 	_reveal : function() {
9921 		if (!this.revealing) {return}
9922 		var container = this.element.parentNode;
9923 		var limit = container.scrollTop+container.clientHeight;
9924 		if (limit<=this.maxRevealed) {
9925 			return;
9926 		}
9927 		this.maxRevealed = limit;
9928 		for (var i=0,l=this.nodes.length; i < l; i++) {
9929 			var item = this.nodes[i];
9930 			if (item.offsetTop<limit) {
9931 				var img = item.getElementsByTagName('img')[0];
9932 				img.src = img.getAttribute('data-src');
9933 				item.revealed = true;
9934 			}
9935 		};
9936 	},
9937 	/** @private */
9938 	updateUI : function() {
9939 		var s = this.selected;
9940 		for (var i=0; i < this.nodes.length; i++) {
9941 			n2i.setClass(this.nodes[i],'in2igui_gallery_item_selected',n2i.inArray(s,i));
9942 		};
9943 	},
9944 	/** @private */
9945 	resolveImageUrl : function(img) {
9946 		return In2iGui.resolveImageUrl(this,img,this.width,this.height);
9947 		for (var i=0; i < this.delegates.length; i++) {
9948 			if (this.delegates[i]['$resolveImageUrl']) {
9949 				return this.delegates[i]['$resolveImageUrl'](img,this.width,this.height);
9950 			}
9951 		};
9952 		return '';
9953 	},
9954 	/** @private */
9955 	itemClicked : function(index) {
9956 		this.selected = [index];
9957 		this.fire('selectionChanged');
9958 		this.updateUI();
9959 	},
9960 	getFirstSelection : function() {
9961 		if (this.selected.length>0) {
9962 			return this.objects[this.selected[0]];
9963 		}
9964 		return null;
9965 	},
9966 	/** @private */
9967 	itemDoubleClicked : function(index) {
9968 		this.fire('itemOpened',this.objects[index]);
9969 	},
9970 	/**
9971 	 * Sets the lists data source and refreshes it if it is new
9972 	 * @param {In2iGui.Source} source The source
9973 	 */
9974 	setSource : function(source) {
9975 		if (this.options.source!=source) {
9976 			if (this.options.source) {
9977 				this.options.source.removeDelegate(this);
9978 			}
9979 			source.listen(this);
9980 			this.options.source = source;
9981 			source.refresh();
9982 		}
9983 	}
9984 }

10004 In2iGui.Calendar.prototype = {

10018 		date.setHours(0);
10019 		date.setMinutes(0);
10020 		date.setSeconds(0);

10034 		var nodes = n2i.byClass(this.element,'in2igui_calendar_event');
10035 		for (var i=0; i < nodes.length; i++) {
10036 			n2i.dom.remove(nodes[i]);
10037 		};
10038 		this.hideEventViewer();
10039 	},

10042 			this.setEvents(data);

10044 			n2i.log(e);
10045 		}
10046 	},

10053 	setEvents : function(events) {
10054 		events = events || [];
10055 		for (var i=0; i < events.length; i++) {
10056 			var e = events[i];
10057 			if (typeof(e.startTime)!='object') {
10058 				e.startTime = new Date(parseInt(e.startTime)*1000);
10059 			}
10060 			if (typeof(e.endTime)!='object') {
10061 				e.endTime = new Date(parseInt(e.endTime)*1000);
10062 			}
10063 		};
10064 		this.setBusy(false);
10065 		this.clearEvents();
10066 		this.events = events;
10067 		var self = this;
10068 		var pixels = (this.options.endHour-this.options.startHour)*40;
10069 		var week = this.getFirstDay().getWeekOfYear();
10070 		var year = this.getFirstDay().getYear();
10071 		n2i.each(this.events,function(event) {
10072 			var day = n2i.byClass(self.body,'in2igui_calendar_day')[event.startTime.getDay()-1];
10073 			if (!day) {
10074 				return;
10075 			}
10076 			if (event.startTime.getWeekOfYear()!=week || event.startTime.getYear()!=year) {
10077 				return;
10078 			}
10079 			var node = n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_calendar_event'});
10080 			var top = ((event.startTime.getHours()*60+event.startTime.getMinutes())/60-self.options.startHour)*40-1;
10081 			var height = (event.endTime.getTime()-event.startTime.getTime())/1000/60/60*40+1;
10082 			var height = Math.min(pixels-top,height);
10083 			node.setStyle({'marginTop':top+'px','height':height+'px',visibility:'hidden'});
10084 			var content = new Element('div');
10085 			content.insert(new Element('p',{'class':'in2igui_calendar_event_time'}).update(event.startTime.dateFormat('H:i')));
10086 			content.insert(new Element('p',{'class':'in2igui_calendar_event_text'}).update(event.text));
10087 			if (event.location) {
10088 				content.insert(new Element('p',{'class':'in2igui_calendar_event_location'}).update(event.location));
10089 			}
10090 			
10091 			day.insert(node.insert(content));
10092 			window.setTimeout(function() {
10093 				In2iGui.bounceIn(node);
10094 			},Math.random()*200)
10095 			node.observe('click',function() {
10096 				self.eventWasClicked(event,this);
10097 			});
10098 		});
10099 	},

10140 		for (var i=this.options.startHour; i <= this.options.endHour; i++) {
10141 			var node = n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_calendar_time',html:'<span><em>'+i+':00</em></span>'});
10142 			if (i==this.options.startHour) {
10143 				n2i.addClass(node,'in2igui_calendar_time_first');
10144 			}
10145 			if (i==this.options.endHour) {
10146 				n2i.addClass(node,'in2igui_calendar_time_last');
10147 			}
10148 			time.appendChild(node);
10149 		};
10150 	},

10178 		In2iGui.firePropertyChange(this,'endTime',this.getLastDay());
10179 	},

10184 		}
10185 		if (p=='endTime') {

10187 		}
10188 		return this[p];
10189 	},
