10249 /** @constructor */
10250 In2iGui.DatePicker = function(options) {
10251 	this.name = options.name;
10252 	this.element = n2i.get(options.element);
10253 	this.options = {};
10254 	n2i.override(this.options,options);
10255 	this.cells = [];
10256 	this.title = n2i.firstByTag(this.element,'strong');
10257 	this.today = new Date();
10258 	this.value = this.options.value ? new Date(this.options.value.getTime()) : new Date();
10259 	this.viewDate = new Date(this.value.getTime());
10260 	this.viewDate.setDate(1);
10261 	In2iGui.extend(this);
10262 	this.addBehavior();
10263 	this.updateUI();
10264 }
10265 
10266 In2iGui.DatePicker.create = function(options) {
10267 	var element = options.element = n2i.build('div',{
10268 		'class' : 'in2igui_datepicker',
10269 		html : '<div class="in2igui_datepicker_header"><a class="in2igui_datepicker_next"></a><a class="in2igui_datepicker_previous"></a><strong></strong></div>'
10270 	});
10271 	var table = n2i.build('table',{parent:element});
10272 	var thead = n2i.build('thead',{parent:table});
10273 	var head = n2i.build('tr',{parent:thead});
10274 	for (var i=0;i<7;i++) {
10275 		head.insert(n2i.build('th',{text:Date.dayNames[i].substring(0,3)}));
10276 	}
10277 	var body = n2i.build('tbody',{parent:table});
10278 	for (var i=0;i<6;i++) {
10279 		var row = n2i.build('tr',{parent:body});
10280 		for (var j=0;j<7;j++) {
10281 			var cell = n2i.build('td',{parent:row});
10282 		}
10283 	}
10284 	return new In2iGui.DatePicker(options);
10285 }
10286 
10287 In2iGui.DatePicker.prototype = {
10288 	addBehavior : function() {
10289 		var self = this;
10290 		this.cells = n2i.firstByClass(this.element,'td');
10291 		this.each(this.cells,function(cell,index) {
10292 			n2i.listen(cell,'mousedown',function() {self.selectCell(index)});
10293 		})
10294 		var next = n2i.firstByClass(this.element,'in2igui_datepicker_next');
10295 		var previous = n2i.firstByClass(this.element,'in2igui_datepicker_previous');
10296 		n2i.listen(next,'mousedown',function() {self.next()});
10297 		n2i.listen(previous,'mousedown',function() {self.previous()});
10298 	},
10299 	setValue : function(date) {
10300 		this.value = new Date(date.getTime());
10301 		this.viewDate = new Date(date.getTime());
10302 		this.viewDate.setDate(1);
10303 		this.updateUI();
10304 	},
10305 	updateUI : function() {
10306 		this.title.update(this.viewDate.dateFormat('F Y'));
10307 		var isSelectedYear =  this.value.getFullYear()==this.viewDate.getFullYear();
10308 		var month = this.viewDate.getMonth();
10309 		for (var i=0; i < this.cells.length; i++) {
10310 			var date = this.indexToDate(i);
10311 			var cell = this.cells[i];
10312 			if (date.getMonth()<month) {
10313 				cell.className = 'in2igui_datepicker_dimmed';
10314 			} else if (date.getMonth()>month) {
10315 				cell.className = 'in2igui_datepicker_dimmed';
10316 			} else {
10317 				cell.className = '';
10318 			}
10319 			if (date.getDate()==this.value.getDate() && date.getMonth()==this.value.getMonth() && isSelectedYear) {
10320 				n2i.addClass(cell,'in2igui_datepicker_selected');
10321 			}
10322 			if (date.getDate()==this.today.getDate() && date.getMonth()==this.today.getMonth() && date.getFullYear()==this.today.getFullYear()) {
10323 				ni2.addClass(cell,'in2igui_datepicker_today');
10324 			}
10325 			n2i.dom.setText(cell,date.getDate());
10326 		};
10327 	},
10328 	getPreviousMonth : function() {
10329 		var previous = new Date(this.viewDate.getTime());
10330 		previous.setMonth(previous.getMonth()-1);
10331 		return previous;
10332 	},
10333 	getNextMonth : function() {
10334 		var previous = new Date(this.viewDate.getTime());
10335 		previous.setMonth(previous.getMonth()+1);
10336 		return previous;
10337 	},
10338 
10339 	////////////////// Events ///////////////
10340 
10341 	previous : function() {
10342 		this.viewDate = this.getPreviousMonth();
10343 		this.updateUI();
10344 	},
10345 	next : function() {
10346 		this.viewDate = this.getNextMonth();
10347 		this.updateUI();
10348 	},
10349 	selectCell : function(index) {
10350 		this.value = this.indexToDate(index);
10351 		this.viewDate = new Date(this.value.getTime());
10352 		this.viewDate.setDate(1);
10353 		this.updateUI();
10354 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'dateChanged',this.value);
10355 	},
10356 	indexToDate : function(index) {
10357 		var first = this.viewDate.getDay();
10358 		var days = this.viewDate.getDaysInMonth();
10359 		var previousDays = this.getPreviousMonth().getDaysInMonth();
10360 		if (index<first) {
10361 			var date = this.getPreviousMonth();
10362 			date.setDate(previousDays-first+index+1);
10363 			return date;
10364 		} else if (index>first+days-1) {
10365 			var date = this.getPreviousMonth();
10366 			date.setDate(index-first-days+1);
10367 			return date;
10368 			cell.update(i-first-days+1);
10369 		} else {
10370 			var date = new Date(this.viewDate.getTime());
10371 			date.setDate(index+1-first);
10372 			return date;
10373 		}
10374 	}
10375 }

10410 In2iGui.Layout.prototype = {
10411 	$$layout : function() {
10412 		if (!n2i.browser.msie7 && !n2i.browser.msie8) {
10413 			return;
10414 		}
10415 		if (this.diff===undefined) {
10416 			var head = n2i.firstByClass(this.element,'in2igui_layout_top');
10417 			var top = n2i.firstByTag(head,'*').clientHeight;
10418 			var foot = n2i.firstByTag(n2i.firstByTag(this.element,'tfoot'),'td');
10419 			var bottom = 0;
10420 			if (foot) {
10421 				bottom = n2i.firstByTag(foot,'*').clientHeight;
10422 			}
10423 			top += n2i.getTop(this.element);
10424 			this.diff = bottom+top;
10425 			if (this.element.parentNode!==document.body) {
10426 				this.diff+=15;
10427 			} else {
10428 			}
10429 		}
10430 		var tbody = n2i.firstByTag(this.element,'tbody');
10431 		var cell = n2i.firstByTag(tbody,'td');
10432 		cell.style.height = (n2i.getViewPortHeight()-this.diff+5)+'px';
10433 	}
10434 };

10601 };/**
10602  * @constructor
10603  * A wizard with a number of steps
10604  */
10605 In2iGui.Wizard = function(o) {
10606 	/** @private */
10607 	this.options = o || {};
10608 	/** @private */
10609 	this.element = n2i.get(o.element);
10610 	/** @private */
10611 	this.name = o.name;
10612 	/** @private */
10613 	this.container = n2i.firstByClass(this.element,'in2igui_wizard_steps');
10614 	/** @private */
10615 	this.steps = n2i.byClass(this.element,'in2igui_wizard_step');
10616 	/** @private */
10617 	this.anchors = n2i.byClass(this.element,'in2igui_wizard_selection');
10618 	/** @private */
10619 	this.selected = 0;
10620 	In2iGui.extend(this);
10621 	this.addBehavior();
10622 }
10623 	
10624 In2iGui.Wizard.prototype = {
10625 	/** @private */
10626 	addBehavior : function() {
10627 		var self = this;
10628 		n2i.each(this.anchors,function(node,i) {
10629 			n2i.listen(node,'mousedown',function(e) {
10630 				n2i.stop(e);
10631 				self.goToStep(i)
10632 			});
10633 			n2i.listen(node,'click',function(e) {
10634 				n2i.stop(e);
10635 			});
10636 		});
10637 	},
10638 	/** Goes to the step with the index */
10639 	goToStep : function(index) {
10640 		var c = this.container;
10641 		c.style.height=c.clientHeight+'px';
10642 		n2i.removeClass(this.anchors[this.selected],'in2igui_selected');
10643 		this.steps[this.selected].style.display='none';
10644 		n2i.addClass(this.anchors[index],'in2igui_selected');
10645 		this.steps[index].style.display='block';
10646 		this.selected=index;
10647 		n2i.ani(c,'height',this.steps[index].clientHeight+'px',500,{ease:n2i.ease.slowFastSlow,onComplete:function() {
10648 			c.style.height='';
10649 		}});
10650 		In2iGui.callVisible(this);
10651 	},
10652 	/** Goes to the next step */
10653 	next : function() {
10654 		if (this.selected<this.steps.length-1) {
10655 			this.goToStep(this.selected+1);
10656 		}
10657 	},
10658 	/** Goes to the previous step */
10659 	previous : function() {
10660 		if (this.selected>0) {
10661 			this.goToStep(this.selected-1);
10662 		}
10663 	}
10664 }

10680 In2iGui.Articles.prototype = {
10681 	/** @private */
10682 	$articlesLoaded : function(doc) {
10683 		this.element.innerHTML='';
10684 		var a = doc.getElementsByTagName('article');
10685 		for (var i=0; i < a.length; i++) {
10686 			var e = n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_article'});
10687 			var c = a[i].childNodes;
10688 			for (var j=0; j < c.length; j++) {
10689 				if (n2i.dom.isElement(c[j],'title')) {
10690 					var title = n2i.dom.getText(c[j]);
10691 					e.appendChild(n2i.build('h2',{text:title}));
10692 				} else if (n2i.dom.isElement(c[j],'paragraph')) {
10693 					var text = n2i.dom.getText(c[j]);
10694 					var p = n2i.build('p',{text:text});
10695 					if (c[j].getAttribute('dimmed')==='true') {
10696 						p.className='in2igui_dimmed';
10697 					}
10698 					e.appendChild(p);
10699 				}
10700 			};
10701 			this.element.appendChild(e);
10702 		};
10703 	},
10704 	$sourceFailed : function() {
10705 		this.element.innerHTML='<div>Failed!</div>';
10706 	},
10707 	/** @private */
10708 	$sourceIsBusy : function() {
10709 		this.element.innerHTML='<div class="in2igui_articles_loading">Loading...</div>';
10710 	},
10711 	/** @private */
10712 	$sourceIsNotBusy : function() {
10713 		n2i.removeClass(this.element,'in2igui_list_busy');
10714 	}
10715 }

10717 /* EOF *//** @constructor */
10718 In2iGui.TextField = function(options) {
10719 	this.options = n2i.override({placeholderElement:null,validator:null},options);
10720 	var e = this.element = n2i.get(options.element);
10721 	this.element.setAttribute('autocomplete','off');
10722 	this.value = this.validate(this.element.value);
10723 	this.isPassword = this.element.type=='password';
10724 	this.name = options.name;
10725 	In2iGui.extend(this);
10726 	this.addBehavior();
10727 	if (this.options.placeholderElement && this.value!='') {
10728 		In2iGui.fadeOut(this.options.placeholderElement,0);
10729 	}
10730 	this.checkPlaceholder();
10731 	try { // IE hack
10732 		if (e==document.activeElement) {
10733 			this.focused();
10734 		}
10735 	} catch (e) {}
10736 }

10738 In2iGui.TextField.prototype = {
10739 	addBehavior : function() {
10740 		var e = this.element;
10741 		n2i.listen(e,'keyup',this.keyDidStrike.bind(this));
10742 		var p = this.options.placeholderElement;
10743 		n2i.listen(e,'blur',this.onBlur.bind(this));
10744 		if (p) {
10745 			n2i.listen(e,'focus',this.focused.bind(this));
10746 			n2i.listen(e,'blur',this.checkPlaceholder.bind(this));
10747 			if (p) {
10748 				p.style.cursor='text';
10749 				n2i.listen(p,'mousedown',this.focus.bind(this));
10750 				n2i.listen(p,'click',this.focus.bind(this));
10751 			}
10752 		}
10753 	},
10754 	focused : function() {
10755 		var e = this.element,p = this.options.placeholderElement;
10756 		if (p && e.value=='') {
10757 			In2iGui.fadeOut(p,0);
10758 		}
10759 	},
10760 	/** @private */
10761 	validate : function(value) {
10762 		var validator = this.options.validator, result;
10763 		if (validator) {
10764 			result = validator.validate(value);
10765 			n2i.setClass(this.element,'in2igui_invalid',!result.valid);
10766 			return result.value;
10767 		}
10768 		return value;
10769 	},
10770 	checkPlaceholder : function() {
10771 		if (this.options.placeholderElement && this.value=='') {
10772 			In2iGui.fadeIn(this.options.placeholderElement,200);
10773 		}
10774 		if (this.isPassword && !n2i.browser.msie) {
10775 			this.element.type='password';
10776 		}
10777 	},
10778 	/** @private */
10779 	keyDidStrike : function() {
10780 		if (this.value!==this.element.value) {
10781 			var newValue = this.validate(this.element.value);
10782 			var changed = newValue!==this.value;
10783 			this.value = newValue;
10784 			if (changed) {
10785 				this.fire('valueChanged',this.value);
10786 			}
10787 		}
10788 	},
10789 	/** @private */
10790 	onBlur : function() {
10791 		n2i.removeClass(this.element,'in2igui_invalid');
10792 		this.element.value = this.value || '';
10793 	},
10794 	getValue : function() {
10795 		return this.value;
10796 	},
10797 	setValue : function(value) {
10798 		if (value===undefined || value===null) {
10799 			value='';
10800 		}
10801 		this.element.value = value;
10802 		this.value = this.validate(value);
10803 	},
10804 	isEmpty : function() {
10805 		return this.value=='';
10806 	},
10807 	isBlank : function() {
10808 		return this.value.strip()=='';
10809 	},
10810 	focus : function() {
10811 		this.element.focus();
10812 	},
10813 	setError : function(error) {
10814 		var isError = error ? true : false;
10815 		n2i.setClass(this.element,'in2igui_field_error',isError);
10816 		if (typeof(error) == 'string') {
10817 			In2iGui.showToolTip({text:error,element:this.element,key:this.name});
10818 		}
10819 		if (!isError) {
10820 			In2iGui.hideToolTip({key:this.name});
10821 		}
10822 	}
10823 };

10834 In2iGui.InfoView.create = function(options) {

10847 In2iGui.InfoView.prototype = {
10848 	addHeader : function(text) {
10849 		var row = new Element('tr');
10850 		row.insert(new Element('th',{'class' : 'in2igui_infoview_header','colspan':'2'}).insert(text));
10851 		this.body.insert(row);
10852 	},
10853 	addProperty : function(label,text) {
10854 		var row = new Element('tr');
10855 		row.insert(new Element('th').insert(label));
10856 		row.insert(new Element('td').insert(text));
10857 		this.body.insert(row);
10858 	},
10859 	addObjects : function(label,objects) {
10860 		if (!objects || objects.length==0) return;
10861 		var row = new Element('tr');
10862 		row.insert(new Element('th').insert(label));
10863 		var cell = new Element('td');
10864 		var click = this.options.clickObjects;
10865 		objects.each(function(obj) {
10866 			var node = new Element('div').insert(obj.title);
10867 			if (click) {
10868 				node.addClassName('in2igui_infoview_click')
10869 				node.observe('click',function() {
10870 					In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'objectWasClicked',obj);
10871 				});
10872 			}
10873 			cell.insert(node);
10874 		});
10875 		row.insert(cell);
10876 		this.body.insert(row);
10877 	},
10878 	setBusy : function(busy) {
10879 		if (busy) {
10880 			this.element.addClassName('in2igui_infoview_busy');
10881 		} else {
10882 			this.element.removeClassName('in2igui_infoview_busy');
10883 		}
10884 	},
10885 	clear : function() {
10886 		this.body.update();
10887 	},
10888 	update : function(data) {
10889 		this.clear();
10890 		for (var i=0; i < data.length; i++) {
10891 			switch (data[i].type) {
10892 				case 'header': this.addHeader(data[i].value); break;
10893 				case 'property': this.addProperty(data[i].label,data[i].value); break;
10894 				case 'objects': this.addObjects(data[i].label,data[i].value); break;
10895 			}
10896 		};
10897 	}
10898 }

10912 In2iGui.Overflow.create = function(options) {

10914 	var e = options.element = n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_overflow'});

10917 	}

10920 
10921 In2iGui.Overflow.prototype = {
10922 	calculate : function() {
10923 		var top,bottom,parent,viewport;
10924 		viewport = n2i.getInnerHeight();
10925 		parent = this.element.parentNode;
10926 		top = n2i.getTop(this.element);
10927 		bottom = n2i.getTop(parent)+parent.clientHeight;
10928 		var sibs = n2i.getAllNext(this.element);
10929 		for (var i=0; i < sibs.length; i++) {
10930 			bottom-=sibs[i].clientHeight;
10931 		};
10932 		this.diff=-1*(top+(viewport-bottom));
10933 	},
10934 	add : function(widgetOrNode) {
10935 		if (widgetOrNode.getElement) {
10936 			this.element.appendChild(widgetOrNode.getElement());
10937 		} else {
10938 			this.element.appendChild(widgetOrNode);
10939 		}
10940 		return this;
10941 	},
10942 	$$layout : function() {
10943 		if (!this.options.dynamic) {
10944 			if (this.options.vertical) {
10945 				var height = n2i.getInnerHeight();
10946 				this.element.style.height = Math.max(0,height-this.options.vertical)+'px';
10947 			}
10948 			return;
10949 		}
10950 		if (this.diff===undefined) {
10951 			this.calculate();
10952 		}
10953 		var height = n2i.getInnerHeight();
10954 		this.element.style.height = Math.max(0,height+this.diff)+'px';
10955 	}
10956 }

10979 		html : '<em class="in2igui_searchfield_placeholder"></em><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="in2igui_searchfield_reset"></a><span><span><input type="text"/></span></span>'

10984 In2iGui.SearchField.prototype = {
10985 	/** @private */
10986 	addBehavior : function() {
10987 		var self = this;
10988 		n2i.listen(this.field,'keyup',this.onKeyUp.bind(this));
10989 		var reset = n2i.firstByTag(this.element,'a');
10990 		reset.tabIndex=-1;
10991 		var focus = function() {self.field.focus();self.field.select()};
10992 		n2i.listen(this.element,'mousedown',focus);
10993 		n2i.listen(this.element,'mouseup',focus);
10994 		//this.element.observe('mousedown',focus).observe('mouseup',focus);
10995 		n2i.listen(reset,'mousedown',function(e) {
10996 			n2i.stop(e);
10997 			self.reset();
10998 			focus()
10999 		});
11000 		n2i.listen(n2i.firstByTag(this.element,'em'),'mousedown',focus);
11001 		n2i.listen(this.field,'focus',function() {
11002 			self.focused=true;
11003 			self.updateClass();
11004 		});
11005 		n2i.listen(this.field,'blur',function() {
11006 			self.focused=false;
11007 			self.updateClass();
11008 		});
11009 		if (this.options.expandedWidth>0) {
11010 			this.field.onfocus = function() {
11011 				n2i.ani(self.element,'width',self.options.expandedWidth+'px',500,{ease:n2i.ease.slowFastSlow});
11012 			}
11013 			this.field.onblur = function() {
11014 				n2i.ani(self.element,'width',self.initialWidth+'px',500,{ease:n2i.ease.slowFastSlow,delay:100});
11015 			}
11016 		}
11017 	},
11018 	onKeyUp : function(e) {
11019 		this.fieldChanged();
11020 		if (e.keyCode===Event.KEY_RETURN) {
11021 			this.fire('submit');
11022 		}
11023 	},
11024 	setValue : function(value) {
11025 		this.field.value=value===undefined || value===null ? '' : value;
11026 		this.fieldChanged();
11027 	},
11028 	getValue : function() {
11029 		return this.field.value;
11030 	},
11031 	isEmpty : function() {
11032 		return this.field.value=='';
11033 	},
11034 	isBlank : function() {
11035 		return this.field.value.strip()=='';
11036 	},
11037 	reset : function() {
11038 		this.field.value='';
11039 		this.fieldChanged();
11040 	},
11041 	/** @private */
11042 	updateClass : function() {
11043 		var className = 'in2igui_searchfield';
11044 		if (this.adaptive) {
11045 			className+=' in2igui_searchfield_adaptive';
11046 		}
11047 		if (this.focused && this.value!='') {
11048 			className+=' in2igui_searchfield_focus_dirty';
11049 		} else if (this.focused) {
11050 			className+=' in2igui_searchfield_focus';
11051 		} else if (this.value!='') {
11052 			className+=' in2igui_searchfield_dirty';
11053 		}
11054 		this.element.className=className;
11055 	},
11056 	/** @private */
11057 	fieldChanged : function() {
11058 		if (this.field.value!=this.value) {
11059 			this.value=this.field.value;
11060 			this.updateClass();
11061 			this.fire('valueChanged',this.value);
11062 			In2iGui.firePropertyChange(this,'value',this.value);
11063 		}
11064 	}
11065 }

11088 /* EOF *//**
11089 	Used to get a geografical location
11090 	@constructor
11091 */
11092 In2iGui.LocationPicker = function(options) {
11093 	options = options || {};
11094 	this.name = options.name;
11095 	this.options = options.options || {};
11096 	this.element = n2i.get(options.element);
11097 	this.defaultCenter = new google.maps.LatLng(57.0465, 9.9185);
11098 	In2iGui.extend(this);
11099 	this.addBehavior();
11100 }
11101 
11102 In2iGui.LocationPicker.prototype = {
11103 	/** @private */
11104 	addBehavior : function() {
11105 	},
11106 	show : function(options) {
11107 		if (!this.panel) {
11108 			var panel = this.panel = In2iGui.BoundPanel.create({width:300});
11109 			var mapContainer = new Element('div').setStyle({width:'300px',height:'300px'});
11110 			panel.add(mapContainer);
11111 			var buttons = In2iGui.Buttons.create({align:'right',top:5});
11112 			var button = In2iGui.Button.create({text:'Luk'});
11113 			button.listen({$click:function() {panel.hide()}});
11114 			panel.add(buttons.add(button));
11115 			panel.element.setStyle({left:'-10000px',top:'-10000px',display:''});
11116 			var latLng = this.buildLatLng();
11117 		    var mapOptions = {
11118 		      zoom: 15,
11119 		      mapTypeId: google.maps.MapTypeId.TERRAIN
11120 		    }
11121 		    this.map = new google.maps.Map(mapContainer, mapOptions);
11122 			google.maps.event.addListener(this.map, 'click', function(obj) {
11123 				var loc = {latitude:obj.latLng.lat(),longitude:obj.latLng.lng()};
11124     			this.setLocation(loc);
11125 				this.fire('locationChanged',loc);
11126   			}.bind(this));
11127 			panel.element.setStyle({display:'none'});
11128 		}
11129 		this.setLocation(options.location);
11130 		if (options.node) {
11131 			this.panel.position(options.node);
11132 		}
11133 		this.panel.show();
11134 	},
11135 	setLocation : function(loc) {
11136 		if (!loc && this.marker) {
11137 			this.marker.setMap(null);
11138 			this.map.setCenter(this.defaultCenter);
11139 			return;
11140 		}
11141 		loc = this.buildLatLng(loc);
11142 		if (!this.marker) {
11143 		    this.marker = new google.maps.Marker({
11144 		        position: loc, 
11145 		        map: this.map
11146 		    });
11147 		} else {
11148     		this.marker.setPosition(loc);
11149 			this.marker.setMap(this.map);
11150 		}
11151 		this.map.setCenter(loc);
11152 	},
11153 	/** @private */
11154 	buildLatLng : function(loc) {
11155 		if (!loc) {
11156 			loc = {latitude:57.0465, longitude:9.9185};
11157 		}
11158 		return new google.maps.LatLng(loc.latitude, loc.longitude);
11159 	}
11160 }

11267 In2iGui.VideoPlayer = function(options) {
11268 	this.options = options;
11269 	this.element = n2i.get(options.element);
11270 	this.placeholder = this.element.select('div')[0];
11271 	this.name = options.name;
11272 	this.state = {duration:0,time:0,loaded:0};
11273 	this.handlers = [In2iGui.VideoPlayer.HTML5,In2iGui.VideoPlayer.QuickTime,In2iGui.VideoPlayer.Embedded];
11274 	this.handler = null;
11275 	In2iGui.extend(this);
11276 	if (this.options.video) {
11277 		if (this.placeholder) {
11278 			this.placeholder.observe('click',function() {
11279 				this.setVideo(this.options.video);
11280 			}.bind(this))
11281 		} else {
11282 			In2iGui.onReady(function() {
11283 				this.setVideo(this.options.video);
11284 			}.bind(this));			
11285 		}
11286 	}
11287 }
11288 
11289 In2iGui.VideoPlayer.prototype = {
11290 	setVideo : function(video) {
11291 		this.handler = this.getHandler(video);
11292 		this.element.update(this.handler.element);
11293 		if (this.handler.showController()) {
11294 			this.buildController();
11295 		}
11296 	},
11297 	getHandler : function(video) {
11298 		for (var i=0; i < this.handlers.length; i++) {
11299 			var handler = this.handlers[i];
11300 			if (handler.isSupported(video)) {
11301 				return new handler(video,this);
11302 			}
11303 		};
11304 	},
11305 	buildController : function() {
11306 		var e = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_videoplayer_controller'});
11307 		this.playButton = new Element('a',{href:'javascript:void(0);','class':'in2igui_videoplayer_playpause'}).insert('wait!');
11308 		this.playButton.observe('click',this.playPause.bind(this));
11309 		this.status = new Element('span',{'class':'in2igui_videoplayer_status'});
11310 		e.insert(this.playButton).insert(this.status);
11311 		this.element.insert(e);
11312 	},
11313 	onCanPlay : function() {
11314 		this.playButton.update('Play');
11315 	},
11316 	onLoad : function() {
11317 		this.state.loaded = this.state.duration;
11318 		this.updateStatus();
11319 	},
11320 	onDurationChange : function(duration) {
11321 		this.state.duration = duration;
11322 		this.updateStatus();
11323 	},
11324 	onTimeChange : function(time) {
11325 		this.state.time = time;
11326 		this.updateStatus();
11327 	},
11328 	onLoadProgressChange : function(progress) {
11329 		this.state.loaded = progress;
11330 		this.updateStatus();
11331 	},
11332 	playPause : function() {
11333 		if (this.handler.isPlaying()) {
11334 			this.pause();
11335 		} else {
11336 			this.play();
11337 		}
11338 	},
11339 	play : function() {
11340 		this.handler.play();
11341 	},
11342 	pause : function() {
11343 		this.handler.pause();
11344 	},
11345 	updateStatus : function() {
11346 		this.status.innerHTML = this.state.time+' / '+this.state.duration+' / '+this.state.loaded;
11347 	}
11348 }

11352 In2iGui.VideoPlayer.HTML5 = function(video,player) {
11353 	var e = this.element = new Element('video',{width:video.width,height:video.height,src:video.src});
11354 	e.observe('load',player.onLoad.bind(player));
11355 	e.observe('canplay',player.onCanPlay.bind(player));
11356 	e.observe('durationchange',function(x) {
11357 		player.onDurationChange(e.duration);
11358 	});
11359 	e.observe('timeupdate',function() {
11360 		player.onTimeChange(this.element.currentTime);
11361 	}.bind(this));
11362 }

11364 In2iGui.VideoPlayer.HTML5.isSupported = function(video) {
11365 	if (n2i.browser.webkitVersion>528 && (video.type==='video/quicktime' || video.type==='video/mp4')) {
11366 		return true;
11367 	}
11368 	return false;
11369 }

11391 In2iGui.VideoPlayer.QuickTime = function(video,player) {

11395 		+'<param value="true" name="enablejavascript"/>'
11396 		+'<param value="undefined" name="posterframe"/>'
11397 		+'<param value="false" name="showlogo"/>'
11398 		+'<param value="false" name="autostart"/>'
11399 		+'<param value="true" name="cache"/>'
11400 		+'<param value="white" name="bgcolor"/>'
11401 		+'<param value="false" name="aggressivecleanup"/>'
11402 		+'<param value="true" name="saveembedtags"/>'
11403 		+'<param value="true" name="postdomevents"/>');
11404 		
11405 	e.observe('qt_canplay',player.onCanPlay.bind(player));
11406 	e.observe('qt_load',player.onLoad.bind(player));
11407 	e.observe('qt_progress',function() {
11408 		player.onLoadProgressChange(e.GetMaxTimeLoaded()/3000);
11409 	});
11410 	e.observe('qt_durationchange',function(x) {

11412 	});

11414 		player.onTimeChange(e.GetTime());

11478 In2iGui.Segmented = function(options) {
11479 	this.options = n2i.override({value:null,allowNull:false},options);
11480 	this.element = n2i.get(options.element);
11481 	this.name = options.name;
11482 	this.value = this.options.value;
11483 	In2iGui.extend(this);
11484 	n2i.listen(this.element,'mousedown',this.onClick.bind(this));
11485 }
11486 
11487 In2iGui.Segmented.prototype = {
11488 	/** @private */
11489 	onClick : function(e) {
11490 		e = new n2i.Event(e);
11491 		var a = e.findByTag('a');
11492 		if (a) {
11493 			var changed = false;
11494 			var value = a.getAttribute('rel');
11495 			var x = n2i.byClass(this.element,'in2igui_segmented_selected');
11496 			for (var i=0; i < x.length; i++) {
11497 				n2i.removeClass(x[i],'in2igui_segmented_selected');
11498 			};
11499 			if (value===this.value && this.options.allowNull) {
11500 				changed=true;
11501 				this.value = null;
11502 				this.fire('valueChanged',this.value);
11503 			} else {
11504 				n2i.addClass(a,'in2igui_segmented_selected');
11505 				changed=this.value!== value;
11506 				this.value = value;
11507 			}
11508 			if (changed) {
11509 				this.fire('valueChanged',this.value);
11510 			}
11511 		}
11512 	},
11513 	setValue : function(value) {
11514 		if (value===undefined) {
11515 			value=null;
11516 		}
11517 		var as = this.element.getElementsByTagName('a');
11518 		this.value = null;
11519 		for (var i=0; i < as.length; i++) {
11520 			if (as[i].getAttribute('rel')===value) {
11521 				n2i.addClass(as[i],'in2igui_segmented_selected');
11522 				this.value=value;
11523 			} else {
11524 				n2i.removeClass(as[i],'in2igui_segmented_selected');
11525 			}
11526 		};
11527 	},
11528 	getValue : function() {
11529 		return this.value;
11530 	}
11531 }

11533 /* EOF *//** @namespace */
11534 In2iGui.Flash = {
11535 	
11536 	fullVersion:undefined,
11537 	
11538 	/** Gets the major version of flash */
11539 	getMajorVersion : function() {
11540 		var full = this.getFullVersion();
11541 		if (full===null || full===undefined) {
11542 			return null;
11543 		}
11544 		var matched = (full+'').match(/[0-9]+/gi);
11545 		return matched.length>0 ? parseInt(matched[0]) : null;
11546 	},
11547 	
11548 	getFullVersion : function() {
11549 		if (this.fullVersion!==undefined) {
11550 			return this.fullVersion;
11551 		}
11552 		// NS/Opera version >= 3 check for Flash plugin in plugin array
11553 		var flashVer = null;
11554 	
11555 		if (navigator.plugins != null && navigator.plugins.length > 0) {
11556 			if (navigator.plugins["Shockwave Flash 2.0"] || navigator.plugins["Shockwave Flash"]) {
11557 				var swVer2 = navigator.plugins["Shockwave Flash 2.0"] ? " 2.0" : "";
11558 				var flashDescription = navigator.plugins["Shockwave Flash" + swVer2].description;
11559 				var descArray = flashDescription.split(" ");
11560 				var tempArrayMajor = descArray[2].split(".");			
11561 				var versionMajor = tempArrayMajor[0];
11562 				var versionMinor = tempArrayMajor[1];
11563 				var versionRevision = descArray[3];
11564 				if (versionRevision == "") {
11565 					versionRevision = descArray[4];
11566 				}
11567 				if (versionRevision[0] == "d") {
11568 					versionRevision = versionRevision.substring(1);
11569 				} else if (versionRevision[0] == "r") {
11570 					versionRevision = versionRevision.substring(1);
11571 					if (versionRevision.indexOf("d") > 0) {
11572 						versionRevision = versionRevision.substring(0, versionRevision.indexOf("d"));
11573 					}
11574 				}
11575 				var flashVer = versionMajor + "." + versionMinor + "." + versionRevision;
11576 			}
11577 		}
11578 		// MSN/WebTV 2.6 supports Flash 4
11579 		else if (navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf("webtv/2.6") != -1) flashVer = 4;
11580 		// WebTV 2.5 supports Flash 3
11581 		else if (navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf("webtv/2.5") != -1) flashVer = 3;
11582 		// older WebTV supports Flash 2
11583 		else if (navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf("webtv") != -1) flashVer = 2;
11584 		else if ( n2i.browser.msie ) {
11585 			flashVer = this.getActiveXVersion();
11586 		}
11587 		this.fullVersion = flashVer;
11588 		return flashVer;
11589 	},
11590 	/** @private */
11591 	getActiveXVersion : function() {
11592 		var version;
11593 		var axo;
11594 		var e;
11595 
11596 		// NOTE : new ActiveXObject(strFoo) throws an exception if strFoo isn't in the registry
11597 
11598 		try {
11599 			// version will be set for 7.X or greater players
11600 			axo = new ActiveXObject("ShockwaveFlash.ShockwaveFlash.7");
11601 			version = axo.GetVariable("$version");
11602 		} catch (e) {
11603 		}
11604 
11605 		if (!version)
11606 		{
11607 			try {
11608 				// version will be set for 6.X players only
11609 				axo = new ActiveXObject("ShockwaveFlash.ShockwaveFlash.6");
11610 			
11611 				// installed player is some revision of 6.0
11612 				// GetVariable("$version") crashes for versions 6.0.22 through 6.0.29,
11613 				// so we have to be careful. 
11614 			
11615 				// default to the first public version
11616 				version = "WIN 6,0,21,0";
11617 
11618 				// throws if AllowScripAccess does not exist (introduced in 6.0r47)		
11619 				axo.AllowScriptAccess = "always";
11620 
11621 				// safe to call for 6.0r47 or greater
11622 				version = axo.GetVariable("$version");
11623 
11624 			} catch (e) {
11625 			}
11626 		}
11627 
11628 		if (!version)
11629 		{
11630 			try {
11631 				// version will be set for 4.X or 5.X player
11632 				axo = new ActiveXObject("ShockwaveFlash.ShockwaveFlash.3");
11633 				version = axo.GetVariable("$version");
11634 			} catch (e) {
11635 			}
11636 		}
11637 
11638 		if (!version)
11639 		{
11640 			try {
11641 				// version will be set for 3.X player
11642 				axo = new ActiveXObject("ShockwaveFlash.ShockwaveFlash.3");
11643 				version = "WIN 3,0,18,0";
11644 			} catch (e) {
11645 			}
11646 		}
11647 
11648 		if (!version)
11649 		{
11650 			try {
11651 				// version will be set for 2.X player
11652 				axo = new ActiveXObject("ShockwaveFlash.ShockwaveFlash");
11653 				version = "WIN 2,0,0,11";
11654 			} catch (e) {
11655 				version = -1;
11656 			}
11657 		}
11658 	
11659 		return version;
11660 	}
11661 }

11693 In2iGui.Links = function(options) {
11694 	this.options = options;
11695 	this.element = n2i.get(options.element);
11696 	this.name = options.name;
11697 	In2iGui.extend(this);
11698 	this.items = [];
11699 	this.addBehavior();
11700 	this.selectedIndex = null;
11701 	this.inputs = {};
11702 }
11703 
11704 In2iGui.Links.prototype = {
11705 	addBehavior : function() {
11706 		n2i.listen(this.element,'click',this.onClick.bind(this));
11707 		n2i.listen(this.element,'dblclick',this.onDblClick.bind(this));
11708 	},
11709 	reset : function() {
11710 		this.setValue([]);
11711 	},
11712 	setValue : function(items) {
11713 		this.items = items;
11714 		this.selectedIndex = null;
11715 		this.build();
11716 	},
11717 	getValue : function() {
11718 		return this.items;
11719 	},
11720 	onDblClick : function(e) {
11721 		e = new n2i.Event(e);
11722 		n2i.selection.clear();
11723 		e.stop(e);
11724 		var link = this.selectAndGetRow(e);
11725 		var values = {text:link.text};
11726 		values[link.kind]=link.value;
11727 		this.editedLink = link;
11728 		var win = this.getEditWindow();
11729 		this.editForm.reset();
11730 		this.editForm.setValues(values);
11731 		win.show();
11732 	},
11733 	onClick : function(e) {
11734 		e = new n2i.Event(e);
11735 		e.stop();
11736 		var element = e.getElement();
11737 		if (n2i.hasClass(element,'in2igui_links_remove')) {
11738 			var row = e.findByClass('in2igui_links_row');
11739 			In2iGui.confirmOverlay({element:element,text:'Vil du fjerne linket?',okText:'Ja, fjern',cancelText:'Annuller',onOk:function() {
11740 				this.items.splice(row.in2igui_index,1);
11741 				if (this.selectedIndex===row.in2igui_index) {
11742 					this.selectedIndex=null;
11743 				}
11744 				this.build();				
11745 			}.bind(this)});
11746 		} else {
11747 			this.selectAndGetRow(e);
11748 		}
11749 	},
11750 	selectAndGetRow : function(event) {
11751 		var row = event.findByClass('in2igui_links_row');
11752 		if (row) {
11753 			var idx = row.in2igui_index;
11754 			if (this.selectedIndex!==null) {
11755 				var x = n2i.byClass(this.element,'in2igui_links_row')[this.selectedIndex];
11756 				n2i.removeClass(x,'in2igui_links_row_selected')
11757 			}
11758 			this.selectedIndex = idx;
11759 			n2i.addClass(row,'in2igui_links_row_selected');
11760 			return this.items[idx];
11761 		}
11762 	},
11763 	build : function() {
11764 		var list = this.list || n2i.firstByClass(this.element,'in2igui_links_list');
11765 		list.innerHTML='';
11766 		for (var i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
11767 			var item = this.items[i];
11768 			var row = n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_links_row'});
11769 			row.in2igui_index = i;
11770 			
11771 			row.appendChild(In2iGui.createIcon(item.icon,1));
11772 			var text = n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_links_text',text:item.text});
11773 			row.appendChild(text);
11774 
11775 			var infoNode = n2i.build('div',{'class':'in2igui_links_info',text:n2i.wrap(item.info)});
11776 			row.appendChild(infoNode);
11777 			var remove = In2iGui.createIcon('monochrome/round_x',1);
11778 			n2i.addClass(remove,'in2igui_links_remove');
11779 			row.appendChild(remove);
11780 
11781 			list.appendChild(row);
11782 		};
11783 	},
11784 	addLink : function() {
11785 		this.editedLink = null;
11786 		this.getEditWindow().show();
11787 		this.editForm.reset();
11788 		this.editForm.focus();
11789 	},
11790 	getEditWindow : function() {
11791 		if (!this.editWindow) {
11792 			var win = this.editWindow = In2iGui.Window.create({title:'Link',width:300,padding:5});
11793 			var form = this.editForm = In2iGui.Formula.create();
11794 			var g = form.buildGroup({above:false},[
11795 				{type:'Text',options:{label:'Tekst',key:'text'}}
11796 			]);
11797 			
11798 			var url = In2iGui.Formula.Text.create({label:'URL',key:'url'});
11799 			g.add(url);
11800 			this.inputs['url']=url;
11801 			
11802 			var email = In2iGui.Formula.Text.create({label:'E-mail',key:'email'});
11803 			g.add(email);
11804 			this.inputs['email']=email;
11805 			
11806 			page = In2iGui.Formula.DropDown.create({label:'Side',key:'page',source:this.options.pageSource});
11807 			g.add(page);
11808 			this.inputs['page']=page;
11809 			
11810 			file = In2iGui.Formula.DropDown.create({label:'Fil',key:'file',source:this.options.fileSource});
11811 			g.add(file);
11812 			this.inputs['file']=file;
11813 			
11814 			var self = this;
11815 			n2i.each(this.inputs,function(key,value) {
11816 				value.listen({$valueChanged:function(){self.changeType(key)}});
11817 			});
11818 			
11819 			var b = g.createButtons().add(In2iGui.Button.create({text:'Gem',submit:true,highlighted:true}));
11820 			this.editForm.listen({$submit:this.saveLink.bind(this)});
11821 			win.add(form);
11822 			if (this.options.pageSource) {
11823 				this.options.pageSource.refresh();
11824 			}
11825 			if (this.options.fileSource) {
11826 				this.options.fileSource.refresh();
11827 			}
11828 		}
11829 		return this.editWindow;
11830 	},
11831 	saveLink : function() {
11832 		var v = this.editForm.getValues();
11833 		var link = this.valuesToLink(v);
11834 		var edited = this.editedLink;
11835 		if (edited) {
11836 			n2i.override(edited,link);
11837 		} else {
11838 			this.items.push(link);
11839 		}
11840 		this.build();
11841 		this.editForm.reset();
11842 		this.editWindow.hide();
11843 		this.editedLink = null;
11844 	},
11845 	valuesToLink : function(values) {
11846 		var link = {};
11847 		link.text = values.text;
11848 		if (values.email!='') {
11849 			link.kind='email';
11850 			link.value=values.email;
11851 			link.info=values.email;
11852 			link.icon='monochrome/email';
11853 		} else if (values.url!='') {
11854 			link.kind='url';
11855 			link.value=values.url;
11856 			link.info=values.url;
11857 			link.icon='monochrome/globe';
11858 		} else if (n2i.isDefined(values.page)) {
11859 			link.kind='page';
11860 			link.value=values.page;
11861 			link.info=this.inputs['page'].getItem().title;
11862 			link.icon='common/page';
11863 		} else if (n2i.isDefined(values.file)) {
11864 			link.kind='file';
11865 			link.value=values.file;
11866 			link.info=this.inputs['file'].getItem().title;
11867 			link.icon='monochrome/file';
11868 		}
11869 		return link;
11870 	},
11871 	changeType : function(type) {
11872 		n2i.each(this.inputs,function(key,value) {
11873 			if (key!=type) {
11874 				value.setValue();
11875 			}
11876 		});
11877 	}
11878 }
